


translate English day6_rs_rkn_8034c587:


    pl "No... No, that's not right, Lavi."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_e162667b:


    pl "I understand what you're saying, I really do... But we can't just end everything on a drop of a hat.{w} There has to be some other way."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_6df92795:


    rv "Excuse me, but you don't seem to understand me at all."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_4a33f916:


    rv "You're from another land. You don't need to involve yourself with us."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_9ada875a:


    rv "So, please. I'm suggesting this for your own benefit.{w} Just forget about--"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_9d7aa484:


    pl "I know I'm asking for too much... And you're right. I'm an outsider."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_43037ffe:


    pl "But I already know about Rose now!{w} I can't BE someone who isn't involved with you two anymore."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_04c778d4:


    pl "So telling me to just forget about everything... It's not that easy, you know."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_a4621121:


    rv "......"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_7f853d8b:


    pl "...Also, you're talking like you're trying to be considerate of me."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_bffb1bbb:


    pl "But do you really think leaving like that would make me feel any better?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_b78c43c0:


    rv "Little [na]..."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_f456ea47:


    nar "I was just running on pure momentum now. I close my mouth and stop talking."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_22788fda:


    nar "Lavien is the smartest priest I know. If he's being so insistent, he must have a clear reason."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_4a98b09a:


    nar "And to tell the truth, I have a faint idea of what that reason is.{w} Rose is still standing over there."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_85b44b50:


    nar "She doesn't seem to understand our rather impassioned conversation; she only looks up at us when her name happens to come up."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_d8be6fbf:


    nar "All while still wearing those dirty clothes.{w} I don't know what kind of a person she is."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_dd825a9e:


    nar "The time I've spent with her has been based on my own foolish misunderstanding, the fiction they've built up, and my curiosity--something that never had a right answer to begin with."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_ee6d9a2b:


    nar "And now it's lost all meaning. Nothing matters anymore."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_650d260f:


    rs "...[na], are you not coming anymore?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_4d3b83ce:


    nar "But that doesn't mean it ended without me learning anything."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_4a9f87c5:


    nar "At least I know there is a person named Rose here at the temple now."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_42bc1346:


    nar "And that's why I can't bring myself to leave so suddenly. Like I told Lavi, going back wouldn't make me feel better."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_29d28a4e:


    nar "I'll probably keep thinking about her."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_00004e44:


    nar "Even if I don't come back to the library, every time I see a children's book or something like it, I'll remember she's here."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_07e4f6fd:


    nar "And after accidentally teaching her just how long it can take to wait for someone...{w} I just can't do it."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_88b88c5e:


    pl "...Lavi... I'm not trying to argue with you.{w} It's just... Can't you let me see Rose, even if it's just once in a while?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_fa979406:


    rv "...Little [na]... You mustn't try and be friends with someone purely out of guilt..."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_b5d8430f:


    pl "Well, why don't you think about HER feelings instead of just mine?! You're her brother, aren't you?!"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_6d9265d6:


    rv "......!"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_ca3e0747:


    nar "Lavien's smile immediately vanishes."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_3a0e34c4:


    nar "He stiffens up, then takes a step back, but when his sister takes hold of his hem, his face goes back to normal."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_6ccf5fe1:


    rv "Rose..."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_67c439c0:


    rs "What?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_a4621121_1:


    rv "......"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_0f6813e7:


    rv "...I am terribly sorry. I tried to rob you two of an important bond, didn't I?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_04971ffa:


    rv "Maybe messing with machines day in and day out has made me somewhat thickheaded."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_e8d42035:


    rv "Anyway, to summarize, Rose needs to be cleaned and the books in the library organized..."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_f3ed6998:


    rv "Little [na], will you be so kind as to help?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_5ecb559a:


    pl "Oh... Huh? Of course. If there's anything at all I can do, just ask! For now... Should I start by cleaning up the books?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_09f09023:


    nar "Suddenly, something damp gets between my palm and fingers.{w} Surprised, I look over and see that it's Rose's hand."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_8430b68c:


    nar "I can't help but frown even then, though, since it's dirty, damp, and a little warm."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_b5aee43d:


    nar "I just hope Lavi doesn't see me frown."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_e5b86e21:


    rv "It seems like Rose wants to go with you."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_7bf162a6:


    pl "W-With me? Are you sure...?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_6e730042:


    rv "Yes. Rose can wash off and get changed herself."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_ac4ceeae:


    rv "So could you just keep an eye out to make sure nobody else sees her?{w} If you have any trouble, just tell me."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_e9fb429a:


    pl "No, I'll... I'll be fine.{w} Anyway, I'm just going with her, right?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_fcfc08cb:


    rv "Yes. Merely being at her side will be a huge help."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_305656e0:


    nar "Lavi looks at me with a smile."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_a1b223c5:


    nar "But I can tell he's not trying to use a smile to express his good mood like most people--just that he's painted over his face with one."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_13b4ce92:


    nar "Summoning my courage, I take Rose's unclean hand. She looks up at me, impassive."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_76c37eb5:


    rv "Here's Rose's change of clothes. She'll only need help with the zipper."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_9ae2b799:


    pl "Oh... Okay."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_e28e5e63:


    rv "Thank you so much for this, Little [na]."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_2665f8f1:


    pl "Right. I'll see you later."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_rs_rkn_c2f6b6c9:


    "\n The two of us leave the library, with Lavi watching us go."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_a9383689:


    "I say \"the two of us,\" but it's really just Rose following after me. She let go of my hand, too."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_aa88a669:


    et "I figured she wouldn't know the layout of the temple very well, but apparently that isn't the case."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_rs_rkn_5da288a6:


    "\n It must be because she's familiar with the Academics Department dormitories, given that she's a priest with them. I want to ask her, but I didn't, since I figured she'd probably stop walking to answer. I'm too anxious about anyone seeing, so I want to get her to the washroom as soon as I can."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_2d038274:


    "Thankfully, the shower room isn't too far away. I'd rather not hang around in front of the women's showers with another priest's clothes in my hand, so I put them into the changing room and leave entirely. I can't hear her response over the shower water."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_b5170d66:


    "The running sink faucet in the silence joins with the distant sound of her shower. It smells the same as in the library--exactly like lavender."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_36be60f3:



    nvl clear
    "\n I dunk my hands and gloves into the pooling water and let the liquid carry away the dirt. The two black gloves lying at the bottom of the pool are almost like their eyes."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_1f8d065d:


    et "Whether they're thinking or feeling, I can't discern what's behind those eyes.{w} For a while, my face gazes idly back out at me."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_5df0fea2:


    pl "Rose, are you there?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_a63038eb:


    nar "After returning, I knock on the changing room door twice.{w} I definitely hear a \"yeah\" this time, but it's echoey, probably because of how small the changing room is."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_f535c751:


    pl "Can you get back to the library by yourself?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_31aa1997:


    rs "Don't go. Stay there."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_817db990:


    pl "Okay, okay... Finish up quickly, alright?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_8fac5f4a:


    rs "...[na], are you not coming anymore?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_aa6a0f0d:


    pl "Hm? You asked that before we left the library."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_2a2afdf6:


    rs "You didn't answer at the time. You looked at Rose with alarm. People who look at Rose like that don't come back to Rose."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_01842e7c:


    pl "Well, that's... That's just because you do surprising stuff. Why did you do that, anyway?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_490dd0d5:


    rs "Because it is \"fun\" for Rose to cover herself in dirt."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_78227d03:


    pl "...It's not fun at all."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_43fd66b2:


    rs "The kids in town seemed to have fun doing it."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_be10ad6c:


    pl "It's not fun. Not in the slightest.{w} It's their fault... Ugh. Just try not to do things out of the blue like that, alright?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_f4856764:


    rs "What does \"out of the blue\" mean?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_20768a12:


    pl "Uh, you know. Like suddenly pulling all the neatly organized books off their shelves."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_ec5ddba0:


    rs "But you told Rose to find one she liked."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_aab8fed4:


    pl "Yeah, but you can find one without spilling them all over the ground..."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_af7102fe:


    rs "Then you aren't coming anymore?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_2a02c609:


    pl "...I'll still visit you. I just had a good talk with your brother.{w} At least, I think I will."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_3ecdee97:


    rs "......"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_0abf3356:


    pl "Does that make you happy?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_b22cc81e:


    rs "Yes. Now you can talk to Rose's brother too."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_b73c8dee:


    pl "That's right. You... You really tricked me, you know that?{w} Do you know how surprised I was?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_c9f99e9c:


    rs "Rose has only listened to her brother's request and carried out the duty of Lavien Rose. Rose has not told a lie."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_659209a3:


    rs "Hence, she has not tricked you."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_368fffbd:


    pl "Guess that makes me the idiot then... Sigh. Didn't you feel anything when you talked about Lavi?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_b515ae83:


    rs "Rose didn't like it."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_5d368724:


    pl "You didn't?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_57d1add2:


    rs "Because Rose couldn't call him her brother."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_4beed73c:


    rs "There are many names in this world. When you don't call someone their name for a long time, its meaning fades."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_161f05b9:


    rs "Whenever Rose was called Lavien instead of Rose, it was the same as Rose disappearing."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_335e401a:


    rs "This is because when Rose was called Lavien, she ceased to be Rose."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_28757468:


    rs "That's why Rose didn't like not being able to call her brother her brother."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_eaf33070:


    rs "Lavien would cease to be Rose's brother, and Rose's bond with him would disappear. Rose didn't want that."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_533f1ea0:


    pl "It's not like you stop being family just because you weren't calling him by his name. I mean, you're obviously twins to begin with..."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_ce8b8bf1:


    rs "That is merely visual information. You are the same, [na], since you didn't realize the truth."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_131f9cca:


    rs "Names are important to Rose because names have meaning and imply bonds."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_34f5116b:


    nar "Her explanation is all sorts of wild, but it's not TOTALLY nonsensical.{w} She's right--I didn't know until today that they were twins."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_88c69290:


    nar "The only reason I was able to realize they were siblings was because she referred to him as such."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_9b0b7799:


    nar "If she hadn't, the idea that they were twins would have only been one possibility in my mind out of many."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_af75a8f6:


    pl "You really like your brother, huh?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_0347fe97:


    rs "Rose's bond with her brother is the only one she has."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_dd66f654:


    pl "Why's that?{w} I mean, you read a lot of books, and... Well, Bishop Evelynn knows about you too, right?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_bcfd2dcc:


    rs "Those are all Lavi's possessions, not Rose's."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_d6fe624f:


    pl "...Well, you get along with me, aren't you? You can add that to the list."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_d38f53ac:


    rs "We get along?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_5dd2028d:


    pl "That's right.{w} And that's not something your brother gave you--it's something you got for yourself.{w} Right?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_d344c74e:


    rs "What are you to Rose, [na]?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_70edfc31:


    pl "Hmm. Friends, I guess. What do you think?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_2c1897d9:


    rs "[na] is Rose's..."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_3ecdee97_1:


    rs "......"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_1df18059:


    pl "...Hey, don't clam up in the middle of that sentence."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_9ef53400:


    rs "Rose can't zip it up. Rose requests help."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_235d54d5:


    pl "Zip it up...{w} Oh, yeah, right, the zipper. Got it."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_79e46bf9:



    nvl clear
    "\n The moment I open the door, she leaps into me."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_14fdad1f:


    "An unnatural whiteness bursts into view, and I reflexively close the door. My back slowly slides down it."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_03aee0ad:


    "Her head, about as big as a ball, presses into my abdomen. Its weight is about the same too--a ball made of firm leather, filled with dried grass and dirt."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_2acfeca8:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Hey--\""


translate English day6_rs_rkn_8141b9a1:


    et "Her pale body seems to almost glow in the darkness. As if to steal my body heat in that state, she stays attached to me, not breaking away."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_rs_rkn_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day6_rs_rkn_62df9280:


    "\n \"How is it?\""


translate English day6_rs_rkn_802d46c3:


    et "This again.{w} Those eyes again. Those black eyes that just seem so lifeless, as empty as a fish swimming through mossy water.{w} I can see my own baffled expression in them."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_3986c508:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Is Rose's body a human's body?\""


translate English day6_rs_rkn_d2b1d559:


    "My embarrassment naturally vanishes then. My heartbeat was racing because of the crazy, sudden situation, but it quickly starts to calm down too."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_4bdb5647:


    "Unlike her wet hair, her body is dry--likely proof that the towel at her feet has served its intended purpose. Rose can take showers by herself. If Lavi wasn't lying to me before, then she probably knows how to get changed on her own too. Which means this is all a sudden bout of selfishness."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_18b5ca63:


    et "As for why she's doing this... I don't really want to think about it."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_04dcd218:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"...It's normal.\""


translate English day6_rs_rkn_476c611b:


    "Normal enough that I shouldn't have to answer that question. There's nothing especially charming about her, nor is there anything to find fault with. She's got the same bones and blood vessels running through her muscles and fat as any other human."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_fd5bbf32:


    et "Plus, there's even a warmth from the hunks of flesh pressing against my legs. While I'm not shaking, maybe I feel colder than I thought, because I start getting goosebumps."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_847f6d1d:



    nvl clear
    "\n It was when I lifted my heavy head that I felt a rejection towards all of it.{w} As I look her up and down, she just stares at me with that same flat, impassive face. It's almost like she's trying to learn something from each and every one of my actions. Despite seeing her face every day, I'm still nowhere near used to that."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_5d407168:


    et "That inhuman part of her clashes terribly with all the human parts of her.{w} I could just reach out and touch her and feel that her warm skin belongs to a human--but far from doing that, I don't even say her name. I don't want to."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_c439b782:


    rv "Welcome back, Little [na]."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_b90de2aa:


    pl "Lavi..."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_bbed716c:


    nar "As soon as I see his face and make sure the door is closed, I collapse.{w} Lavi takes Rose; I can't tell from his face whether he's just confused or if he feels responsible."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_e0e01fa6:


    pl "She fell asleep on the way back. She's quite a sleepyhead, huh?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_c9e641f8:


    rv "Thank you for all this. And I'm sorry she caused you trouble."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_40ba3a8a:


    rv "I try to have her do these things herself, but she's always been a handful...{w} Did she trouble you in any way?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_1fa01567:


    pl "N-No... Not really. Just got a little tired after carrying her...{w} Haha. She did wash off by herself, so it was looking pretty good for a while."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_b67ae1e5:


    rv "That's good to hear--really. I'm not sure how to thank you."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_e208772e:


    pl "I'm just glad I could help..."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_3829b429:


    nar "Guilt drives into my heart.{w} I shut my eyes tight, trying to prevent my breathing from quickening and to erase that sensation from my memory."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_8df913ae:


    nar "But for each attempt, it comes back to me more vividly."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_79d271a5:


    pl "...It seems like she's taking a liking to me. I can watch her in your place from now on, when you need..."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_5aa0bcf7:


    pl "So if you need anything at all, just tell me."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_f0e64e03:


    rv "Oh, no, I couldn't..."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_5eaf76d8:


    nar "I feel like spitting at myself, calling myself a madman.{w} What I say is purely impulsive. I'm not even considering whether I actually think I can take responsibility--I just wanted to say the words."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_f7ea51d7:


    rv "...Well, alright. If I refused you any more than this, it would be rude to both of you."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_a6e3ba91:


    rv "It seems you wish to gain thanks enough to last a lifetime from me."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_78e54b27:


    rv "I'm embarrassed to say that despite being a priest of the Academics Department, I don't have much of a penchant for words."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_3d148286:


    rv "So it may sound like I'm repeating myself, but... I'll say it a hundred times--no, a thousand if I have to."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_917178c4:


    rv "Thank you--thank you so very much. From the bottom of my heart."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_627caf97:


    rv "And if you ever need any help from me, you can tell me anytime."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_ae4f28b5:


    pl "H-Ha..."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_f8db10a0:


    nar "Don't laugh."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_d31bc933:


    pl "Haha... You're really exaggerating, you know... I... What am I supposed to..."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_eb1e660c_1:


    pl "......"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_b9d0132c:


    pl "I should get going."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_aa454a66:


    rv "Yes, it's getting to be that time. Please take care, Little [na]."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_b0a9f8ae:


    nar "I walk out, staggering under my own weight."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_1885f789:


    nar "Mentally, I'm exhausted, and yet my body feels as light as a feather."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_b8a4a636:


    nar "My legs move on their own, as if they don't belong to me, wandering this way and that in the temple.{w} My surroundings keep changing, and quite a few people pass by me."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_57c893cf:


    nar "What have I done? What's going to happen now?"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_54f068c4:


    nar "If word of what I've done gets out, everyone at the temple will start giving me second looks."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_669bb0bf:


    nar "......"


translate English day6_rs_rkn_89dca27b:



    nvl clear
    "\n When I raise my head, I see a light. A brilliantly bright light that urges me forward, the type that burns forever, unable to be extinguished. It beckons me."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_f29c5c12:


    "I wasn't wandering aimlessly after all. I'd returned to this spot on purpose."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_e99f4a4d:


    et "Two big wings, so white they're almost blinding, clearly not of this world."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_9271b365:



    nvl clear
    "\n My vision darkens, my eyes unable to bear the light in all its brilliance. My head naturally falls forward, and I drop to my knees."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_b302d262:


    "I raise my trembling hands, reaching out to touch her skin.{w} I feel even more deplorable for not knowing the proper way to do this."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_2f667f8b:


    "But the angel gives even someone disrespectful like me a chance, allowing me to touch her. Unintentionally, I start to cry."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_d0cb3ef7:


    "I take her soft hands in mine and weep like a newborn baby."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_781dfd15:


    et "I am touching the angel. And yet my eyes have not been stricken with blindness, I can speak without vomiting, my mind is clear, and I don't even have a headache."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_69cca741:



    nvl clear
    "\n The angel appeared in this world for me. {w}Oh, god. Thank you, my beloved angel."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_361a1f97:


    "I beg you to forgive me.{w} Please watch over me in my foolishness with your mercy and compassion."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_4b483f0d:


    et "Forgive me my sins."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_8e92792d:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"I... I've doubted the pure heart of a priest of the Academics Department."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_8e8eed56:


    "Her guardian asked me to take care of her, and thus it should fall to me to be responsible for her, and yet..."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_160b0482:


    et "I have felt feelings of disgust against her, she who should be treasured.\""


translate English day6_rs_rkn_bf7296b4:



    nvl clear
    "\n Spoken aloud, my sin takes on a tangible weight."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_6caee1bf:


    "Once I spit out every last one of my crimes, I can finally accept them as truth."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_23e45339:


    "The light still hides the sinner, shining on me rather than fleeing from my sinful soul.{w} As long as the angel forgives this trespass, I can remain human."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_e8240e71:


    et "Within the shadow cast by her wings, as the warm wind blows onto me... I welcome the most beautiful light in all the world."


translate English day6_rs_rkn_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


