translate English day7_rs_8804abba:



    nvl clear
    "\n I had a very, very long dream. With my vision blurred and my head throbbing in pain as if trapped in a vice, it feels like I've been asleep for seven days."


translate English day7_rs_c633cf33:


    "All I know for sure is that my consciousness remains trapped in that dream, though I can't for the life of me remember what happened."


translate English day7_rs_7a26e823:


    "I get the feeling I had a nightmare, but I also feel like it wasn't so bad, too."


translate English day7_rs_94aca8d8:


    "With long dreams, they're usually so pleasant that you never want to wake up--or so terrifying that it's impossible to come back to the waking world."


translate English day7_rs_648c3dd7:


    "Not wanting to think about it any more, I sink my throbbing head into my pillow. {w}I'm so done with thinking."


translate English day7_rs_d7ae7cd2:


    "How much time have I wasted reflecting on my dreams lately?"


translate English day7_rs_c4056ed6:


    et "I don't need to do that anymore.{w} The angel doesn't speak to me in dreams--she speaks to me in real life, too..."


translate English day7_rs_478b31fc:



    nvl clear
    "\n As I lie on the bed, I lift my face up a little and gaze at the bright, white light shining in through the window."


translate English day7_rs_8105756b:


    "The sun, which set during the night, has risen once again to mark the morning.{w} That faint light must mean it's a new day."


translate English day7_rs_91031fe1:


    "My body feels heavy.{w} I squeeze my eyes shut, but the pounding in my head doesn't stop. I doubt I'll be able to rest any longer."


translate English day7_rs_9cc593e7:


    "Maybe it isn't just me--maybe I really did sleep for seven days. For some reason the idea excites me a bit, but I'm pretty sure that's not what happened."


translate English day7_rs_3923c360:


    et "As my mind awakens from the dream, my memories come back to me. In my head, I go over what needs doing today."


translate English day7_rs_06a49c8f:



    nvl clear
    "\n First, I've gotta get out of bed.{w} I need to prepare for the morning by securing a wash station before the whole washroom is filled with people, and I should probably clean the clothes I've been wearing this whole time."


translate English day7_rs_108d26cd:


    et "Once I'm clean and clothed, I'll say hello to Maya, then go take the bishop's class.{w} It'll be a little awkward facing her, but I'll just be listening and not talking to her, anyway."


translate English day7_rs_f0780563:



    nvl clear
    "\n Work isn't great, but I think I can manage it.{w} I'm still technically a newbie here, but I'm starting to learn the ropes well enough."


translate English day7_rs_b456ec53:


    "But right now, I'm lying in a salty-smelling bed under a too-familiar ceiling.{w} I can hear the footsteps of the priests outside the door, getting ready for the day as usual."


translate English day7_rs_33fa2f05:


    "I could do it if I wanted, but I don't want to.{w} Not just my Cleanup Department work, either--I don't want to do anything, including get out of bed."


translate English day7_rs_58c1b5f6:


    et "Is it just a whim or is it indolence?{w} Either way, I fold my arms over my stomach again and try to continue to rest."


translate English day7_rs_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_rs_0bf27179:


    et "\n \"Do you not like it?\""


translate English day7_rs_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_rs_7be71fc5:



    nvl clear
    "\n I must have been resting my eyes for about ten minutes."


translate English day7_rs_c96b4327:


    et "I struggle to get my heavy body up, not because the silence in the hallway is making me anxious but because I know I should."


translate English day7_rs_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day7_rs_52451a50:


    nar "A damp wind blows past my eyes, which are rough and dry at the moment.{w} I look again to see the sky is awfully cloudy."


translate English day7_rs_a2a27202:


    nar "Before entering the room, I stop myself for a moment.{w} About ten people come out of the room at once. Roll call must be over."


translate English day7_rs_72cd9e40:


    pl "Maya!"


translate English day7_rs_c45a297c:


    nar "I spot a familiar face from within the crowd and happily walk over to her."


translate English day7_rs_94be9f51:


    nar "The other priests shoot us curious glances as they file out into the hallway, observing the two of us walking side-by-side."


translate English day7_rs_771f900e:


    my "G-Good morning, [na2]."


translate English day7_rs_ada8473e:


    pl "Are you on your way to work?"


translate English day7_rs_02ed3da9:


    my "Y-Yeah. I, uh..."


translate English day7_rs_2ab315ab:



    nvl clear
    "{nw}" with sshake


translate English day7_rs_0f9d8f17:



    nvl clear
    nar "As she shuffles along slowly, trying to get out of line, someone shoves her as they pass by."


translate English day7_rs_34abf5ad:


    pl "Are you okay, Maya?!"


translate English day7_rs_c2468179:


    my "Y-Yes. They didn't hit me that hard...{w} It's my fault for standing still in the middle of a tight hallway."


translate English day7_rs_3e07e769:


    pl "Oh, good.{w} I just wish things didn't constantly happen to get you hurt..."


translate English day7_rs_50c33ba3:


    my "Oh, you're... You're exaggerating, [na2]... But thanks for worrying about me."


translate English day7_rs_8887b431:


    pl "No thanks needed--anyone would worry. I was the one who started awkwardly talking to you... Sorry."


translate English day7_rs_158d7775:


    my "...[na2]... Did you get back alright yesterday?"


translate English day7_rs_0b1cd7a5:


    pl "Huh...? Oh, well... Yeah. Thanks for asking."


translate English day7_rs_cb373e80:


    my "You, um... You looked really tired, so I was worried."


translate English day7_rs_97e284c2:


    pl "Haha... Sorry for making you worry yet again."


translate English day7_rs_f80fae5a:


    my "...I'll pretend it never happened, so I'd like it if you did the same, [na2]."


translate English day7_rs_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day7_rs_0b69aacc:


    my "...I'll get going."


translate English day7_rs_f7c75dee:


    pl "Right... D-Do you want me to come with you?"


translate English day7_rs_b3b5b3bd:


    my "No... I can't keep making you and Cue do all the work.{w} You do a proper job with your own work too, okay?"


translate English day7_rs_644e3d87:


    pl "...Be careful, alright?"


translate English day7_rs_1e97661b:


    my "I will... You too, [na2]."


translate English day7_rs_8ac69840:


    nar "I watch her petite back slip further away from me as she runs down the hall. {w}I notice the unmistakable mark of the angel on it."


translate English day7_rs_eb1e660c_1:


    pl "......"


translate English day7_rs_9a68b6f4:


    nar "Before I know it, nobody is left in front of the room and I hear what sounds like guys laughing inside the room."


translate English day7_rs_e57428e2:


    pl "Pretend it never happened..."


translate English day7_rs_a2c0d046:


    nar "I ruminate on the words the angel left me."


translate English day7_rs_922e53e9:


    nar "They're basically the same as what Lavien told me yesterday.{w} Did she forgive me for my sin?"


translate English day7_rs_b44777dd:


    nar "Does that mean the sin I committed towards Rose is nullified?"


translate English day7_rs_9ad9d8b5:


    nar "I finish up my tasks quickly and return to the workplace."


translate English day7_rs_2d60ed34:


    nar "It's still really noisy here with all the machines spinning, but today I hear a strange metal sound, like someone pounding iron."


translate English day7_rs_cc8b23c9:


    nar "Securett is not too far away, standing in an odd position, peering intently inside a storehouse."


translate English day7_rs_0c390330:


    nar "I get closer. As I thought, I don't need to investigate--the metallic noises are coming from inside there."


translate English day7_rs_629fe525:


    pl "Hey. What are you up to?"


translate English day7_rs_77791284:


    sc "......"


translate English day7_rs_9e931fd6:


    nar "Securett opens his mouth to speak.{w} He says something, but he's always had a soft voice, so the mechanical discord drowns him out."


translate English day7_rs_8008a836:


    nar "I put a hand to my ear to tell him I can't hear well, but he closes his mouth again, despite seeing it."


translate English day7_rs_b636dffb:


    nar "Before I can display how little I appreciate his attitude, he finally turns his eyes towards me again."


translate English day7_rs_06ba4aea:


    sc "...The machine broke down.{w} An Academics Department priest is fixing it for us now."


translate English day7_rs_08f8fa57:


    pl "You really hate raising your voice, huh?{w} Anyway, the Academics Department, huh?"


translate English day7_rs_a5c4002e:


    sc "All the machines at the temple are things the Academics Department has built. You didn't know?"


translate English day7_rs_cc0e0daa:


    pl "Hmm... Actually, I think someone from their department mentioned that when I went to the library before..."


translate English day7_rs_c1c4d0dd:


    nar "I peer into the storehouse he's facing. My words catch in my throat."


translate English day7_rs_1df8a567:


    nar "Because the very person I'd just thought of comes walking out of there."


translate English day7_rs_916871bd:


    nar "He has a little bit of soot on his cheeks and nose as he exits, pulling out the hair caught behind his goggles."


translate English day7_rs_4fbb4a94:


    rv "Huh? Why, hello, Little [na]. Did you get back safely yesterday?"


translate English day7_rs_ca7acc09:


    pl "Oh, wow... You were the one who came to fix it, Lavi?{w} Yeah, I got home just fine."


translate English day7_rs_95f72883:


    sc "Thanks for all the hard work, Lavi. How are the repairs going?"


translate English day7_rs_8f390fa7:


    rv "I can't say it's 100%% back to normal, but it's about 87%% okay which is basically brand new now, so you shouldn't have any problems for a while."


translate English day7_rs_56eacfde:


    pl "Man, you're really something else."


translate English day7_rs_429512c2:


    sc "...I don't recall you two being friends."


translate English day7_rs_5e48e958:


    pl "Well, I mean...{w} I've been stopping by the library a lot recently."


translate English day7_rs_95f9c3a9:


    pl "I'm studying solely to stop you from nagging to me all the time. No more griping out of you, ha ha!"


translate English day7_rs_6a00ca64:


    sc "Huh..."


translate English day7_rs_af66e6f1:


    nar "Securett glances at the bag I've been dragging around."


translate English day7_rs_12876042:


    sc "Are you using that, [na2]?"


translate English day7_rs_1dafeed8:


    pl "Well, yeah."


translate English day7_rs_31edbdab:


    sc "In that case, I'll clean up for you. You two can have a chat or something."


translate English day7_rs_2a60e6aa:


    pl "Huh? What?"


translate English day7_rs_bc9fa7df:


    rv "Oh, my... I'm perfectly fine with it!{w} But what about you, Little [na]?"


translate English day7_rs_a26aa917:


    pl "Honestly, if he wants to do my work for me, I'm all for it, but..."


translate English day7_rs_d9ba54b7:


    sc "But what?"


translate English day7_rs_79101dee:


    pl "Hmm... Nah, never mind. Just don't change the story on me later, got it?"


translate English day7_rs_669f3abc:


    nar "As Securett transfers my bag to a cart and brings it all into the storehouse, the two of us start walking a good distance away."


translate English day7_rs_b07b7204:


    nar "I start to hear an awful mechanical noise after that."


translate English day7_rs_bbded8de:


    nar "A noise like hardened things getting crushed, even the toughest matter being shaved to bits, and liquid being squeezed out of them..."


translate English day7_rs_ccc27239:


    pl "Ghek. Kinda feel sick..."


translate English day7_rs_fd274ca0:


    rv "Even people from this department don't get used to that, huh?"


translate English day7_rs_f6be41c3:


    pl "Of course not. How could I?"


translate English day7_rs_8f6cca92:


    rv "I suppose it's said that in all matters, there is a minimum of thirty kinds of predicaments, selected representatively."


translate English day7_rs_7e393eba:


    pl "If those are supposed to represent the rest, then that's a lot...{w} That aside, does everyone at the temple call you Lavi?"


translate English day7_rs_5bffaf96:


    rv "No, not at all. If there were ten people here, about two of them would call me that."


translate English day7_rs_da73c27d:


    pl "Hmm... That's not a whole lot.{w} You know, that guy almost never calls people by a nickname. It's kinda strange."


translate English day7_rs_f46d2172:


    rv "But don't you call me a nickname as well, Little [na]?"


translate English day7_rs_98becfd3:


    pl "Guess I'm part of your little circle of acquaintances, huh? Haha."


translate English day7_rs_616e7144:


    nar "Though it's not only HIS circle..."


translate English day7_rs_f8b7ad4e:


    pl "...Was Rose alright after that?"


translate English day7_rs_aa1108d4:


    rv "She slept until we got back to the dorm. She was pretty tired...{w} A lot happened that day, after all."


translate English day7_rs_34cc8ae4:


    pl "Yeah... A lot did happen. I'm glad nothing caused a problem.{w} Like I said yesterday, if you ever need help with anything, you can ask me."


translate English day7_rs_636838a1:


    rv "Then excuse the suddenness, but there was actually something I wanted to ask of you."


translate English day7_rs_53d575cb:


    pl "You... Hey, you planned on this from the start!{w} Anyway, what is it?"


translate English day7_rs_70f6776f:


    rv "It's none other than this: I'd like you to bring Rose to the cafeteria and have lunch with her."


translate English day7_rs_d52f033e:


    rv "Normally, she eats a packed lunch... But apparently she didn't get one today."


translate English day7_rs_164a04bb:


    pl "So I should just go eat lunch with her and come back?"


translate English day7_rs_d5f2b5c0:


    rv "Yes. Rose isn't a very picky eater, but if there are tomatoes on the menu, do your best to convince her to eat them."


translate English day7_rs_85894fca:


    pl "Sure, I guess... But you can't enter the cafeteria twice in one day, right? What will you do?"


translate English day7_rs_5a6aad65:


    rv "I'm going to finish up a few leftover jobs from recently.{w} There really aren't many, so I'll probably finish them in an hour."


translate English day7_rs_3a2588ec:


    pl "I... I wasn't really asking about your work. What about your lunch?"


translate English day7_rs_0fb7f370:


    rv "A little hunger sharpens my focus. It can actually be kind of useful."


translate English day7_rs_831da78d:


    nar "Lavi smiles at me. What's so fun about any of that?"


translate English day7_rs_edc1cc67:


    nar "It actually rubs me the wrong way, but I don't say anything in particular."


translate English day7_rs_06488a1c:


    nar "After all, if he eats lunch today, Rose wouldn't be able to instead."


translate English day7_rs_3f3b30c9:


    pl "Alright, well... If you're fine with it. I can grab you a few pieces of bread if there's any around."


translate English day7_rs_c7407cd5:


    rv "I'm grateful beyond words for he offer, Little [na], but you're not allowed to bring food out of the cafeteria."


translate English day7_rs_165e5a9f:


    pl "Seriously...? I've done it more than once already..."


translate English day7_rs_0f37c3f7:


    rv "Again, I really appreciate the offer. In any case, I need to get back to the Academics Department."


translate English day7_rs_58d75247:


    pl "Already? I guess you're pretty busy too, huh?"


translate English day7_rs_dea95c9d:


    rv "I have my own responsibilities to attend to. Thank you for being so kind despite how sudden my request of you was."


translate English day7_rs_3d6fac69:


    rv "And say hello to Little Securett for me, too."


translate English day7_rs_630df22a:


    pl "Sure thing. Good luck."


translate English day7_rs_f012d922:


    nar "With a grunt, Lavi shoulders his big bag and nimbly heads out of the workplace, moving like it barely weighs a thing."


translate English day7_rs_b4c7980c:


    nar "As I look after him, I still feel odd, but I decide not to think about it. I don't want to be a busybody for no reason."


translate English day7_rs_6044ea4a:


    nar "With the mechanical noises gone, I go back to the storehouse just as Securett is trying to pick up a bag covered in black grime."


translate English day7_rs_44410145:


    sc "Finished talking already? That was fast."


translate English day7_rs_90a39c2d:


    pl "I mean, there's not much I need to talk to him one-on-one for. But thanks for being considerate."


translate English day7_rs_c29aa452:


    sc "I just figured it'd be easier for you two to be alone since it was so loud."


translate English day7_rs_d672ee4f:


    pl "Right, right."


translate English day7_rs_7318d6a0:


    nar "I grab the bag's opening and spread it out.{w} Securett, using a long-handled gourd, scrapes off the grime and throws it inside."


translate English day7_rs_ffce8b63:


    nar "The light bag gets heavier and heavier, filling with unknown matter."


translate English day7_rs_68e56dc7:


    pl "...Are you friends with Lavi?"


translate English day7_rs_3338d307:


    sc "We just say hello when we happen to see each other. It's mostly when one of our department's machines breaks like before."


translate English day7_rs_5fa76c33:


    pl "He's so busy. I bet he has stuff to do for his own department, too..."


translate English day7_rs_73782097:


    pl "Oh. By the way, does the Academics Department do anything besides observing the Pestis?{w} I feel like I heard about them deciphering relics at some point."


translate English day7_rs_319610f3:


    sc "They decipher ancient relics, research them, and turn them into things we can use.{w} Things like building technology, and typewriters."


translate English day7_rs_ef6518fb:


    sc "According to them, compared to the technology of the ancients, humanity right now is still like barbarians."


translate English day7_rs_ae221f3b:


    pl "And the ones left behind are really struggling to catch up, huh..."


translate English day7_rs_5a1cf1e7:


    sc "It's like that for everyone."


translate English day7_rs_906fd3d0:


    pl "Anything else?"


translate English day7_rs_64c57dc0:


    sc "Anything else...?{w} Well, they do independent research too."


translate English day7_rs_633c143a:


    sc "We just have to work, work, work here without thinking. But the priests need to get results."


translate English day7_rs_f5989502:


    sc "If one of them writes a thesis and their bishop likes it, their life at the temple improves."


translate English day7_rs_7be442e1:


    pl "Huh... I guess their department isn't one just anyone can make it in.{w} What kind of research does Lavi do?"


translate English day7_rs_f93a4c88:


    sc "I don't know. But he's an auxiliary bishop, so he must have gotten pretty good results from it."


translate English day7_rs_60c8ab70:


    sc "He's really knowledgeable, so it's probably a good idea to make friends with him."


translate English day7_rs_940826c9:


    pl "Ha, Enoch said the same thing earlier."


translate English day7_rs_e67013bd:


    pl "If someone gloomy like you approves of him, he must be pretty amazing!"


translate English day7_rs_9f281572:


    sc "...He is."


translate English day7_rs_fd57ab63:


    pl "Well... Anyway, is there anything bothering him?"


translate English day7_rs_24a1e498:


    sc "Bothering him...? If there is, I'd want to know as well."


translate English day7_rs_c604de0f:


    nar "The bag, already extremely heavy, takes a lot more force to lift up now."


translate English day7_rs_42717406:


    sc "But I'm sure he does... He's only human, after all."


translate English day7_rs_91d82a4b:


    pl "Ha ha... Yeah, he's only human..."


translate English day7_rs_669bb0bf:


    nar "......"


translate English day7_rs_e91b5687:


    nar "As soon as my work is over, I go see Rose."


translate English day7_rs_d634df7c:


    nar "I knock on the door, but there's no answer at first. Eventually I hear it get unlocked, so I carefully open it."


translate English day7_rs_50ec4af0:


    rs "Wel...come."


translate English day7_rs_a768fafe:


    nar "Rose, standing slightly bent with her hands on her knees, looks different from usual."


translate English day7_rs_4e7e6a82:


    nar "Her clothes aren't too different, but she's switched out her usual pants for a skirt."


translate English day7_rs_2133b7ab:


    nar "Several hair pins are holding her shaggy bangs back, letting her eyes--which have always been hidden behind them--look at me directly."


translate English day7_rs_315d5a60:


    pl "Rose...?{w} What are you wearing?"


translate English day7_rs_21c8fb5f:


    rs "These are Rose' priest clothes. Lady Evelynn gave them to her.{w} Because Rose's brother said Rose can be Rose now."


translate English day7_rs_1e202b33:


    pl "But if you wear different clothes, won't more people start suspecting you two?"


translate English day7_rs_e775e428:


    rs "Rose's brother said it was okay. He told her to wear clothes she likes."


translate English day7_rs_50265f94:


    pl "Clothes you like...?"


translate English day7_rs_36672296:


    rs "How does Rose look?{w} From your point of view."


translate English day7_rs_88310b1e:


    nar "Unlike her brother, who comes off looking like a swallow's tail,"


translate English day7_rs_4755d7d1:


    nar "her clothes are like a round tablecloth, softening her generally boyish impression."


translate English day7_rs_c9f3707c:


    nar "Not only that, but even Rose herself is talking with so much less of her mechanical tone than I remember."


translate English day7_rs_76f9f843:


    pl "Well... It does look more attractive, maybe because I can see your face without the bangs there."


translate English day7_rs_45c23246:


    rs "Attractive... Is that a compliment?"


translate English day7_rs_b6d82e5a:


    pl "Yep, and my compliments are worth a lot!{w} I'm sure you're happy about getting one."


translate English day7_rs_ea1490ff:


    rs "Rose is happy.{w} Rose is attractive. A compliment.{w} Rose is very happy!"


translate English day7_rs_9244ea81:


    pl "Ha ha ha... You need a little more practice to speak naturally."


translate English day7_rs_21759ea8:


    rs "What should Rose do?"


translate English day7_rs_3edb6069:


    pl "Well... For example, if you're happy, I think you should smile.{w} See? Like this."


translate English day7_rs_5dcc6b93:


    nar "It's pretty weird, telling her to smile normally while also teaching her how to make a perfectly normal facial expression."


translate English day7_rs_f420ac4e:


    nar "I use my shaking lips and drooping eyelids to give my best impression of a natural smile."


translate English day7_rs_f5a176c1:


    nar "Rose looks at me with those dark eyes all the while."


translate English day7_rs_066abadb:


    nar "Her eyes seem unfocused as they silently stare at each and every wrinkle my face movements are making."


translate English day7_rs_3ecdee97:


    rs "......"


translate English day7_rs_293737a1:


    nar "Then, eventually, she smiles at me. Tugged by her eye bags, the corners of her eyes turn up, and her slender lips slowly split to either side too."


translate English day7_rs_6ea2bba7:


    nar "Her smile isn't strange at all--it's normal. The expression is so naturally ingrained that you'd never believe she figured it out purely based on someone else giving her an example."


translate English day7_rs_df6e3afc:


    nar "The next thing I know, the expression is gone from my face."


translate English day7_rs_69145892:


    pl "...Yeah. That looks nice."


translate English day7_rs_d67b53bf:


    nar "Maintaining her smile, she purses her lips and speaks almost like doing ventriloquy."


translate English day7_rs_3616938e:


    rs "Is it attractive?"


translate English day7_rs_cedf4902:


    pl "I mean, I'd say so."


translate English day7_rs_aa2a06e2:


    nar "I rub my hands firmly against her cheeks, feeling like I'm kneading flour or clay as I return her face to normal."


translate English day7_rs_d7e5401b:


    nar "Rose's skin is warmer than it looks, and it has a slight dampness to it. I don't want to touch it for very long."


translate English day7_rs_36f773cb:


    pl "Rose, your brother probably already told you this, but you'll be eating lunch in the cafeteria with me today."


translate English day7_rs_127e832b:


    rs "Cafeteria?"


translate English day7_rs_1facbf43:


    pl "The one in the temple. You still don't want to leave the room?"


translate English day7_rs_9a557a90:


    rs "No, Rose is okay now.{w} She'll go."


translate English day7_rs_7d1191a9:



    nvl clear
    "\n We pick out a corner seat while eating.{w} Fortunately, I don't see anyone I know. Then again, I've always stood out in a crowd, so people did look at us sometimes."


translate English day7_rs_db2b9b1b:


    "Lavi's worries turn out to be true--tomatoes are on the menu."


translate English day7_rs_1058aa4e:


    "Rose frowns and starts grumbling uncharacteristically. I sit her down and give her a gentle talk.{w} I ask her if it's an allergy, but she shakes her head no."


translate English day7_rs_38517edf:


    et "When I ask her why she doesn't like tomatoes, she replies with a short answer: they feel weird."


translate English day7_rs_a553b60d:



    nvl clear
    "\n So it's a texture thing... I can't help but think back to work this morning.{w} Those chunks of human, rotten to the point of being goopy."


translate English day7_rs_9afbd425:


    "The red tomatoes have been boiled in the stew, so they don't look like tomatoes anymore.{w} Only the thin pieces of skin you can pluck out give any indication of to what they used to be."


translate English day7_rs_c3f8ec8c:


    "The soft chunks of tomato drift across the liquid as I mix in a few of them with my spoon, crush them, and mix them with the broth.{w} White bubbles pop up on the surface."


translate English day7_rs_fa1e7ed7:


    "As I watch it with a complicated look for a few moments. In the end, I'm fascinated--and Rose is watching."


translate English day7_rs_0e467fdc:


    et "I want to say to her, \"What? I've got tastes and preferences too, you know.\""


translate English day7_rs_2baf7c25:



    nvl clear
    "\n When I put the spoon in my mouth, Rose finally moves her own spoon, seeming uninterested.{w} The tomato gets crushed in my mouth and floats over my tongue before descending down my esophagus."


translate English day7_rs_e6cb9cf4:


    et "I stand up without having tasted any of it much.{w} Rose follows me, constantly rubbing her stomach. Maybe she's not happy about filling herself with food she doesn't like."


translate English day7_rs_8f20ca3f:


    pl "Rose, do you have something on your hand?"


translate English day7_rs_6601aa08:


    rs "On my hand?"


translate English day7_rs_5ae326e7:


    pl "Hold still a minute. I knew you were holding your spoon wrong..."


translate English day7_rs_a5af1ece:


    nar "I take a look around, then go over to a nearby faucet and wet a tissue."


translate English day7_rs_e69a7e84:


    nar "After making Rose stand in front of me, I squat down and fold her hem up twice."


translate English day7_rs_ad44ec3b:


    rs "Did Rose...get her clothes dirty?{w} The attractive clothes Rose was allowed to have...?"


translate English day7_rs_7abbfce5:


    pl "It's okay. Don't be so sad, or you're gonna make me sad too..."


translate English day7_rs_432127f8:


    nar "I take Rose's hand, then wipe off each of her fingers as though brushing away dust from small objects."


translate English day7_rs_7a3b1ff0:


    nar "Going along her blood vessels, which look blue on the back of her white hand, and her smooth bones, which I can feel underneath her joints, I arrive at the end of her hand."


translate English day7_rs_a6bdc499:


    nar "Her fingertips are notched, looking like gears, like the kind you'd find in a clock."


translate English day7_rs_a6a6db11:


    pl "Do you bite your nails a lot?"


translate English day7_rs_3ecdee97_1:


    rs "......"


translate English day7_rs_c8dd91e6:


    pl "No backing out of this."


translate English day7_rs_058653a8:


    rs "...Yeah."


translate English day7_rs_fc28fa2b:


    pl "That's not a good habit."


translate English day7_rs_55d60fd6:


    rs "Rose's brother says it's bad too. So Rose wanted to hide it from you."


translate English day7_rs_66e12cb7:


    pl "You can't just hide stuff like this. They're a mess."


translate English day7_rs_bd439203:


    rs "It's okay.{w} Rose's brother put medicine on them."


translate English day7_rs_f72353c3:


    pl "Medicine... Oh. Okay."


translate English day7_rs_3b5038be:


    nar "I feel like I'm taking care of a little sister much younger than me."


translate English day7_rs_9428eb16:


    nar "As I see to Rose, I'm reminded of the kids in my home village."


translate English day7_rs_9c8f644d:


    nar "I've never felt quite this bothered by having to take care of someone."


translate English day7_rs_f210ebf3:


    nar "Lavi probably has to do it every day."


translate English day7_rs_20cc90a5:


    pl "Be careful in the future, got it?"


translate English day7_rs_058653a8_1:


    rs "Got it."


translate English day7_rs_8c7fb090:


    pl "...Hmm. I might as well take you back to the library too."


translate English day7_rs_8732c25f:


    rs "Will you not read a book today?"


translate English day7_rs_03363f47:


    pl "Unfortunately, I'm kinda tired from today. I want to go to sleep early."


translate English day7_rs_c3dcc284:


    rs "Okay... Then Rose won't go to the library today either.{w} She'll go back to her dorm."


translate English day7_rs_f70574e2:


    pl "Oh. Then I'll bring you there."


translate English day7_rs_058653a8_2:


    rs "Okay."


translate English day7_rs_1a9cfd7e:


    nar "...Going the whole way there in silence would be uncomfortable. Maybe I should make conversation."


translate English day7_rs_03e43d83:


    pl "Hey, so are you not an Academics Department priest?"


translate English day7_rs_2a8781da:


    rs "Affirmative. Rose, who does not borrow her brother's name and only answered to \"Lavien Rose\" in the past, is an outsider."


translate English day7_rs_b3b9889a:


    pl "Oh... Your brother is researching something, right? Any idea what it is?"


translate English day7_rs_f0dd7543:


    rs "No. Rose has never asked.{w} Rose's brother talks to Rose about a lot of things, but not about his work."


translate English day7_rs_ba9926a6:


    pl "Then what kind of things do you two usually talk about?"


translate English day7_rs_31aa9ee1:


    rs "We speak regarding how clear the day's weather was, about how Rose is feeling physically, about the smell of tea leaves, and about new animals Rose found in dictionaries..."


translate English day7_rs_efeb4e51:


    pl "Sounds pretty normal."


translate English day7_rs_18c71fc9:


    rs "Did you want to know about his research?"


translate English day7_rs_007fb0c2:


    pl "I mean, I'm curious, but it's not mega important."


translate English day7_rs_35806270:


    rs "You have a habit of being curious about everything, [na]."


translate English day7_rs_97add964:


    rs "The Academics Department performs research on many things, such as plants that grow from decayed earth, the ancestors of living animals, human psychology, automata..."


translate English day7_rs_ca7f767d:


    pl "Automata?"


translate English day7_rs_e58c65a8:


    rs "Rose speaks of research on machines."


translate English day7_rs_2f9bf064:


    pl "Oh. So then there's others besides your brother who are machine experts, huh? I guess that makes sense."


translate English day7_rs_34d0384f:


    pl "They do make all the machines the temple uses, after all."


translate English day7_rs_a5236e50:


    rs "But there is no one more amazing than Rose's brother."


translate English day7_rs_524277a9:


    rs "He is the most amazing person on the continent. Rose will not allow anyone to scorn him!"


translate English day7_rs_691d54b0:


    pl "Okay, I got it, I got it..."


translate English day7_rs_f016e33a:


    nar "Suddenly, I see someone. My feet stop moving.{w} It's Maya. It's not strange for her to be walking there, but why now, of all times?!"


translate English day7_rs_4ea99e1d:


    nar "I desperately search for an excuse, but in the end I just scoop up Rose and hide in an alley."


translate English day7_rs_80f936cc:


    nar "Eventually, she disappears.{w} I breathe a sigh of relief as Rose squirms in my arms using her fingers."


translate English day7_rs_3991fd43:


    pl "Oh, sorry. Someone I knew just passed by.{w} Um, you don't want anyone seeing you either, right?"


translate English day7_rs_b3535072:


    rs "Rose doesn't? Why not?"


translate English day7_rs_6245e330:


    pl "Well, because... Because you're supposed to be Lavi."


translate English day7_rs_e529fd40:


    pl "If you're out walking around without a care, it'll make problems for him."


translate English day7_rs_3ae413bb:


    rs "Rose mustn't make problems for her brother. She understands.{w} Rose will do her best not to stand out."


translate English day7_rs_4f505d84:


    pl "Glad you understand."


translate English day7_rs_d8132e15:


    rs "Were you thinking of his position too, [na]? Is that why you sheltered Rose?"


translate English day7_rs_ce3989ea:


    pl "Yeah, that too, but... Well, let's just leave it at that."


translate English day7_rs_f4fdc0a4:


    rs "It was the same yesterday."


translate English day7_rs_c8614925:


    pl "Yesterday? Oh, you mean Lavi.{w} In that situation, I had to do it. So yeah, just like that.{w} It was a bad situation."


translate English day7_rs_93fb2d7e:


    rs "A bad situation... Then when Rose is in a \"bad situation,\" you will shelter her like you're doing now?"


translate English day7_rs_65831f1e:


    pl "Well... If I can help, I will."


translate English day7_rs_3ecdee97_2:


    rs "......"


translate English day7_rs_5983eacb:


    pl "Okay, we're here. I can't go inside, so you'll have to get back to your room on your own. Will you be alright?"


translate English day7_rs_8eb24457:


    rs "Yes."


translate English day7_rs_2fa86357:


    pl "Don't go getting lost after confidence like that, okay?"


translate English day7_rs_1b92265c:


    rs "No problem."


translate English day7_rs_8224648d:


    pl "Good answer. Okay, bye-bye."


translate English day7_rs_3ecdee97_3:


    rs "......"


translate English day7_rs_537cdf24:


    pl "Hey, Rose? Where's my bye-bye?"


translate English day7_rs_111271ee:


    rs "Hm?{w} Oh... Bye-bye."


translate English day7_rs_6205c173:


    nar "As I walk towards the temple, looking back every so often, I never hear any footsteps coming from behind me."


translate English day7_rs_58329fb7:


    nar "I walk to the whole way to the temple with my head down."


translate English day7_rs_0cd18ae7:


    nar "Because I feel like if I look back now, I'll see Rose standing there, staring after me."


translate English day7_rs_5f46f39f:



    nvl clear
    "\n I have more time than I usually do just because I decided not to go to the library.{w} I mean, I could have just gone there and spent time with her like I usually do, though. I wonder why I didn't."


translate English day7_rs_38c09451:


    "In truth, I kind of understand the reason. I feel too guilty to say it outright, but it's because spending time with her is boring."


translate English day7_rs_b98f6dbf:


    et "That little room in the headache-inducing flower-scented library, where the only thing around are boring books.{w} The only reason I've been going to such a cramped little place and talking to this reticent girl who I have nothing in common with was pure curiosity."


translate English day7_rs_9e8bbd6c:



    nvl clear
    "\n And that mystique faded overnight.{w} Instead of someone who could guide me to a new adventure or explain the secrets of the Pestis to me, it was a normal girl I read uninteresting books with."


translate English day7_rs_592ce770:


    "A pathetic girl who left everything to her brother--he decided what friends she could talk to, planned her meals, and barely even let her leave the room.{w} With my curiosity gone, only sympathy is left."


translate English day7_rs_8740395c:


    et "I go straight back to my room without making any stops. I've always considered my room cramped, but compared to hers, it feels spacious."


translate English day7_rs_011bee00:



    nvl clear
    "\n Heaving a sigh, I lie down on the bed.{w} That's the moment her impassive face and tensed voice come to mind."


translate English day7_rs_423d44f6:


    "I understand she's trying to show me different sides of her. But in my head, her eyes are still black."


translate English day7_rs_d0a4470a:


    "Unblinking--like those of a farmer looking at livestock. Innocent eyes that could take lives."


translate English day7_rs_0387d984:


    "Maybe I'm still expecting something from her. Expecting another secret about the twins, one I don't know... It's a ridiculous notion."


translate English day7_rs_0fccf982:


    et "The temple's library drives people mad.{w} Probably because of the air of mystery the dim place has, plus the slight boredom and the mind-numbing smell..."


translate English day7_rs_76b69b1f:



    nvl clear
    "\n The smell... Come to think of it, the Academics Department bishop gave me some perfume the day I first went to the library. I haven't seen it at all since then.{w} Where did I put it?"


translate English day7_rs_b9c975b8:


    et "That's where I stop thinking. I think about where I left the perfume, but end up falling asleep without searching for it."


translate English day7_rs_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day8_rs_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day8_rs_28314e3e:



    nvl clear
    et "\n The angel obscured up my sin, made it so it didn't happen.{w} If everyone who knows about my crime stays quiet, will the truth disappear?"


translate English day8_rs_2de57bac:


    nar "Morning. Possibly thanks to going to sleep early, I feel like I slept really well."


translate English day8_rs_3eb433cb:


    nar "I go back through what happened yesterday.{w} I sent Rose back to the desk job team... And I was going to look for the perfume."


translate English day8_rs_9bbc91eb:


    nar "It doesn't feel right to just leave a gift I received sitting around in my room forever."


translate English day8_rs_581d638d:


    nar "Fortunately, I find it when I open the drawer. Naturally, it sparkles the same way it did when I first got it."


translate English day8_rs_d0076575:


    nar "The day I got this was the day I first met Rose. If I'd never opened that door that day..."


translate English day8_rs_65d2857f:


    nar "I stop thinking right there. I don't want to assign any meaning to a simple object."


translate English day8_rs_f95d6708:


    nar "It was also the worst day of my life, so I wish I could forget it."


translate English day8_rs_e7bb6c61:


    pl "Morning, Maya..."


translate English day8_rs_afaa912f:


    nar "Reservedly, I greet her. Maya, sitting in her seat, slowly turns and responds in a quiet voice."


translate English day8_rs_7a83f029:


    nar "She probably said \"good morning.\"{w} Like always."


translate English day8_rs_530eb07c:


    pl "How was work yesterday?"


translate English day8_rs_9b4a8b59:


    my "It was fine... It wasn't really work. All the tasks I get assigned are pointless..."


translate English day8_rs_305080dc:


    pl "Pointless?"


translate English day8_rs_119859a9:


    my "Yeah, like picking up garbage..."


translate English day8_rs_9003940b:


    pl "That's not pointless! That's important!"


translate English day8_rs_7480d2bb:


    my "...Maybe."


translate English day8_rs_63dc0996:


    pl "Well... Hey, about yesterday..."


translate English day8_rs_f3c23ffa:


    my "...What's that in your hand, [na2]?"


translate English day8_rs_468299bc:


    pl "Hm...? Oh, this? Something I got when I visited the library a few days ago."


translate English day8_rs_9e9b463d:


    my "You mean what you mentioned before...?"


translate English day8_rs_7310ae94:


    pl "Oh, right. I did tell you about it...{w} Maya, what kind of flower are irises?"


translate English day8_rs_eea8ede4:


    my "Irises... I actually looked them up after you mentioned them."


translate English day8_rs_4f964c98:


    my "They're flowers that look weak, but are really hardy when it comes to dry and cold weather..."


translate English day8_rs_ec2d4ff1:


    pl "Hardy...?"


translate English day8_rs_3f8c929e:


    my "It means they can live with no rain for a long time, and even when it's cold..."


translate English day8_rs_2e3eb878:


    my "They'll wither if a day goes by, so for a long time I only ever saw them in books. But apparently they've been discovered again recently."


translate English day8_rs_c2c2fee8:


    pl "Huh... So it's a pretty tough flower to get.{w} Where did that bishop even find something like this?"


translate English day8_rs_e9088785:


    my "Maybe she's raising them in the forest...?"


translate English day8_rs_57173c65:


    pl "The forest? You mean the one right by the temple?"


translate English day8_rs_9daaa044:


    my "Yeah. But I'm just guessing..."


translate English day8_rs_7ad32e37:


    my "The forests nearby are all the Academic Department's private property. I heard the priests there maintain it..."


translate English day8_rs_2d120d7f:


    my "The bishop seems especially fond of raising plants..."


translate English day8_rs_35df6dbc:


    pl "Really... So it's like the workplace for the Cleanup Department?{w} I guess when you're as important as them, you get a lot more land to work with."


translate English day8_rs_4f0700f4:


    my "...And the bishop of a department like that would have a lot of things she could give to people."


translate English day8_rs_c18acc44:


    nar "Gifts..."


translate English day8_rs_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day8_rs_b1a70137:


    my "...Oh, but I... I'm fine."


translate English day8_rs_508c333b:


    pl "Hm?"


translate English day8_rs_0b4373a7:


    my "You said before that you'd give it to me.{w} You've been worried about that, haven't you...? You've looked kind of uncomfortable this whole time..."


translate English day8_rs_9fc716c9:


    pl "Ah, no, that's... That's not exactly it..."


translate English day8_rs_61ca793b:


    my "I don't really need it since I'm in the Cleanup Department. You should do what you want with it, [na2]..."


translate English day8_rs_85e862d2:


    pl "Okay... Then I guess I'll look for someone else..."


translate English day8_rs_4892783c:


    my "...I wonder who it is you'd want to give this perfume to."


translate English day8_rs_8e59b5f3:


    pl "What? Maya, I literally just said I'll LOOK for someone.{w} Haha... It's not like a little perfume means much, right?"


translate English day8_rs_788ae3cb:


    my "Oh... I see."


translate English day8_rs_11d86f5d:



    nvl clear
    "\n Maya doesn't say any more. Soon, the bishop comes in and we do our morning greetings. Maya looks away from me the whole time."


translate English day8_rs_e9f91789:


    "We said bye to each other while leaving the room, but that was all. Everything should be going perfectly fine, but for some reason, I'm uneasy."


translate English day8_rs_ea29dce2:


    "Both men and women hate people wearing thick perfume.{w} I don't understand why you'd have to go beyond hiding your own scent and add some of your own as extra."


translate English day8_rs_608c9009:


    et "The smell of her perfume stays in a corner of my mind, always."


translate English day8_rs_491b720e:



    nvl clear
    "\n I can't remember what sort of smell it was.{w} It was a thick odor meant to cover up the stench of death seeped into her clothing, skin, and hair."


translate English day8_rs_d0c80897:


    "But I can definitely remember it all feeling so wrong I wanted to throw up."


translate English day8_rs_eb1c4bd5:


    "Finely crafted scents drive people crazy. The same goes for the Academics Department bishop. The smell of sweet milk given off by flowers, the wind, and by animals with soft flesh..."


translate English day8_rs_199228ee:


    et "They're artificial scents made for the sole purpose of seduction.{w} By the time I smelled her body odor once, my sense of smell had grown more sensitive than I ever wanted it to."


translate English day8_rs_7a85f9e0:



    nvl clear
    "\n At the moment, when I think of flowery smells, I think of lavender."


translate English day8_rs_84a8c17d:


    "It's far more fragrant than dead bodies like these are, but it also irritates the nerves and makes you want to vomit just as much as corpses do."


translate English day8_rs_8c3e0385:


    nar "After finishing work, I head to the library, which is kind of noisy for some reason.{w} I can't hear anyone talking, really, but the mood is different than usual."


translate English day8_rs_6ef5ea69:


    nar "I quickly find the reason behind it."


translate English day8_rs_be9bb265:


    nar "Rose, with the same short skirt and bared forehead she had yesterday, is sitting right there in the library reading a book."


translate English day8_rs_30d1ecc2:


    nar "The moment our eyes meet, my tensed body heats up all at once.{w} It's shame."


translate English day8_rs_ee8291fb:


    nar "I don't know why someone totally unconnected to this has to feel this way." with sshake


translate English day8_rs_4e8a15b4:


    nar "But before I think about it, I grab her hand and we go into her room."


translate English day8_rs_2705635a:


    nar "Rose is probably confused at why I didn't even say hello. And inside the room, writing into a book, is Lavien."


translate English day8_rs_4a224bb0:


    nar "I quickly close the door."


translate English day8_rs_e08ef500:


    rv "Oh? Hello, you two."


translate English day8_rs_0f4fd609:


    pl "Lavi..."


translate English day8_rs_abd708fe:


    rs "[na], your hand."


translate English day8_rs_9ad9338f:


    pl "Oh... Sorry."


translate English day8_rs_8354929c:


    rv "Is something the matter?"


translate English day8_rs_df169fb0:


    pl "Is... Why are you two in opposite places today?{w} Shouldn't Rose be in this room?"


translate English day8_rs_e509ae28:


    rv "Ahh... So that's why you were confused. I apologize for not explaining in advance."


translate English day8_rs_850648bd:


    rv "Rose came to me and asked if she could read a book in the library. So I just let her out of the room."


translate English day8_rs_0ac2729e:


    rv "There's no point in keeping her locked up in a little room like this, is there?"


translate English day8_rs_2d5e1ff7:


    pl "That's not the problem and you know it!" with sshake


translate English day8_rs_a4621121:


    rv "......"


translate English day8_rs_e39db1f5:


    rs "Rose needed information from a new book. The information she currently has is not enough to satisfy you, [na]."


translate English day8_rs_a51addbb:


    rs "So don't bully Rose's brother!" with sshake


translate English day8_rs_e2a692be:


    pl "Bully him? I'm just... I don't think it's good that you two are doing that kind of thing."


translate English day8_rs_e343ce92:


    rs "[na], do you not want Rose to go outside?"


translate English day8_rs_c1e3c2b0:


    pl "No, that's not it. It really isn't. It's just..."


translate English day8_rs_1f39ad98:


    rv "I think I understand what you're trying to say, Little [na]."


translate English day8_rs_189b952f:


    rv "I apologize for worrying you. And I thank you for putting so much thought into my position."


translate English day8_rs_dcef423e:


    rv "But this really is fine."


translate English day8_rs_1c09f055:


    pl "...But you have a lot of work to do in the temple, don't you? I mean, you're an auxiliary bishop and all..."


translate English day8_rs_e34ea21f:


    pl "I just don't think it's right for Rose to keep stealing your position. Not that I think either of you are to blame, of course."


translate English day8_rs_3b443ead:


    pl "It's just... It's weird. From the perspective of someone who knows what's going on."


translate English day8_rs_0a9143ce:


    rv "Hmm..."


translate English day8_rs_3b923594:


    pl "Lavi... You're smart. I know you get it.{w} You won't be able to hide such an obvious trick from the others in the temple."


translate English day8_rs_a34c4ecf:


    pl "People are already suspicious of you... Maybe it's time to think of a safer way. For Rose's sake."


translate English day8_rs_29f661ac:


    rv "I apologize in advance, because this is going to sound like an excuse."


translate English day8_rs_225c3f15:


    rv "It's not that I haven't thought about it. But there just isn't anything we can do right this instant."


translate English day8_rs_178e8db4:


    rv "The temple doesn't allow outsiders in--especially not the Academics Department."


translate English day8_rs_4609ec50:


    rv "Even the few previous examples weren't here on a near-permanent basis like Rose."


translate English day8_rs_7fab2fae:


    rv "As long as we don't have a way to prove that Rose won't misuse the Academics Department's information or be a security threat..."


translate English day8_rs_a54ea8da:


    rv "Sigh, and even if we could, she wouldn't be able to be a full-fledged priest like me."


translate English day8_rs_7fe1b3c7:


    pl "But there's gotta be another way. Like...{w} Having Rose join the Cleanup Department or something."


translate English day8_rs_e5eee35a:


    pl "Then she'd be a priest here too, and there wouldn't be a problem."


translate English day8_rs_e9bf72f9:


    rv "Thank you for the wonderful idea.{w} Actually, Lady Evelynn made the same offer."


translate English day8_rs_36771000:


    rv "But... Little [na], in your eyes, what is Rose like?"


translate English day8_rs_f749f728:


    rv "Would she be able to adapt to a new environment on her own and properly carry out the tasks assigned to her?"


translate English day8_rs_082d0846:


    pl "I... That's..."


translate English day8_rs_6c7f21f2:


    nar "That immediately shuts me up. I don't know what to say. I want to insist she'll be fine anyway, but I just can't."


translate English day8_rs_c80ec055:


    pl "She'll be okay... As long as she has someone to help her--no, wait... If we just believe in her..."


translate English day8_rs_027fa269:


    nar "I trail off as I talk."


translate English day8_rs_35f7a74e:


    nar "Reverentially, the reason I can say something like this--being an outsider--is because I'm ashamed to show my face to Rose and Lavi."


translate English day8_rs_9e5ef0d9:


    nar "I'm transferring to the Magic Department soon, so I won't be able to be with Rose forever."


translate English day8_rs_7f07cc52:


    nar "And with Lavi in a different apartment, it'll be hard for me to take care of her.{w} It takes at least twice as much effort for Rose to do something on her own as other people."


translate English day8_rs_5f0ed0ef:


    nar "Even now, she's just standing there, watching us talk and not understanding any of what's going on."


translate English day8_rs_5a690391:


    nar "Lavi doesn't answer, but he does give a bitter smile, as though recalling some bygone day I know nothing about."


translate English day8_rs_ef3299d5:


    rv "Thank you. You've already shown us far more kindness than we deserve."


translate English day8_rs_23c1d976:


    rv "You have no idea how grateful I am just to know you're thinking of us."


translate English day8_rs_dba52eea:


    pl "...I'm sorry."


translate English day8_rs_d6d4a5a0:


    rv "Once I've gotten enough money to live... I plan to leave the temple with Rose."


translate English day8_rs_9df3ab09:


    rv "I know this must all seem shameful, but I beg you to overlook it until that day comes."


translate English day8_rs_2e427b51:


    nar "But when will that be?{w} How long will this life be able to last? I swallow the questions down before they leave my mouth."


translate English day8_rs_ae53dc97:


    nar "One thing is clear now--that rather than suggesting any specific solutions, I need to think of ways to help them out in little ways."


translate English day8_rs_27aa6a06:


    nar "Some way to take the load off him, if even for a day.{w} Some way to let Rose have fun..."


translate English day8_rs_ef477aa5:


    pl "...Hey, what about this?"


translate English day8_rs_7fe5c5ce:


    pl "I'll take Rose out for a bit. Outside the temple, that is--where there's nobody who knows you."


translate English day8_rs_d18625ef:


    pl "And you could focus on your job during that time."


translate English day8_rs_2886a601:


    rv "You want to take her outside the temple...?"


translate English day8_rs_a45779c3:


    nar "Rose, who has been looking elsewhere this whole time, perks up and turns back to us, seeming interested."


translate English day8_rs_5c620387:


    pl "Yeah. I'm a newcomer here anyway. As long as I finish my morning work, I've got afternoons free."


translate English day8_rs_0a0c0514:


    pl "And I bet Rose wants to breathe the outside air once in a while too."


translate English day8_rs_14b3ca49:


    rv "I'd certainly be grateful if you'd do that, but... Are you sure it's okay for me to ask you for such a thing?"


translate English day8_rs_0e7f00b0:


    rv "The chances may be low, but if anyone sees you, it would put you in a bind, Little [na]..."


translate English day8_rs_a6ac0477:


    pl "No, it's no problem--I'm on the cleanup crew, after all!{w} The Cleanup Department always goes walking around outside--it's no big deal."


translate English day8_rs_a4621121_1:


    rv "......"


translate English day8_rs_125e95fd:


    rs "Are we going outside?"


translate English day8_rs_565d62ee:


    pl "That's right. And outside the temple, it's really, really big!"


translate English day8_rs_05189bfd:


    nar "Seeing Rose's enthusiasm, Lavi sinks into thought again."


translate English day8_rs_360cad40:


    nar "The attitude is more like he's taken aback by the sudden proposal than being particularly troubled or worried.{w} He glances at his sister, then lowers his gaze to the floor."


translate English day8_rs_cc17f645:


    nar "On the floor are books, papers, and the like that he probably put there for his work."


translate English day8_rs_539af85a:


    rv "Don't go too far out."


translate English day8_rs_c112e99c:


    pl "I won't. I've got a pretty good grasp on the local area."


translate English day8_rs_c10255b8:


    nar "Lavi removes the cross around his neck and holds it out as if to give it to me."


translate English day8_rs_e7a96d51:


    nar "The silver rosary hanging on a long chain has small letters engraved in it, just like mine."


translate English day8_rs_c2386fab:


    rv "If you're headed out, you'll need permission, so take my rosary with you."


translate English day8_rs_53f52036:


    rv "The one around Rose's neck is a fake I bought elsewhere."


translate English day8_rs_c4be0b40:


    pl "E-Even the rosary is fake...?{w} You're so careful, but so bold at the same time."


translate English day8_rs_ebf5b780:


    rv "I just painted a wooden one silver.{w} It looks like the real thing from far away, doesn't it?"


translate English day8_rs_7911357c:


    nar "After placing the rosary in my hand, Lavi goes over to his sister and gently takes off her necklace."


translate English day8_rs_8cfb23b3:


    nar "His movements are skillful, and he avoids touching her hairpin, her cheeks, or her nose at all."


translate English day8_rs_ad32fde4:


    nar "And then he takes a step back, as if it's someone else's turn. I step up and put the rosary on her."


translate English day8_rs_50bcbca0:


    nar "I try to copy how he does it, but my hands are shaking like crazy."


translate English day8_rs_9385e88e:


    nar "Perhaps sensing it, Rose reflexively shuts her eyes the moment my hands go past her ears."


translate English day8_rs_670e8ec8:


    nar "Then Lavi puts his sister's necklace on himself--the fake one that can't actually prove his position at the temple."


translate English day8_rs_d6988e9f:


    rv "I'll report it to the bishop and put this entire day down as a day off for me."


translate English day8_rs_94512318:


    rv "That way, even if someone sees me around the temple, I'll be safe."


translate English day8_rs_a6cf8db3:


    pl "You're taking off?"


translate English day8_rs_e97e621c:


    rv "It works the same as in the Cleanup Department.{w} Anyone who has been working here for at least a year gets fifteen sick days starting the following year."


translate English day8_rs_cc4bf25b:


    rv "I'm not taking the day off so much as staying out of sight and handling the work that's piled up, though..."


translate English day8_rs_030f14c7:


    pl "Is there even a point then...?"


translate English day8_rs_a0b23e0b:


    rv "There is indeed. As long as I get everything done quickly, I'll actually have some free time."


translate English day8_rs_937dacde:


    rv "And it's all thanks to you, Little [na]. Thank you so, so much."


translate English day8_rs_9117656d:


    pl "Well... If you say so, I guess."


translate English day8_rs_046d5ac3:


    nar "Taking the uncharacteristically excited Rose's hand, I leave the room with the same quick steps I entered with."


translate English day8_rs_ca190619:


    nar "Before opening the door, I feel like maybe I'm sticking my neck in where it's not needed."


translate English day8_rs_f6ecedef:


    nar "But Rose is already holding my hand."


translate English day8_rs_ac94420b:


    nar "And Lavi is already seeing us out with a plastered on smile."


translate English day8_rs_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day8_rs_8a7c7dbb:


    "\n Rose does a good job keeping up with me, but sometimes she falls a couple steps behind. It feels like walking while pulling a large cart."


translate English day8_rs_983026b2:


    et "I keep my mouth shut the entire time--as we get out of the temple where nobody can see us, as the inspector verifies Rose's permission when we go through the checkpoint, as the two of us are looked up and down. Rose's unsociable attitude comes in handy at times like these."


translate English day8_rs_20a9da5a:



    nvl clear
    "\n The first thing I do once we get down into town is buy a wide-brimmed straw hat for Rose and put it on her.{w} Just in case anyone happens to know Lavien's face."


translate English day8_rs_c9bcfc33:


    et "For once, the skies of the ever-bright, never-setting midnight sun feel good.{w} That's because I wanted to show Rose a white sky with the bright sun in it, rather than all the dark clouds, since we're here anyway."


translate English day8_rs_837eff30:



    nvl clear
    "\n Black air drifts through the sky as usual, but it's much clearer and brighter than the enclosed library's ceiling. It's a good thing I made her wear that hat."


translate English day8_rs_cb91dede:


    et "The midafternoon sun is stronger than usual, and Rose's pale hands are turning red.{w} Rose in the sunlight--I almost feel like I'm dreaming, even though she's right there."


translate English day8_rs_3e443c0b:



    nvl clear
    "\n Rose stays mostly quiet while looking around town too. She used to live in a village closer to the capital than me, so I guess that's normal.{w} Maybe I was unconsciously looking down on her again."


translate English day8_rs_70839f4a:


    et "She doesn't act crazy and energetic like the characters in books, but I think she's having fun gazing at the buildings and letting the wind blow by her. Seeing her enjoy herself makes me enjoy myself."


translate English day8_rs_8204a631:


    rs "[na], Rose cannot see in front of her."


translate English day8_rs_cb030204:


    pl "Your bangs would have been worse."


translate English day8_rs_332fb83c:


    nar "With the midpoint of afternoon work hours at the temple coming up, I slip out of town and take the hat off Rose's head."


translate English day8_rs_b5bf783b:


    nar "Her scruffy bangs hang down to her nose."


translate English day8_rs_0f7cf42b:


    pl "You really don't want to buy a book or anything?"


translate English day8_rs_56699df2:


    rs "Rose hasn't finished reading the ones she has now."


translate English day8_rs_b71b32b0:


    pl "I thought you read them all over and over again."


translate English day8_rs_05e52641:


    rs "As Rose explained before, simple information gathering does not lead to complete understanding."


translate English day8_rs_144adff5:


    pl "Oh, well... If you say so. Anywhere else you want to go?"


translate English day8_rs_9b856cc0:


    rs "The forest."


translate English day8_rs_efdc2b4b:


    pl "The forest?{w} But you go there... Oh."


translate English day8_rs_036a9faf:


    rs "Because Rose is not a member of the Academics Department, she is not permitted to thoughtlessly go outside, even if she stays in the temple."


translate English day8_rs_65f984c0:


    nar "Rose's voice is as monotone as ever, but that just makes it seem sadder. I didn't want to make her repeat all this."


translate English day8_rs_0832dc40:


    pl "I got it... I guess we can go to the forest.{w} But don't get lost, alright?"


translate English day8_rs_058653a8:


    rs "Rose understands."


translate English day8_rs_30c2bbca:


    nar "I actually want to stay in town a little longer, but that wouldn't be considerate of Rose's position."


translate English day8_rs_e655aae3:


    nar "I go through the forest every day, but it probably means something different for her."


translate English day8_rs_579aa3f1:


    nar "The two of us walk down a forest path close to the temple.{w} In a way, it's just our return trip."


translate English day8_rs_ae643dee:


    nar "Feeling like the mood is right, I take the perfume out of my pocket."


translate English day8_rs_4445c1a0:


    pl "Rose, you can have this."


translate English day8_rs_8db117aa:


    rs "Perfume?"


translate English day8_rs_5cf94939:


    pl "Yeah. I got it in the library you live in."


translate English day8_rs_a45ffd27:


    rs "Ah... Rose smells Lady Evelynn..."


translate English day8_rs_36f29753:


    pl "Do you not like her?"


translate English day8_rs_664a83df:


    rs "Rose hates her.{w} Rose hates anyone who bullies her brother."


translate English day8_rs_5d089567:


    pl "She's probably just giving him work, you know, not bullying him."


translate English day8_rs_182ce9d7:


    rs "Rose knows.{w} Rose's brother always tells Rose to be grateful to Lady Evelynn."


translate English day8_rs_34da1cd6:


    rs "He says that it's all thanks to her I can be at the temple...{w} But the work torments him and makes him busy."


translate English day8_rs_b79aa2e6:


    pl "But it's thank to his work that he gets to be an auxiliary bishop."


translate English day8_rs_677013a8:


    rs "Auxiliary Bishop--is that a good thing?{w} People are always saying mean things about him because he's an auxiliary bishop."


translate English day8_rs_e65ea8a2:


    rs "They say he makes the Academics Department look bad. Just for being a little late or for having a little bit of grease on his hands."


translate English day8_rs_a9954086:


    rs "Rose hates them.{w} Rose wants to kill them. Rose will kill them..."


translate English day8_rs_18f11959:


    pl "...How did you two end up coming to the temple?"


translate English day8_rs_13b002bb:


    rs "Rose's knowledge is extremely limited."


translate English day8_rs_14c8bfd8:


    rs "Rose knows only that her brother is a very talented individual and that Lady Evelynn is giving us assistance."


translate English day8_rs_b9a67c45:


    pl "Oh... Then Lavi's really working his hardest, without resting at all, just to make sure you're healthy."


translate English day8_rs_f5dc4a8f:


    rs "Is it Rose's fault?"


translate English day8_rs_8b9e6816:


    pl "No, it's... I didn't mean it like that... What I mean is that Lavien is a really good brother."


translate English day8_rs_17e44e52:


    rs "Rose's brother is the greatest.{w} Rose has lived alone with him since she was little."


translate English day8_rs_b1765791:


    rs "We apparently had parents long ago, but Rose does not possess memories from that time."


translate English day8_rs_42cf5671:


    rs "But Rose's brother has worked hard so that we can live together."


translate English day8_rs_f1aa02b1:


    pl "Haha... Then I guess you should repay him somehow too, for how wonderful he is."


translate English day8_rs_b50da9b2:


    rs "Repay... Yeah. Rose wants to be helpful to her brother too."


translate English day8_rs_31927c1d:


    rs "But he says that Rose being healthy, safe, and happy is the same as her being helpful."


translate English day8_rs_cde20a5c:


    pl "...Then you absolutely have to stay that way, right?"


translate English day8_rs_a2c1cecf:


    rs "...But--"


translate English day8_rs_c1789e4b:


    pl "Hey, look, Rose!{w} Look at the pretty flower growing over there."


translate English day8_rs_e3115d92:


    nar "I purposely look away and towards a wildflower growing at an odd height atop a cliff. I wanted to escape her gaze."


translate English day8_rs_d38a975f:


    rs "Flowers..."


translate English day8_rs_e4e77f54:


    pl "There's only one of them around... Doesn't that make you feel good?"


translate English day8_rs_3aaa66bd:


    rs "Yes. Rose feels good."


translate English day8_rs_17edd7f2:


    pl "That's good.{w} I was worried you didn't like flowers much."


translate English day8_rs_f902dab3:


    rs "You talk a lot about flowers, [na]."


translate English day8_rs_2abbf11b:


    pl "Oh... Do I? Probably because I'm friends with someone who likes flowers."


translate English day8_rs_0953300d:


    rs "Rose will treasure this gift. Thank you."


translate English day8_rs_92a5bc37:


    pl "You're welcome. We should be getting back, Princess."


translate English day8_rs_c2d4732f:


    rs "Princess?"


translate English day8_rs_428afbec:


    pl "...That just kinda felt like good word to use. You can ignore me."


translate English day8_rs_a1151c37:


    rs "Rose is a princess?{w} Really?"


translate English day8_rs_648d686f:


    pl "Quit it, you're being embarrassing!"


translate English day8_rs_b11107db:


    nar "After that, I bring Rose to the Academics Department and part ways with her."


translate English day8_rs_99df2e17:


    nar "I consider stopping by the library, but I don't want to get in Lavi's way when he's probably really focused."


translate English day8_rs_de5783c4:


    nar "All the day's exhaustion sweeps through me at once. I feel heavy."


translate English day8_rs_b91f2194:


    nar "Rose carefully cradled the little bottle in both hands all the way until she went into her dorm.{w} I figured she'd hate that smell."


translate English day8_rs_97391736:


    nar "Since it was originally a gift from Lady Evelynn and all. But she didn't seem to mind it that much."


translate English day8_rs_efc391ce:


    nar "Watching her made me vaguely realize why I'd hesitated to give it to Maya instead."


translate English day8_rs_463a60a1:


    nar "It wasn't just an object--it was a gift, and gifts have meaning."


translate English day8_rs_b67ce18e:


    nar "After showering and returning to the dorm, I lie down in bed to go to sleep."


translate English day8_rs_ef847c0c:


    nar "Time flies by when I'm with Rose, but for some reason, I can't remember a thing we talked about."


translate English day8_rs_eb3bcdbb:


    nar "Probably because she doesn't say much."


translate English day8_rs_bf39f1f8:


    nar "I always had these crazy ideas about Rose being uniquely mysterious."


translate English day8_rs_e3b08f29:


    nar "But it's probably just because she doesn't talk very much."


translate English day8_rs_d46a5ff1:


    nar "...*knock knock*"


translate English day8_rs_c7db01ee:


    pl "...?"


translate English day8_rs_a3a84cc2:


    pl "...Whoa! Lavi?!" with sshake


translate English day8_rs_d35e61b5:


    rv "I... I'm sorry for visiting this late.{w} Little [na], is Rose here, by any chance?"


translate English day8_rs_b1b2ead7:


    pl "Rose? No, she's not... Why, did something happen?"


translate English day8_rs_a4ea63db:


    rv "After I made sure she got back to the dorm, I accidentally dozed off. And when I woke up, she was nowhere to be found..."


translate English day8_rs_969fdd0b:


    rv "My permit is gone too, so I thought she might have gone outside the temple."


translate English day8_rs_c6c219ca:


    rv "But embarrassingly enough, I don't know much about what kinds of places Rose might go..."


translate English day8_rs_b6f35ac0:


    rv "And now I don't have my permit. I have to help her somehow, though..."


translate English day8_rs_ae3eb801:


    pl "Alright. Just have to look in places she's likely to be, right? I'll get ready, so wait a sec for me."


translate English day8_rs_11b775e7:


    rv "I'm truly, truly sorry about this..."


translate English day8_rs_dafb26c7:


    nar "In front of the temple, as Lavi goes to step straight towards the checkpoint without hesitation, I call out to stop him."


translate English day8_rs_a971bb87:


    pl "Hey, wait a minute! You can't go!" with sshake


translate English day8_rs_d8ed936b:


    rv "What?"


translate English day8_rs_74c1150b:


    pl "Not only do you not have your permit, but Rose has already gone through here. If they see you going out the checkpoint too..."


translate English day8_rs_875cc6ae:


    pl "Oh, I know. Why don't we wait for them to change shifts?"


translate English day8_rs_487297b8:


    rv "Then it will be far too late!{w} This is my responsibility. It's my fault this happened...!" with sshake


translate English day8_rs_f7158c04:


    pl "It's not your fault. Rose left on her own, right?"


translate English day8_rs_9793c788:


    rv "Rose isn't to blame.{w} Must we force my precious Rose to wander around by herself until late at night...?"


translate English day8_rs_9697461f:


    rv "Please. Don't accuse Rose of a crime. She's just a poor girl."


translate English day8_rs_18480174:


    rv "Tortured just for being born, discriminated against, and now she's lost her way... And it's all because I brought her to the temple..."


translate English day8_rs_7152a963:


    pl "Could you just calm down for a second...?{w} You did everything you were supposed to as her brother. You dedicated your life to her."


translate English day8_rs_5bfaa437:


    pl "And if you want someone to blame, I'm the one who took her out into town today..."


translate English day8_rs_5d027dd4:


    rv "No...!{w} No, I could never do that! I knew that if you took care of Rose, I'd..." with sshake


translate English day8_rs_097fa6d1:


    rv "I'd get a few hours of rest, at least. That's the only reason I allowed it."


translate English day8_rs_aa1f6384:


    rv "You suggested what you did out of pure goodwill towards Rose, and yet I've...{w} Ah, my lord... I'm sorry, Rose..."


translate English day8_rs_6cdde751:


    pl "Get a grip, would you?!{w} It's because you only think about that stuff that Rose became unable to leave!" with sshake


translate English day8_rs_a4621121_2:


    rv "......"


translate English day8_rs_c4def0b7:


    pl "...*sigh* From my point of view, you haven't gotten any rest at all."


translate English day8_rs_20d96d0b:


    pl "And yet you still do nothing but work. You're crazy, you know that?"


translate English day8_rs_b1af7f15:


    pl "Is it so wrong to want to rest?{w} Look, just stay here and wait. And stop thinking about dumb stuff!"


translate English day8_rs_a4621121_3:


    rv "......"


translate English day8_rs_3fe44b87:


    nar "My face white, I leave the downcast Lavi behind and exit the temple."


translate English day8_rs_cec0e664:


    nar "It's really fortunate the road isn't dark, because my mood is dark enough as I retrace the steps Rose and I took through the forest."


translate English day8_rs_075c0f34:


    nar "It's less fear than anxiety--and less anxiety than annoyance.{w} I didn't think Lavien would be so out of sorts."


translate English day8_rs_02284a72:


    nar "He treated me like an outsider so much. Why'd he get me wrapped up in all this?"


translate English day8_rs_732642f2:


    nar "If I'm too late to return, the dorms will be locked up, too."


translate English day8_rs_c025eba2:


    nar "Even now that I'm in this situation, I'm surprised at how I'm worrying about my own affairs."


translate English day8_rs_3d7d6018:


    nar "In fact, I want to stop right here and give myself a punch in the cheek or head. I don't have time to, though."


translate English day8_rs_b38dd714:


    nar "For now, I have to put Rose's safety first in my mind."


translate English day8_rs_4d479a80:


    nar "If... If Rose is hurt or something, then I...{w} I..."


translate English day8_rs_669bb0bf:


    nar "......"


translate English day8_rs_742d6873:


    rs "[na]."


translate English day8_rs_eb9f8236:


    pl "Whoa!" with sshake


translate English day8_rs_345669ba:


    nar "As I was standing there, a voice addressed me."


translate English day8_rs_2959d505:


    nar "When I turned around, thinking I'd scold her, I found myself at a loss for words."


translate English day8_rs_dee875e3:


    nar "She's an absolute mess."


translate English day8_rs_4d16e03d:


    nar "She's not visibly wounded, but straw and dirt are stuck in her hair. She looks like a giant fur ball."


translate English day8_rs_0f2e1fe0:


    nar "Even the hair and clothes her brother had so thoughtfully helped her with are a mess--it was like she'd gone to sleep in the filthiest place she could find."


translate English day8_rs_f27d2fed:


    nar "Now, she resembles the wild side of nature itself."


translate English day8_rs_8d38cb45:


    pl "Rose, you... What were you...?"


translate English day8_rs_f362b3bd:


    rs "Here."


translate English day8_rs_c915d3d5:


    pl "...A flower?"


translate English day8_rs_3d003a1f:


    rs "[na] gave Rose a present.{w} So Rose is repaying you. You said this flower was pretty, so..."


translate English day8_rs_db39b131:


    rs "Is that wrong?"


translate English day8_rs_95c6b324:


    pl "Hah... Ha ha ha. Thank you..."


translate English day8_rs_9185dcbe:


    nar "I fake a laugh.{w} It's just a wildflower--nothing special about it. An ugly wildflower I don't even know the name of--nor do I want to."


translate English day8_rs_78cc9e60:


    nar "Rose seriously accepted the meaning I randomly assigned it."


translate English day8_rs_aa4e381c:


    nar "All I wanted to do was look somewhere else and end that conversation. I didn't care how it happened."


translate English day8_rs_ff555ebb:


    nar "I didn't want to get any more involved in whatever is going on with these siblings."


translate English day8_rs_dcfb9e17:


    nar "I'm fully aware Rose likes me a lot, but I wanted to ignore it."


translate English day8_rs_d31bf7b2:


    pl "...Rose, what happened to your leg?"


translate English day8_rs_f36ec8ab:


    rs "Rose's leg?"


translate English day8_rs_d8fa8473:


    pl "Stay still for a minute."


translate English day8_rs_df75b344:


    nar "Rose is dragging one of her legs.{w} In haste, I take her shoe off. My throat is parched."


translate English day8_rs_72b25d15:


    nar "The ominous feeling I've had since this morning is about to rear its ugly head.{w} I want to hand Rose off to Lavi RIGHT NOW and get back to my dorm room."


translate English day8_rs_92ed76a9:


    nar "I feel like I NEED to do so.{w} Before I come face to face with something I regret."


translate English day8_rs_91b6c4ec:


    rs "[na]?"


translate English day8_rs_ca3c0d68:


    nar "Pressured by her voice saying my name as if to rush me, I take her sock off with my stiff hands."


translate English day8_rs_a9451a9a:


    nar "At the same time, my crouched-over back goes limp, and I sit down."


translate English day8_rs_50516b81:


    nar "There's a black mark on what should be pure white skin."


translate English day8_rs_a48a7f33:


    nar "It wasn't there when I first saw her bare skin.{w} I smell something familiar from that little foot of hers--a smell I was never supposed to smell."


translate English day8_rs_9f3b45d4:


    nar "My vision darkens."


translate English day8_rs_3ecdee97:


    rs "......"


translate English day8_rs_8f8891fc:


    nar "Rose looks at me from above. Seeming confused, she puts her arms around me."


translate English day8_rs_7aeea190:


    nar "As she embraces me, all around us is silence. Terrifying, horrific silence."


translate English day8_rs_388794aa:


    nar "No birds chirp. Not even the wind blows.{w} Not even her heart beats, perhaps."


translate English day8_rs_4b6907ad:


    nar "Lavi, hiding somewhere nobody would find to question him, cries out as soon as he sees the two of us."


translate English day8_rs_cf44b4a2:


    nar "Without scolding or moaning over Rose, he thanks me over and over."


translate English day8_rs_538935cb:


    nar "Afraid of him finding Rose's wound, I carry her back to their dorm."


translate English day8_rs_53c48d65:


    nar "I told Rose absolutely never to tell anyone about it, but I think maybe, deep down, she understands."


translate English day8_rs_0650fbc9:


    nar "Lavi tells me many things before we part."


translate English day8_rs_a48498af:


    rv "I'm terribly sorry for all the trouble we've caused you today.{w} And once again, I sincerely thank you."


translate English day8_rs_c663dadf:


    rv "I was about to have a lapse in judgment and commit a grave error."


translate English day8_rs_23a7f756:


    pl "Well, nobody can blame you for being worried for your only sister. Don't worry about it."


translate English day8_rs_34b72c15:


    rv "To tell the truth... Rose has snuck out without me knowing before."


translate English day8_rs_99fff5b2:


    rv "Whether she didn't like me never resting, or just wanted to help me...{w} She went into the storehouse and broke all the machines inside."


translate English day8_rs_45e183ea:


    rv "I don't need anything more than Rose's safe homecoming, but it is still somewhat worrying..."


translate English day8_rs_45a35bc3:


    pl "...Hey, um, Rose... Who is she, really?{w} Is this how she's always been?"


translate English day8_rs_23a66b7f:


    rv "Rose is... How should I explain this? To put it simply, she's a Pestis victim."


translate English day8_rs_59d5c798:


    rv "All children in waste districts are alienated from the Lord's blessing, so each of them is born with a curse."


translate English day8_rs_6998c540:


    rv "I was lucky and was born without its influence on me. But Rose was not so fortunate."


translate English day8_rs_fc68d298:


    pl "Lucky, huh..."


translate English day8_rs_e0844feb:


    rv "Yes. I alone received of the Lord's protection.{w} And if I have some heavenly mandate from the God who has taken my side..."


translate English day8_rs_92283d3a:


    rv "I believe it's to devote myself to Rose--because I'm all she has."


translate English day8_rs_eb1e660c_1:


    pl "......"


translate English day8_rs_f90ad830:


    rv "Ahh... I apologize. The conversation has become depressing again."


translate English day8_rs_b8c0506b:


    rv "But Rose is alright now because she doesn't only have me anymore--she has you too."


translate English day8_rs_e247cd49:


    nar "I should never have taken Rose out with me."


translate English day8_rs_8b46a985:


    nar "I should never have met her to begin with.{w} When Lavi gave me that opportunity to leave her in my past, I should have said yes and left."


translate English day8_rs_c28656e3:


    nar "And no matter how I think about it, all I have is grief towards my own circumstances now."


translate English day8_rs_20963141:


    nar "I get back to my room fine, but I can't fall asleep. I just put my hands together and pray to the angel all night long."


translate English day8_rs_573de63c:


    nar "Pray for her to be at my side once again, pray for her to put me back on the right path, pray for her to grant me enlightenment in the wake of my foolishness..."


translate English day8_rs_1405cf1a:


    nar "But the angel doesn't respond.{w} And so the night passes."


translate English day8_rs_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_rs_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_rs_8a3c0aad:



    nvl clear
    "\n I don't get a wink of sleep all night."


translate English day9_rs_8bc62535:


    "Whenever I closed my eyes, I'd see Rose's black wound in the darkness. Unease and worry would spring from it, clinging to my mind. I wonder if Rose is still asleep. If she gets changed, they'll see the wound right away."


translate English day9_rs_559d18c6:


    "Lavi was incredibly out of sorts just from his sister's disappearance. If he knew about this, would he take revenge against me?"


translate English day9_rs_caa9d904:


    et "Or would he blame it all on me and be crippled for life?{w} Either way would be scary."


translate English day9_rs_a0683c1c:



    nvl clear
    "\n And when those wild imaginings crossed my mind, my hands would naturally join together, seeing no choice but to cling to God for help. I spent the entire night imagining every possible thing I can think of."


translate English day9_rs_ec9ea0e3:


    et "Sometimes I would cry, thinking about how unfortunate it was that this happened to someone, unable to even lie down, just staring at the door. Because I was so sure that the moment I let myself relax, even a little, would be the moment someone knocked."


translate English day9_rs_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_rs_9ebf818e:


    "\n When the slightly darker blue skies of night finally give way to the white of day, I realize morning has come, and I leave. With the wind hitting my cracked eyelids, I go to a sink nobody is using and wash my face."


translate English day9_rs_ffb3ef92:


    et "In the mirror, my face is haggard. White keratin is now on my lips because I was biting them all night, and dark purple wrinkles tug at my eyes.{w} I can feel it--there's no doubt. She's stealing away my youth."


translate English day9_rs_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_rs_5b059ab9:


    "\n When I arrive, the department room is empty."


translate English day9_rs_e6a661e5:


    "I'm used to seeing it empty, but it makes me feel weird to see it at this time of day. The key was behind a picture frame on the wall."


translate English day9_rs_6f4ceb0a:


    et "When Securett told me about it, I figured I'd never need to remember it, since I was going to be late all the time anyway...{w} And now I'm having the experience of getting here first--an experience I probably never would have had were it not for Rose."


translate English day9_rs_7cebe452:



    nvl clear
    "\n Apparently, I accidentally fell asleep face-down on my desk after coming in.{w} Eventually the room grows louder until I hear the bishop's languid greeting. Someone talks to me at some point, but I still don't wake up."


translate English day9_rs_bd21818d:


    et "My head is way too jumbled to let anyone else's words through, and I'm not confident I can hold a conversation."


translate English day9_rs_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_rs_7d505051:


    "\n Naturally, I can't focus on my work, either. For some reason, the stench of death I thought I'd long since gotten used to seems way worse than other days, and it makes me continuously throw up onto the floors I just cleaned."


translate English day9_rs_b6432783:


    "The bathroom is hell now, with the stench of rotted corpses mixed with that of vomit."


translate English day9_rs_94c64618:


    et "As I hold my stomach and continue to throw up, the sweet scene in the library flashes before my eyes."


translate English day9_rs_e88a1fe7:



    nvl clear
    "\n It's better when it's an animal's corpse you have to clean up.{w} Today, a cat died. Ravaged by wind and rain, it was stiff, staring up at the sky from its spot in the grass."


translate English day9_rs_dbd341aa:


    "It's in relatively good condition, but its hair has fallen out in clumps in places and the skin I can see underneath is so thin now I can see its bones. I'd bet it starved to death. Its two eyes are withered like a couple of overripe peaches, which again reminds me of Rose."


translate English day9_rs_4dec160c:


    et "I can't believe myself for seeing her in an animal that's died a long death."


translate English day9_rs_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_rs_4b315b4b:


    "\n I've got it bad.{w} While I know now that Rose is a human just like me, I've unconsciously been thinking of her as something else."


translate English day9_rs_e15ef273:


    et "On my way back, I keep apologizing to her in my head.{w} \"I'm sorry, Rose.\""


translate English day9_rs_c1adbb3f:


    nar "When I open the door to the quiet department room, I see the bishop.{w} I feel awkward, probably because I've been avoiding talking to her lately."


translate English day9_rs_fe776cbd:


    hk "Oh, what's this? Thank you for your hard work, Brother."


translate English day9_rs_d4b155e5:


    pl "It's not often you're in the department room this late, Bishop."


translate English day9_rs_5ac82c24:


    hk "Yes, I had a bit of an errand to run, and I decided to enjoy the silence after it was done."


translate English day9_rs_273e4ebb:


    pl "By yourself?"


translate English day9_rs_e0fefeeb:


    hk "Yes, by myself~"


translate English day9_rs_a6cbe0b6:


    extend "My goodness... What a dirty thing to ask~"


translate English day9_rs_ef47398b:


    pl "I thought you were a bishop. You can't be joking so lewdly like that..."


translate English day9_rs_ddad69c1:


    nar "Leaving the smiling bishop behind, I walk to the back of the room."


translate English day9_rs_da317a91:


    nar "The moment I open up my locker to put my tools away, a dark shadow falls overhead, blocking my view." with sshake


translate English day9_rs_dfa513e7:


    nar "Something cold and wet dampens my face, and a cloth that tastes like dirt falls into my gaping mouth."


translate English day9_rs_ec2af6a6:


    nar "Compared to the disgust, the actual pain of it hitting me is nothing."


translate English day9_rs_312f7747:


    nar "It's a mop that was standing straight up.{w} Obviously, I'm not the one who put it in there."


translate English day9_rs_e6ec1b3d:


    nar "Someone else must have, once they were finished working--the cloth is still dripping with muddy, black water--someone's dregs from the workday."


translate English day9_rs_a9cc8204:


    nar "The stench of waste water assails my nose."


translate English day9_rs_4dbbfbd5:


    hk "Are you all right~?"


translate English day9_rs_0dfa5e1a:


    nar "The voice from behind me is as slow and relaxed as always."


translate English day9_rs_d434d85f:


    hk "Ah, it seems to be a malicious prank."


translate English day9_rs_1281abcd:


    nar "She's right--it's just a prank. The kind of juvenile one a little kid might think up."


translate English day9_rs_bff895c4:


    nar "However much malice was intended, it's only a prank."


translate English day9_rs_d8c450be:


    nar "But its simplicity makes it pretty clear what the culprit meant by it."


translate English day9_rs_0171758f:


    nar "A warning--a message that they don't want me as part of their crowd."


translate English day9_rs_918ff46e:


    pl "I guess when you're someone like me, you gotta expect this stuff..."


translate English day9_rs_f495fc72:


    hk "Hmmm~?"


translate English day9_rs_e38bd50e:


    pl "I mean, I'd love to just disappear if I could for you all, but..."


translate English day9_rs_7e37ab1f:


    pl "These jerks may all hate me, but I'm the one who knows my problems best, you know!"


translate English day9_rs_cc96625f:


    hk "What in the world has you lamenting your life, Brother?"


translate English day9_rs_f503e610:


    pl "Everything! It just seems like I'm doing everything wrong.{w} I don't want to die--I just want to disappear."


translate English day9_rs_761ac1ed:


    hk "Because you believe you need to?"


translate English day9_rs_46fade45:


    pl "Yeah. I mean, it's not like I'm thinking this way because I want to or something."


translate English day9_rs_aecdd81c:


    pl "All of the incidents and accidents have me right in the middle. It's like every situation I run into is telling me to go die in a ditch."


translate English day9_rs_706ae303:


    pl "And I don't want to die!!!" with sshake


translate English day9_rs_7444f3fc:


    hk "Even if you disappeared and everything went back to normal, your sins wouldn't disappear."


translate English day9_rs_17e803aa:


    pl "Sins...?{w} What the hell brought that on, anyway?{w} You know something, don't you. You do!!!"


translate English day9_rs_4678260d:


    hk "I do not.{w} Naturally it's because you've never confessed them."


translate English day9_rs_44204d74:


    pl "...Well, I don't have any.{w} None at all."


translate English day9_rs_9959177f:


    hk "Well, alright. That is quite fine."


translate English day9_rs_f6cab1a5:


    hk "You cannot speak to that which you do not have, so I'd like you to keep one piece of advice in mind."


translate English day9_rs_7fa4d714:


    hk "A sin, when left unspoken, is like a trace amount of poison."


translate English day9_rs_92a75fe5:


    hk "It may seem like you've digested it properly, but it will slowly build up in your body and eventually cause you to die."


translate English day9_rs_63524a27:


    pl "Even if that's true, if someone's gonna get hurt if I so much as open my mouth, I shouldn't say anything..."


translate English day9_rs_1c96140b:


    hk "Then it isn't a sin you won't confess, but a sin you cannot confess... People refer to those as \"secrets.\""


translate English day9_rs_055bafd7:


    hk "Indeed--and it is said everyone has secrets~"


translate English day9_rs_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_rs_f9c292d5:


    hk "However, Brother, just because it is the case for everyone does not mean you must conform."


translate English day9_rs_1720a316:


    hk "Just because there is someone you respect does not mean that everyone leads that sort of life..."


translate English day9_rs_56178735:


    nar "Her eyes are mysterious. I'm sure they're looking at me, but they also seem unfocused, like they're gazing in a completely different direction."


translate English day9_rs_ba2440a6:


    nar "The longer I stare into her eyes, the stronger that sense becomes."


translate English day9_rs_d87e6edc:


    pl "...Ha ha. I have no idea what you're talking about, Bishop."


translate English day9_rs_c369b3c1:


    pl "If there's any sins here, it would be on the jerks who did this to me, right? Not me."


translate English day9_rs_4bfaa28b:


    pl "Or do you want me to confess to a sin that doesn't exist?"


translate English day9_rs_e33c0ee3:


    hk "Hmmm... I suppose you're right~{w} I have truly been quite rude..."


translate English day9_rs_b81a5b0f:


    nar "Her eyes, narrowed gently, stare at me calmly. Finally, I feel like we're actually seeing eye to eye again."


translate English day9_rs_4b41628d:


    hk "I do have a hobby of hearing confessions of sins that don't--or rather, should not exist..."


translate English day9_rs_857e2dfc:


    nar "Without saying another word, I uncomfortably leave the room.{w} She stays just as quiet as me."


translate English day9_rs_ad31c939:


    nar "I don't even turn back, either. We pass by each other as though we're not even here."


translate English day9_rs_836a20b2:


    nar "But not for long. I speed up and begin to run.{w} My formless thoughts are exploding in my mind, throwing me into utter disarray."


translate English day9_rs_349d880e:


    nar "I needed to forget about \"that\"...{w} But like the angel said, \"that\" never happened."


translate English day9_rs_f0bb9249:


    nar "Just as the angel dictated..."


translate English day9_rs_f7bb9f2e:


    nar "I run in a daze until eventually I come to the infirmary. The lights are off inside, but the door is open like it usually is."


translate English day9_rs_7aa2aa47:


    nar "In my memories, the infirmary always smelled good. But today it smells like dull soot and smoke."


translate English day9_rs_5bde844a:


    nar "I push the door all the way open and hear someone inside quickly moving a chair.{w} A moment or two later, the lights turn on."


translate English day9_rs_1158e057:


    gr "...You surprised me. Is that you, [na2]?"


translate English day9_rs_863eb72f:


    pl "Th-That's my line...{w} What were you doing in here with the lights off?"


translate English day9_rs_c4916c1f:


    gr "Hm? Well, I was..."


translate English day9_rs_42c9ada7:


    gr "I was doing some thinking.{w} It's easier to focus when it's dark, right? Ahaha..."


translate English day9_rs_78bff70b:


    pl "Is that right...? Well, I actually came because there was something I wanted to ask. But if I'm bothering you..."


translate English day9_rs_d0e3fab8:


    gr "No, not at all. I've just about finished up. And no visit from little [na2] is a bother."


translate English day9_rs_b8470eeb:


    gr "Come, come in."


translate English day9_rs_33d76030:


    nar "Hurriedly, she puts a cup in front of me. White steam billows from the water, and only then do I smell anything."


translate English day9_rs_c99fe702:


    gr "Tea was all I had today. I hope that's alright."


translate English day9_rs_320fce94:


    pl "I'm just glad you're here."


translate English day9_rs_63c3384c:


    gr "Then why don't we talk about what's on your mind, [na2]?"


translate English day9_rs_12e180a4:


    pl "To tell the truth... This might sound a little sudden, but I started getting curious about something while working."


translate English day9_rs_6d31ecf3:


    gr "Oh, then could it... have to do with the Pestis?"


translate English day9_rs_a7f6e652:


    pl "Yeah. It's got so many effects, and... Well, there's one that makes your body start to decay, right?"


translate English day9_rs_8813964a:


    gr "Indeed. That one is a horrible illness.{w} And there are several types of it, too."


translate English day9_rs_a6911d9e:


    pl "Like what?"


translate English day9_rs_194cc206:


    gr "In some cases, you'll see pus building under the skin, and it will stay there. Others could stop the flow of blood in your arms or legs, causing them to become necrotic."


translate English day9_rs_1a62a08f:


    gr "And other cases where you see a black, mold-like wound..."


translate English day9_rs_b5072db6:


    pl "Yeah! That last one, it's gotta be!{w} How do you fix that?!"


translate English day9_rs_d898f322:


    gr "The symptoms may differ, but the treatment is always the same. The only way is to cut off the rotting portion."


translate English day9_rs_d411b8f7:


    pl "C-Cut off? Wait, what about like... healing techniques? Or medicine?"


translate English day9_rs_040ee266:


    gr "Both healing techniques and medicine are for boosting the body's own regenerative abilities."


translate English day9_rs_60826938:


    gr "To do that, you need to first cut away the parts that are already dead, then either wait for it to heal or do a transplant."


translate English day9_rs_e706ccd0:


    pl "That won't work! We can't!{w} You called it a disease! Can't diseases be cured?!" with sshake


translate English day9_rs_b5e75744:


    gr "There are some diseases that aren't curable, [na2]..."


translate English day9_rs_48c5d86b:


    gr "Of course, you may be right--there might be a better way. But with what healing techniques we have at this point in time, that's the best we can do."


translate English day9_rs_3cdc0e32:


    pl "But... But you fixed my arm for me!!!"


translate English day9_rs_7357ea45:


    gr "They were only wounds to heal--not a body-decaying disease."


translate English day9_rs_fa7a3ef4:


    gr "And yours healed startlingly fast only because of your strange ability..."


translate English day9_rs_f3449be6:


    nar "Strange ability?{w} Well, if this supposed to be a blessing from God, I would rather have had it go to poor Rose, not me."


translate English day9_rs_6eb008d6:


    nar "We can't use an annoying method like that.{w} If any trace of it remains, our secret will turn into a sin and make everyone unhappy."


translate English day9_rs_5a1a46d8:


    nar "I need to search for another way."


translate English day9_rs_088243fc:


    gr "...Would you happen to know someone with such a disease, [na2]?"


translate English day9_rs_eb1e660c_1:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_rs_d8311989:


    gr "[na2], I don't know the details, but... If someone is ill, then they need to receive proper treatment at once."


translate English day9_rs_35164f2d:


    gr "A disease won't go away if you hide it."


translate English day9_rs_8285dbd6:


    gr "Time will not solve anything.{w} Not asking for help from others when you're in a dangerous situation isn't strength--it's hiding weakness."


translate English day9_rs_eb1e660c_2:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_rs_752f6e77:


    gr "...[na2]?{w} Wait! Hold on a minute! [na2]...!"


translate English day9_rs_74f6cb26:


    nar "If my sin could be forgiven just by confessing it, I'd spit out this poison here and now. But it won't be--can't be."


translate English day9_rs_3e250afd:


    nar "I already know about it, so this isn't a matter of forgiving or not."


translate English day9_rs_d4740039:


    nar "I don't want to be forgiven, and I don't want anyone to take revenge on me. I need to keep this sin a secret."


translate English day9_rs_8fc9016f:


    nar "She's right. Me disappearing won't solve anything.{w} In fact, I'm the only one who can fix all this."


translate English day9_rs_b2fa4fd4:


    nar "As long as Rose gets better, nothing else matters."


translate English day9_rs_4f4c92d7:


    nar "Lavi won't have to go through the shock, Rose will be okay, and my sin will vanish."


translate English day9_rs_aa1f882b:


    nar "So I need to look for another way."


translate English day9_rs_eb1e660c_3:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_rs_9b562e6f:


    ev "You shoulder a sin."


translate English day9_rs_eb1e660c_4:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_rs_7a96fbb9:


    ev "We haven't seen each other in some time. How have you been?{w} To think you would suddenly come seeking knowledge..."


translate English day9_rs_58bf1a7e:


    nar "Her appearance wasn't a sudden one. {w} On the other hand, I'm the one who suddenly showed up here."


translate English day9_rs_fa2bc57a:


    nar "I stack a full shelf's worth of books on the desk and begin thumbing through them."


translate English day9_rs_5f896922:


    nar "Truly I'm the uninvited guest here."


translate English day9_rs_c57047ab:


    pl "...My friend is sick. When I asked the doctor in the Health Department, she said it was incurable."


translate English day9_rs_f993ebf2:


    ev "Oh, my... For someone always willing to stand up and fight for what's right, for her to say it's incurable must mean it is a grave situation indeed..."


translate English day9_rs_2554032a:


    pl "But everything in this world can be cured. We just don't know how yet."


translate English day9_rs_ade0b5a6:


    pl "I might be able to find out how, right?"


translate English day9_rs_8a4e58d8:


    ev "Those are respectable words indeed."


translate English day9_rs_0a0c1d29:


    pl "Do you know anything, Lady Evelynn? I want to heal a Pestis disease in a flash without leaving a trace."


translate English day9_rs_8ec60c7e:


    pl "It's as if nothing like that has ever existed... You're the smartest one at the temple, right?"


translate English day9_rs_acf06296:


    ev "Indeed. That which we call the Pestis is a punishment God levies on His people.{w} A punishment towards those who linger in this world of death without the will to accept admonishment."


translate English day9_rs_57b2c5ad:


    ev "That is why humans live ever under its threat..."


translate English day9_rs_b89d6e93:


    ev "I, too, am but a mere human. You have rated my abilities quite highly, so I say this to you in return."


translate English day9_rs_4dfc1a0e:


    ev "A mere human such as myself does not know much more than what they could tell you."


translate English day9_rs_e1911c73:


    pl "...Okay, fine. I'll look by myself."


translate English day9_rs_30bd0e28:


    ev "Hm-hm... You're an interesting person. You know humans can't go against the Pestis, and yet you don't give up on looking for a way through..."


translate English day9_rs_4ecbeb79:


    ev "Are such reckless imaginings only possible because we cling to God in despair?"


translate English day9_rs_608b889e:


    ev "Is that why you are attempting to do something only permitted to God Himself?"


translate English day9_rs_825d53f9:


    pl "Hah? Why's everyone trying to pick a fight with me, anyway... I don't WANT to be in a musty old place like this, you know."


translate English day9_rs_86d96090:


    pl "I'm getting subjected to your dumb priests hiding and spying on me, and to your stupid flower smells that make my head feel like it's gonna split open."


translate English day9_rs_0b9a22bb:


    pl "And this gloomy music, too! I can't focus one bit!" with sshake


translate English day9_rs_4a96128e:


    nar "SMASH!!! I flip over the phonograph that's been in the same spot since day one." with sshake


translate English day9_rs_bc3fcfd3:


    nar "The endless music finally cuts off."


translate English day9_rs_0550ef3a:


    ev "Oh... I liked that record, too..."


translate English day9_rs_e3f39481:


    pl "Something only God's permitted to do? So what?{w} What, you tryin' to say I'm sinning by blaspheming or whatever?"


translate English day9_rs_83c0ac86:


    pl "I just want to solve this problem, no matter what I have to do. I can't just leave it be!"


translate English day9_rs_89315450:


    ev "Sins are nothing more than a standards created by humans."


translate English day9_rs_ce6c2e37:


    ev "It is but one standard by which we make assumptions about what we cannot understand, or must not understand...{w} And I cannot say that either is foolish."


translate English day9_rs_007bae85:


    ev "The idea of wanting to become the god of your own little world, or become someone else's god, is not in and of itself equivalent to blaspheming against the Lord."


translate English day9_rs_004456eb:


    ev "In fact, I want to say it's wonderful!{w} For sometimes, it is blind courage that paves the way to new discoveries..."


translate English day9_rs_31be4703:


    nar "As excited as a rich person showing off their wealth, she takes out a golden key, her little finger raised all the while."


translate English day9_rs_103fa2a7:


    nar "From the round ring hangs a brown leather ornament."


translate English day9_rs_bafe78c3:


    ev "I shall lend you my aid.{w} But only a little bit of it."


translate English day9_rs_d5e365b4:


    pl "...Huh?"


translate English day9_rs_3d8c01c2:


    nar "I make a face, but the woman must be used to it, because she ignores it and simply gestures for me to come along."


translate English day9_rs_d43695e1:


    nar "Since she said she'd lend me her aid, I don't have much choice other than to follow her."


translate English day9_rs_644409bf:


    nar "She doesn't turn back until we get to a place deep within the library. She thinks it's only natural that I'd be following her, and so she doesn't need to check."


translate English day9_rs_a132c66d:


    nar "This woman is a witch.{w} Not \"like\" a witch--she IS a witch, no doubt."


translate English day9_rs_2a94033a:


    nar "And I'm a fool for knowing that and still following her this deep into the library."


translate English day9_rs_a7541264:


    nar "The place the witch takes me to is a normal study."


translate English day9_rs_9708930c:


    nar "When she opens the door, it's a room so normal that the strange smoke drifting past my head and the bloodstained torture devices would probably be ashamed to come in here."


translate English day9_rs_fc4933d1:


    ev "This room once had an owner, but... He has moved to another room."


translate English day9_rs_e94a142b:


    ev "Currently, it is vacant. I will lend it to you."


translate English day9_rs_49f612fd:


    pl "To me...?"


translate English day9_rs_dd9be0e4:


    ev "Yes. The previous owner's things are still littered about, but...{w} You may do as you please with them as well as this room."


translate English day9_rs_6e9422b2:


    pl "...What are you plotting? Is this another of your whims? Like how you decided to let me come and go from the library?"


translate English day9_rs_be9655c1:


    ev "This library means quite a lot to me..."


translate English day9_rs_d7618744:


    ev "Perhaps because I've spent so much time here. Perhaps because I've dedicated half my life to this place."


translate English day9_rs_a9234c17:


    ev "It has fully engulfed me, without a doubt.{w} So right now, it feels like I'm lending out a part of myself to you..."


translate English day9_rs_eb1e660c_5:


    pl "......"


translate English day9_rs_0303be64:


    ev "You may borrow it. You wish to keep this a secret, yes?"


translate English day9_rs_7bd698db:


    nar "For a moment, the carefully controlled air in the room seems stuffy and depressing."


translate English day9_rs_6e9e6570:


    nar "If the library is a part of her, then this place is definitely her stomach."


translate English day9_rs_6d4543f0:


    nar "I reach out my hand, feeling like I'm giving myself over to a snake's fangs. The golden ring falls into it as though it's found its owner, just as it surely did once before."


translate English day9_rs_32c01780:


    nar "Bishop Evelynn looks at me with a satisfied smile."


translate English day9_rs_0621e889:


    ev "Be sure to bring those books into here."


translate English day9_rs_32cd38ee:


    nar "Never tiring of wearing her priest's mask, the witch leaves."


translate English day9_rs_3319e561:


    nar "With its owner gone, there's no sign of anyone having been here recently."


translate English day9_rs_eca26e15:


    nar "The desks of the drawers contain piles of paperwork, and there are a few dusty trophies on the bookshelf."


translate English day9_rs_5a9eab7f:


    nar "But it still feels somehow empty."


translate English day9_rs_a9497759:


    nar "In any case, my body grows heavy, maybe due to the relief of having gained something. But this is where the real work begins."


translate English day9_rs_7d03b193:


    nar "I bring in all the books I'd gotten before until I get to the last one, and head for the next room."


translate English day9_rs_0978d858:


    nar "There's nobody around, and yet Rose is curled up in a little ball, as though the space she's in is much smaller than it really is."


translate English day9_rs_0c1e1f4c:


    nar "I give her emaciated shoulder a tap, and that's enough for her to smoothly open her eyes."


translate English day9_rs_5b17197e:


    rs "Hello, [na]."


translate English day9_rs_c59bf65f:


    pl "Rose... How long have you been here?"


translate English day9_rs_4a309062:


    rs "Since Rose's brother went to work."


translate English day9_rs_9245cfc8:


    pl "Whoa. You really waited a long time... I almost didn't realize you were in here at all."


translate English day9_rs_4eafb495:


    rs "Rose was right here."


translate English day9_rs_5befbaf6:


    pl "Yeah... I know."


translate English day9_rs_3ecdee97:


    rs "......"


translate English day9_rs_e648f99d:


    pl "...Rose, did Lavi find out about your leg?"


translate English day9_rs_e2186023:


    rs "No. Rose gets changed on her own."


translate English day9_rs_d71667d7:


    pl "Really? He really doesn't know about it?"


translate English day9_rs_8d69b925:


    rs "Whenever Rose falls ill or is injured, he always takes care of her."


translate English day9_rs_8a8709e0:


    rs "He won't do his job and all day, he'll stay at Rose's side with an odd expression on his face.{w} But today, he was normal."


translate English day9_rs_e23b63f1:


    pl "*sigh*... That's great. We can rest easy."


translate English day9_rs_650c2a0e:


    pl "Be careful for a while, alright? If your brother finds out, he'll probably be really worried..."


translate English day9_rs_a457b864:


    pl "And you don't like worrying him either, do you?"


translate English day9_rs_67e7563d:


    rs "Agreed."


translate English day9_rs_1e2431ae:


    pl "...I'm going to read some books today, but in a different room.{w} If you have anything you want to read, you can bring it over there too."


translate English day9_rs_f5e87fc4:


    rs "Another room? Outside the library?"


translate English day9_rs_972c85e5:


    pl "No, it's inside the library.{w} Listen, Rose."


translate English day9_rs_dfcc976f:


    pl "We'll be reading in another room today, but you can't tell anyone else about it. Even Lavi."


translate English day9_rs_ba899b87:


    rs "Why?"


translate English day9_rs_4cad569b:


    pl "Hmm..."


translate English day9_rs_17ad7cc5:


    pl "I think he'd be sad if he knew you were hanging out somewhere else after he made this place just for you."


translate English day9_rs_125dbe72:


    rs "Then... Rose won't leave because her brother did make this place for her..."


translate English day9_rs_12989bce:


    pl "A-Actually!{w} I made a place for you too, Rose. So I'd be happy if you came with me." with sshake


translate English day9_rs_757dae5c:


    rs "You did?"


translate English day9_rs_e0cec88c:


    pl "Yeah... You can go out when you want now, right? Why not come with me for today, then?"


translate English day9_rs_24b669f6:


    rs "...Okay. Rose will go with you."


translate English day9_rs_3cef28d7:


    nar "Rose is clearly limping.{w} It's not serious, but it's enough to throw off her balance."


translate English day9_rs_540d8e19:


    nar "I feel like Lavi would have sensed something wrong from that, but..."


translate English day9_rs_44b288ea:


    nar "Their secret relies on the fact that they look so much alike."


translate English day9_rs_4cd29c45:


    nar "In order to protect that secret, the difference between them can't be allowed to grow."


translate English day9_rs_6a3a9f0b:


    nar "From a purely external point of view, Rose has to remain someone who doesn't exist."


translate English day9_rs_e5b73e0c:


    nar "When I think of that, the weight of all the books under my arm pales in comparison to Rose's hand in mine."


translate English day9_rs_5b4f453f:


    pl "When does your brother usually get back, again?"


translate English day9_rs_bf4a9c35:


    rs "At seven in the evening."


translate English day9_rs_5a79cfba:


    pl "Did you eat lunch?"


translate English day9_rs_e6921e2f:


    rs "Yes."


translate English day9_rs_349d6a10:


    pl "Good. Maybe we should have brought in a cushion or a blanket or something...{w} Anyway, make yourself at home."


translate English day9_rs_7b0ac525:


    rs "Those books... Are you going to read them all?"


translate English day9_rs_b8cdec25:


    pl "I am. But I'm still not used to how they talk here in the capital, so I'll need you to help me a lot."


translate English day9_rs_e135ebca:


    rs "Okay. But why?{w} Is there something new you want to find?"


translate English day9_rs_3ebc732a:


    pl "...Yeah. I've gotta cure your disease."


translate English day9_rs_d7a933c4:


    rs "Rose is glad, [na]."


translate English day9_rs_a46e1cbb:


    pl "Why?"


translate English day9_rs_c4c49b4c:


    rs "Because you wanted to find something new."


translate English day9_rs_dc84a32e:


    pl "...What book did you bring in here?"


translate English day9_rs_f62d0f38:


    rs "The Princess in the Tower."


translate English day9_rs_d1c64923:


    pl "Haven't you read that five times already today?{w} You're pretty wild. I get tired of it just looking at the cover."


translate English day9_rs_8d972936:


    rs "Rose knows all of the words comprising this book, but if she doesn't understand its content, she cannot say she has read it."


translate English day9_rs_848ab976:


    rs "But after Rose read it the fifth time, she finally understood why the princess left the tower, leaving the witch who was essentially her mother behind..."


translate English day9_rs_1b41b1c6:


    rs "Rose thinks so, anyway."


translate English day9_rs_e773a4fb:


    pl "Glad to hear that.{w} You're not uncomfortable with me bringing you here all of a sudden, are you?"


translate English day9_rs_bae91920:


    rs "No. Rose is in a dangerous situation, correct?{w} That's why you hid Rose here."


translate English day9_rs_73c6e81f:


    rs "So Rose isn't uncomfortable.{w} Also..."


translate English day9_rs_0b55dd31:


    rs "For some reason, Rose feels relaxed in this room."


translate English day9_rs_84fcb992:


    pl "Oh, good to hear it. Maybe because there's none of that head-splitting flower stench in the air...{w} You sure trust me, huh?"


translate English day9_rs_38e8be86:


    rs "You are a lot like Rose's brother."


translate English day9_rs_a6e894da:


    pl "Huh...? That's silly... If anyone heard that, it would be the embarrassment of the century for us both.{w} Is it because I helped you?"


translate English day9_rs_058653a8:


    rs "Yes."


translate English day9_rs_9240bc63:


    pl "If that's the only reason I'm like him, then all of mankind would be like him... Sheesh."


translate English day9_rs_696369ba:


    rs "[na], is this room a secret too?"


translate English day9_rs_9602ebb1:


    pl "...Yeah."


translate English day9_rs_0f574925:


    nar "And so I start reading the pile of books."


translate English day9_rs_e8aed4e5:


    nar "Cramming the unfamiliar letters and information I can't understand even if I can read it into my head like this, it's no wonder my eyelids start to grow heavy."


translate English day9_rs_a30495d9:


    nar "Rose is acting strangely today."


translate English day9_rs_313e56b7:


    nar "Normally, she's suspiciously quiet--or biting her nails--while she reads books, or is just asleep.{w} But it's a lot more than that today."


translate English day9_rs_2ebc40d9:


    nar "She's ripping out her hair and shoving it in her mouth."


translate English day9_rs_2558cf90:


    pl "H-Hey! What the hell are you doing?!" with sshake


translate English day9_rs_fb7a5519:


    nar "Despite me grabbing her arms, she just stands there, seemingly unaware of why I'm confused."


translate English day9_rs_5292bf6b:


    nar "I'm holding her pretty tightly, but she doesn't make any move to shake me free. It's like gripping a big tree or something."


translate English day9_rs_96c67cb2:


    pl "What are you doing...?"


translate English day9_rs_e6941455:


    nar "I repeat the question as I release her arms, moving only my eyes to look at her. I suddenly get goosebumps."


translate English day9_rs_465773d2:


    rs "Playing."


translate English day9_rs_7739a30c:



    nvl clear
    "\n The conversation stops there. Rose falls silent, and I go back to the desk feeling a whole lot worse."


translate English day9_rs_5b65a741:


    "I decide not to look back again."


translate English day9_rs_84caf583:


    "I try my best to pretend nothing is happening behind me, and only call for her when there's a sentence I have no clue about."


translate English day9_rs_415c04e6:


    et "And I don't particularly ask her, either; I just place the book closer to her and draw a line with my finger. Rose reads the words like a living dictionary, clearly explaining their meanings."


translate English day9_rs_45ba4259:



    nvl clear
    "\n To tell the truth, I want to touch her as little as possible."


translate English day9_rs_f7aaa0d2:


    "I shouldn't, and I know it--but for every time she reads aloud in her monotone voice about the horrors of the Pestis, about the terrifying symptoms and case studies,"


translate English day9_rs_c8206a7b:


    extend " the fear growing inside me only increases. Fear towards the disease--and fear that everything I'm doing will have been for nothing."


translate English day9_rs_d1571d25:


    "The fear has nowhere to go and each time it bubbles up, someone talks to me in my head."


translate English day9_rs_e0af9c21:


    "What if I tell Lavi about it now, and have Rose sent to the infirmary?{w} Dr. Grette is nice, so I know she'll make room..."


translate English day9_rs_16a536b9:


    et "To ignore the thought, I stubbornly copy down the book's contents on a piece of paper."


translate English day9_rs_346c0b30:



    nvl clear
    "\n The moment I say yes to that voice is the moment this secret becomes a sin."


translate English day9_rs_e08ac3de:


    "A lot more people will get involved, and Lavien will have to shoulder all the responsibility by himself."


translate English day9_rs_82d32969:


    "Even though I take care of Rose as best I can, our differing departments mean our time together is limited."


translate English day9_rs_efbbe70b:


    et "Every time I look at the sick Rose, the guilt will attack me--and even after she's healed, I'll probably keep suffering, never able to wash away the sin."


translate English day9_rs_f0a1d692:



    nvl clear
    "\n No matter how many sentences I copy down, my thoughts are too tangled for me to understand any of it. I can't even find a hint that might lead in the right direction."


translate English day9_rs_80269a50:


    et "For a few moments, I take my eyes off the words on the page and look at the book itself. I've been going so hard that the opened tome is nearly in its final pages."


translate English day9_rs_2d1236bc:


    rs "[na]..."


translate English day9_rs_b357f884:


    pl "Not another step!!!" with sshake


translate English day9_rs_c2d5cfe3:


    nar "My sudden outburst causes Rose to cringe and tremble.{w} I tremble too, as I look at her."


translate English day9_rs_049a62e1:


    nar "I catch my breath, my nose clogging and water forming in my eyes."


translate English day9_rs_1f0c1010:


    pl "I... I'm sorry."


translate English day9_rs_89f93f01:


    nar "What the hell am I doing?"


translate English day9_rs_7a3fa53f:


    nar "This is all for her. Why am I acting so selfishly and being so cruel toward her?"


translate English day9_rs_bd4e4621:


    pl "I'm sorry, Rose... I didn't mean that...{w} Sorry for yelling. None of this is your fault. All of it is mine..."


translate English day9_rs_94afb331:


    nar "Sniffing up the stuff coming out of my nose, I give Rose a hug.{w} Holding her shoulders and waist tight, I put my palm on her short hair."


translate English day9_rs_88a40cec:


    nar "Rose keeps her mouth shut; not even an \"it's okay\" comes from it."


translate English day9_rs_4d3c391b:


    nar "All I can hear is her soft, mechanical heartbeat next to me."


translate English day9_rs_a017a424:


    pl "You smell like perfume today..."


translate English day9_rs_cfad8465:


    rs "Rose tried putting some on. Do you like it?"


translate English day9_rs_70bfdd44:


    nar "Her head is sturdy and warm.{w} She might have an incredible wealth of knowledge packed away in there, but that's all."


translate English day9_rs_feed2e2d:


    nar "She told me she couldn't understand other people just by gathering information.{w} What is she, then? Why can't she understand?"


translate English day9_rs_5d6a7025:


    nar "Is Rose not a human after all?"


translate English day9_rs_46e08729:



    nvl clear
    "\n After mulling it over for a while, I come to a conclusion.{w} In short, Rose hasn't always been a living human--she's an automaton created by Lavien Rose, priest of the Academics Department."


translate English day9_rs_11783c86:


    "When I think over everything again, it all ties together. Every priest in this department needs to have at least one topic of research.{w} To become an auxiliary bishop, Lavien both had to prove his own talents and produce results that would satisfy the bishop."


translate English day9_rs_7efb253b:


    et "But given how strange Evelynn Violetta is, a regular paper or little machine won't have satisfied her. Lavien Rose would have put his own special talents to good use--to shocking results."


translate English day9_rs_76b2fe88_5:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_rs_12a7caac:


    "\n And that result was an automaton. A puppet made of inorganic material, made to look human. That was how Rose came into this world--without life."


translate English day9_rs_29372952:


    "But the rest of the department couldn't know about her.{w} Maybe there was a chance the knowledge would be misused, or maybe it was the bishop being greedy--or maybe it was just Lavien's naturally modest personality."


translate English day9_rs_bdd7eb93:


    et "Whatever the case, they had a secret whose existence had to be confined to the Academics Department. So the other priests here all agreed never to tell anyone."


translate English day9_rs_dcf19145:



    nvl clear
    "\n Rose's existence shocked them, but her position here was unclear. Not only did her nature bar her from priesthood, but she also couldn't understand human feelings. And the Academics Department had to hide her anyway, so her place to belong quickly shrunk."


translate English day9_rs_111fef02:


    "And then I appeared. I found her, the one who was supposed to have been left alone, and showed way too much interest in her.{w} I showed her, a girl without a soul, how to imitate a human, which was fine--but then I damaged that which belongs to someone else."


translate English day9_rs_0ee29254:


    et "And now I need to fix her before her owner notices the damage."


translate English day9_rs_76b2fe88_6:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_rs_76b2fe88_7:


    nvl clear


translate English day9_rs_c0d93f6e:


    "\n After dismantling Rose, I arrange her pieces by section. It's pretty difficult, since machines are completely out of my wheelhouse, but once I know how to do it, the work goes smoothly."


translate English day9_rs_11e1371d:


    "Each piece is hot, as though they've overheated from all her activity. The oil powering her leaks everywhere every time I take a piece off--astonishing. It's a good thing I laid down a sheet beforehand."


translate English day9_rs_96550096:


    et "Rose's round head has its eyes shut, breathing calmly, just like when she's asleep.{w} The peaceful expression seems somehow pathetic, so I stroke her head. A little more, and she'll be all better."


translate English day9_rs_b9b5caf3:



    nvl clear
    "\n Lifting her leg, disassembled like a log, I put a scalpel to where the wound is."


translate English day9_rs_a17263c2:


    "The blade goes in very easily, splitting her leg in half, as though it's falling apart into its original pieces. It looks like a rotten fruit, cut in half."


translate English day9_rs_e900228b:


    "I scoop out the flabby, blackened parts, leaving only untouched skin. Next we need new skin to replace the old."


translate English day9_rs_1560ad7c:


    et "I think for a bit, then decide to scrape some off her chest. I mean, she doesn't need that part, given she's modeled after Lavien. I'm sure he'll thank me too."


translate English day9_rs_4bd504d5:



    nvl clear
    "\n Just as I did when I cut the leg, I cut the flesh off her ribs. They're full of moisture, so the fresh-looking skin sparkles like the facets of an expensive jewel."


translate English day9_rs_83f791e6:


    "I take the skin in my hand and dig it out, suddenly getting a dizziness-inducing dose of flower scent. Iris--the one I gave her."


translate English day9_rs_761831b2:


    "The skin is in place now, so I put the puppet back together again.{w} She looks perfect. I completely fixed her."


translate English day9_rs_e8c85f43:


    "Everyone said it was impossible, but I figured it out. I kept it a secret, and kept it from becoming a sin."


translate English day9_rs_7f2f1f2d:


    et "Everyone will be satisfied with this result. I'm glad I was able to fix her.{w} It's okay now, Rose. You're all better now..."


translate English day9_rs_669bb0bf:


    nar "......"


translate English day9_rs_c0e5ab00:


    nar "Rose is asleep in the room's shadows."


translate English day9_rs_1bf83737:


    nar "Her eyes are shut, and she's breathing peacefully."


translate English day9_rs_5883c0d9:


    nar "Nothing is around her that would lock her in, but her position seems to be away from the papers on the floor."


translate English day9_rs_bc06f347:


    nar "There's still the mark of Pestis on her foot."


translate English day9_rs_7c151632:


    rs "...Mmmnnn..."


translate English day9_rs_73aea071:


    rs "...Oh, [na]... You look just like Rose's brother."


translate English day9_rs_7ac581db:


    nar "The day goes by."


translate English day9_rs_76b2fe88_8:


    nvl clear


translate English day10_rs_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day10_rs_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day10_rs_5f7336fa:


    "\n Another two days and nights pass."


translate English day10_rs_99c727ce:


    "Yesterday, after hurriedly checking the time, I brought Rose to the next room over.{w} When I spread out the futon for Rose so she could lie on that instead of her zabuton, it felt like covering her in a funeral shroud."


translate English day10_rs_f842ca80:


    et "Her face pale, Rose closed her eyelids against the shadow I cast on her from above, and the perfume wafting from her body mixed with the awful smell of her wound.{w} That's probably why I said \"so long\" instead of \"see you tomorrow\" like I usually do."


translate English day10_rs_d02537a7:



    nvl clear
    "\n After that, I went back to the study and immersed myself in reading until late in the night. I doubt I'd ever read as many books in my whole life as I did that night."


translate English day10_rs_99523cdb:


    "Since the underground library isn't affected by the weather, I have to rely on candles for illumination both during the morning and the night."


translate English day10_rs_1f3ed927:


    "Plus, these walls are so thick they put the flimsy ones in the Cleanup Department dorms to shame. They block all outside noise, so I lose track of how much time is passing."


translate English day10_rs_33313be4:


    et "Nobody comes to knock on the door.{w} Thanks to that, I forget about the outside world for a little while, able to focus solely on the contents of the books. And so a quiet night began."


translate English day10_rs_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day10_rs_ac0f4ab0:



    nvl clear
    "\n I rest my head on the desk and close my eyes. In the darkness, I see a vision of a temple without me in it."


translate English day10_rs_79c86951:


    "Nobody searches for me.{w} Nobody makes me work, nobody tries to talk to me, and nobody tries to blame me for anything."


translate English day10_rs_8f9c1cb0:


    "Everyone goes on fulfilling their own roles as if I never existed."


translate English day10_rs_82bf1c33:


    et "I'm the freest one of them all. I don't exist, so I have no body, and since I have no body, I have no mind. Within the sense of liberation I get from all my worries disappearing, I cry out in joy by myself and drift lightly through the air... before opening my eyes again and moving my heavy fingers."


translate English day10_rs_8837351f:



    nvl clear
    "\n It happened when I saw the Rose dream, too. In my dream, Rose sat quietly with not only her legs but her newly rotted arms hanging at her side, limp.{w} I have to spoon warm soup into her mouth for her."


translate English day10_rs_46884cd8:


    et "She can't use her arms, so she can neither put her shoes nor change her clothes by herself.{w} I have to bring her to the library, the dorm, and even the bathroom. The same goes for washing her."


translate English day10_rs_a570394c:



    nvl clear
    "\n She can eat on her own right now, but eventually even her teeth will rot and become unusable, and I'll have to feed her fluids."


translate English day10_rs_ea538f91:


    "As I wait for snacks to come into my mind of their own volition, Rose smiles sweetly, looking like a princess. She's a fantastical being--the kind that only exists in fairy tales. And books are the only place where she belongs."


translate English day10_rs_e64cc897:


    et "Her dear, charming frilled dress, and the nose-tingling, strong scent--my princess..."


translate English day10_rs_64df1332:


    pl "...Mnn..."


translate English day10_rs_e1279d32:


    ev "Good morning."


translate English day10_rs_3e37d321:


    pl "Bishop Evelynn...? I thought I locked the door. How did you..."


translate English day10_rs_cf7bb8f9:


    ev "Heh heh... Such is the privilege of the bishop."


translate English day10_rs_994cbece:


    pl "A library master key... Cool. Didn't know something like that existed..."


translate English day10_rs_df5d7a84:


    nar "Just this woman's entrance into the room washes over the slight mustiness in the air with a floral scent."


translate English day10_rs_2ad2ae9d:


    nar "She has a teacup on a pretty-looking plate as well as several cookies. White steam billows from it. She places them on the desk."


translate English day10_rs_a35e587e:


    pl "Oh, uh... Thanks."


translate English day10_rs_cfad7ddf:


    ev "You're welcome. You are my guest, after all."


translate English day10_rs_8ccb59e2:


    nar "A unique, burnt smell drifts from the tea, but it's oddly reddish and clouded."


translate English day10_rs_dbe1b28c:


    pl "...Urp. That's sweet!" with sshake


translate English day10_rs_7abfd1cf:


    ev "Oh, is that so? It tasted normal to me...{w} Hee hee hee. Perhaps three spoons of jam isn't your liking."


translate English day10_rs_332258ae:


    pl "Even just two would have been too much...!{w} I'm really grateful you gave it to me, but my stomach's too empty for sweets..."


translate English day10_rs_4918913a:


    ev "If you're hungry, I have cake as well."


translate English day10_rs_18957b63:


    pl "...Did you listen to a word I said?"


translate English day10_rs_40379375:


    ev "Hee hee hee... That was a little teasing, but quite often what you think is out of the ordinary is something common sense to me."


translate English day10_rs_ab0c9741:


    ev "An ordinary person who goes crazy for being around other crazy people--who, then is the truly crazy one?"


translate English day10_rs_fe6db1a9:


    pl "...I'm pretty sure the group doing the incomprehensible stuff is considered the crazy one there."


translate English day10_rs_99cfa0d6:


    pl "Common sense has a really good reason for being common sense."


translate English day10_rs_99958a6f:


    ev "Then you're doing something outside of common sense right now, right?"


translate English day10_rs_b4895052:


    pl "I guess so."


translate English day10_rs_a578f514:


    nar "I probably look plenty crazy to other people at the moment."


translate English day10_rs_b676f575:


    ev "How is your research coming along?"


translate English day10_rs_5b277e8a:


    pl "...It's not."


translate English day10_rs_ba168d3d:


    ev "Oh, my. What would be the reason for that?{w} Do the black letters seeping into your eyes whisper to you that it's hopeless?"


translate English day10_rs_31170caa:


    ev "Or is the remainder of a thought you still can't get out of your head tickling at your brain?"


translate English day10_rs_a529d07e:


    pl "Both. I think it's both... I just can't find any leads at all."


translate English day10_rs_5d36302a:


    pl "This doesn't look solvable... But it's only been one day, right? Maybe I just couldn't find it that quickly."


translate English day10_rs_0d103b0c:


    ev "Some say that to acquire knowledge, you must treat a book as you might a lover. I've done a lot of staring at my desk in the past myself."


translate English day10_rs_42f3f29c:


    ev "If you happen to see yourself in a mirror after being so absorbed you forget to eat or sleep,"


translate English day10_rs_c4c69f3b:


    ev "what you'll see is the face of a wild animal, a warped version of a hero wielding knowledge and courage."


translate English day10_rs_1bde33c1:


    ev "Yes, which is exactly what you look like."


translate English day10_rs_be823d79:


    pl "I'm glad there's no mirror in here... I guess ignorance is bliss."


translate English day10_rs_bc420917:


    ev "Ignorance is what, you say? Ignorance is also the means through which we accept, body and mind, the pleasure of gaining knowledge."


translate English day10_rs_a0053590:


    ev "And that is why books are so fascinating."


translate English day10_rs_b186aed5:


    pl "Did you do research once before too, Bishop?"


translate English day10_rs_42630373:


    ev "Oh, but of course. When I had just arrived here, I was young and rather average...{w} It's a long story..."


translate English day10_rs_bcccd8fd:


    ev "Hee hee. How about it? Would you like to put your books aside for a moment and share stories?"


translate English day10_rs_83f6a866:


    pl "Well... I was just thinking of taking a rest. Never thought I'd need rest after doing nothing but sit in this chair..."


translate English day10_rs_4ff873fb:


    ev "Oh, naturally. Using your mind is equally as taxing as moving your body."


translate English day10_rs_cf8cc612:


    ev "Always be airing out the library inside your head--and expanding it."


translate English day10_rs_780a5a58:


    pl "Is that why you like sweet stuff that much?"


translate English day10_rs_dc2cfa77:


    ev "Yes, that's right... Hee hee hee. They're not for the body--they're treats for the mind."


translate English day10_rs_3e00d800:


    pl "I can't imagine someone like you being new here.{w} When did you become a priest?"


translate English day10_rs_c47a6c20:


    ev "That is a story that takes me back..."


translate English day10_rs_7450dc2b:


    ev "The day of my coming-of-age ceremony, I left a dear friend behind to come to the temple."


translate English day10_rs_25e8d400:


    ev "At the time, I was the glossy girl who always smelled like soap."


translate English day10_rs_96222c80:


    ev "My unripe, immature mind was filled with curiosity instead of emotions."


translate English day10_rs_b4e93874:


    ev "My hair was so long it reached my tailbone, and I strutted around the temple like a fluffy, newborn kitten."


translate English day10_rs_cfd7b583:


    pl "Wow. Actually, I'm doing a lot of walking around these days too."


translate English day10_rs_0c196239:


    ev "Hee hee hee... We were born as creatures of curiosity."


translate English day10_rs_a0a43c11:


    pl "Oh, by the way. I heard everyone in the Academics Department has to do some kind of research."


translate English day10_rs_1c83b790:


    pl "What sort of research did you do, Lady Evelynn?"


translate English day10_rs_e26efe53:


    pl "I'm curious what you had to write to make you the bishop."


translate English day10_rs_7562ce7c:


    ev "Immortality. I wrote about God imitating humans, and about humans who have metamorphosized into the Pestis."


translate English day10_rs_d22a12ba:


    pl "Immortality? Like, never getting old or dying, right? I've heard of that.{w} But that's all fiction, right?"


translate English day10_rs_98ad6f60:


    ev "No, it surprisingly exists. Very close to us, in fact--a human who does not grow old or die..."


translate English day10_rs_3ad6bccb:


    nar "The corner of Bishop Evelynn's lips come up into a thin, cold smile, as if she's recalling a fond experience."


translate English day10_rs_08f08dd6:


    nar "Her narrowed eyes still burn with the fires of curiosity."


translate English day10_rs_50d5b9ac:


    ev "The temple's cardinal is determined by divine revelation. Whoever receives it stops aging from that point forward."


translate English day10_rs_7e716577:


    ev "These revelations are not formal things simply for determining inheritance--they are God's literal choices."


translate English day10_rs_1b4be54f:


    ev "Therefore, the cardinal has directly communicated with our God above, and becomes equivalent to the Pestis--one of God's servants."


translate English day10_rs_9bc0bc79:


    pl "...Thinking about someone like that being the head of a temple dedicated to fighting the Pestis is a little sickening."


translate English day10_rs_dd3e292d:


    ev "God summons forth His Pestis as a way to make His own will a reality..."


translate English day10_rs_0ddf7c11:


    ev "And a cardinal is he or she who moves in accordance with God's will, making them an equivalent existence to the Pestis."


translate English day10_rs_669cbc99:


    pl "But if they just don't get older, that doesn't necessarily mean they'll never die, right? If they're hurt badly enough, they'll still die."


translate English day10_rs_6f793964:


    ev "They are possessed of a strange regenerative ability.{w} The same as the one you have, Brother [na]."


translate English day10_rs_e782b5df:


    pl "...I'm pretty sure I'd die if someone cut off all my limbs, though."


translate English day10_rs_97183173:


    ev "They would likely die to mortal wounds. There are records of cardinals being killed..."


translate English day10_rs_9a121e7a:


    ev "However, what fueled the fires of my curiosity was the bishop of the Academics Department at the time."


translate English day10_rs_02126460:


    ev "When I happened to bring up this topic with him, he gave me a strange look, straight in the eyes, and said one thing.{w} \"I will not die.\""


translate English day10_rs_5a2f5d28:


    ev "And that man is the one who is now the cardinal."


translate English day10_rs_19a0523f:


    pl "Couldn't he have just been bluffing for some weird reason?"


translate English day10_rs_3a0f3e44:


    ev "If he had been, he's turned out to be quite a magician. With those words, he stole all of my fascination and curiosity..."


translate English day10_rs_969f535b:


    ev "I lost myself in research, forgetting to enjoy my youth."


translate English day10_rs_fa5d2ac9:


    ev "Chasing the unknown is quite fun in and of itself. It felt as though I was in the middle of a long, long dream..."


translate English day10_rs_6d608cc3:


    pl "Hmm...{w} Anyway, did you figure out where the whole immortality thing came from?"


translate English day10_rs_074400eb:


    ev "I did not.{w} I am but a human, and attempting to peer into their sacred relationship was an incredibly impertinent act."


translate English day10_rs_acf98461:


    ev "I have long pursued the truth, but that alone has always eluded me..."


translate English day10_rs_c3a8c3dd:


    ev "In the end, what made me bishop was a paper called this: \"On the Relationship Between Pestis and Humans, and About the Fields\"."


translate English day10_rs_8723e626:


    pl "Oh, come on. You were leading me along!{w} Tricked again..."


translate English day10_rs_361f7a64:


    ev "I never once said that specific research was what made me bishop."


translate English day10_rs_73cfb95f:


    ev "And you were asking about my research, were you not?"


translate English day10_rs_d943f665:


    ev "For me, it wasn't research... It was only extracting what was naturally in my mind."


translate English day10_rs_474f55e9:


    ev "Without a zeal to pursue truth and an all-devouring greed, it cannot be called research."


translate English day10_rs_24172298:


    pl "Sigh... Making fun of me again, I see."


translate English day10_rs_22f956a2:


    ev "Hee hee... What I want you to know, Brother, is that there is no reason to despair just because you can't see the correct answer..."


translate English day10_rs_7d02eace:


    ev "Don't close yourself off in a labyrinth."


translate English day10_rs_64402b3c:


    ev "Remind yourself who you're doing this for, whose god you are trying to become, and always remember that you are blessed."


translate English day10_rs_cab95c0d:


    nar "I don't even need to think about that. Everything has been for Rose's sake.{w} And I'm not the one who needs that blessing--she does."


translate English day10_rs_6e44749d:


    pl "...Now that I have a goal in mind, I can't go back empty-handed.{w} You didn't regret giving up, right, Lady Evelynn?"


translate English day10_rs_8f809d51:


    ev "I grew too old for it.{w} A woman begins to age as soon as she realizes how dull her life has been..."


translate English day10_rs_d52dd482:


    ev "As soon as I realized it, the things that once filled me vanished from me one after another, leaving only free space in their place."


translate English day10_rs_bee25675:


    ev "And with that space, an equal amount of emptiness accumulated. That was when I began tending the woods and inviting others to do the same."


translate English day10_rs_98a5290f:


    pl "Come on. You make it sound like you started raising a pet or something."


translate English day10_rs_ca9789c1:


    ev "It is purely a hobby.{w} And on the other hand, a woman can live forever if she feels fulfillment in life."


translate English day10_rs_ee17cfc6:


    ev "In that sense, Lavi is a wonderful priest.{w} He even has permission from me to grow older... Though that may be a rather figurative way to put it, hee hee..."


translate English day10_rs_94ed6e16:


    pl "How did you first meet Lavi?"


translate English day10_rs_38040967:


    ev "Hmm... It's been six years already."


translate English day10_rs_958c388b:


    ev "To become an Academics Department priest, you have to score high enough on an exam that's held only once a year."


translate English day10_rs_b3f2e6eb:


    ev "But there was one among those who passed who refused to become a priest."


translate English day10_rs_bdf92733:


    ev "Curious as to why, I decided to ask directly."


translate English day10_rs_936232ba:


    pl "Directly?"


translate English day10_rs_3c32e8cb:


    ev "Yes. I wanted to see his face. So I appeared before him not as a bishop, but as a mysterious, beautiful lady of marriageable age."


translate English day10_rs_2e993f1f:


    ev "To summarize, his reason for not coming to the temple was that if he was gone for too long, he wouldn't be able to watch his younger sister."


translate English day10_rs_9d5a3aa9:


    ev "How respectable!{w} He wanted to dedicate those life-defining talents to his flesh and blood."


translate English day10_rs_1e36f654:


    ev "It was a difficult task indeed to stop myself from trembling..."


translate English day10_rs_59864c35:


    ev "As a reward, I granted him an opportunity--as opportunities are to be granted equally."


translate English day10_rs_005bd766:


    pl "...That's why everyone calls you a witch behind your back, you know."


translate English day10_rs_c0fec12a:


    ev "Oh, yes. I am a witch for certain."


translate English day10_rs_8737f623:


    ev "I tempt poor little children with rainbows of spells and strange, fascinating objects, then gobble them up to keep myself beautiful for all eternity..."


translate English day10_rs_e62d8886:


    ev "What I truly wish to teach my priests is not some dull topic of research or other, but this very sense of aesthetic beauty."


translate English day10_rs_bb677e3f:


    ev "And in a very annoyingly troubling turn of events, they began to regard me as a saint of some kind."


translate English day10_rs_0d9c2471:


    pl "What was so boring in the first place? Pretending to live as a witch?"


translate English day10_rs_eb00002b:


    ev "It continued to fascinate me for a long time...{w} Eternity is a boring concept, after all. The moment you attain it, you lose yourself."


translate English day10_rs_61e11d02:


    ev "And it is because I realized that fact that I became an adult."


translate English day10_rs_496b1704:


    pl "Do you mean you lost hope in people?"


translate English day10_rs_a13d500e:


    ev "Mm, rather I was pursuing a fiction. I didn't want to be chained down by a fiction forever."


translate English day10_rs_ef4560fa:


    pl "Doing whatever you want and being free-spirited must be nice."


translate English day10_rs_093861a2:


    ev "I must say, however, that you have changed, Brother."


translate English day10_rs_01820bfd:


    pl "I have?"


translate English day10_rs_6288db5a:


    ev "When I first met you, you were brimming with curiosity."


translate English day10_rs_c2e2f2a7:


    ev "You were like a small animal just born into this world--ignorant of its ways, yet fierce, and you came here on the road of your adventure."


translate English day10_rs_f08e536c:


    ev "But now, you've been swallowed up by this place, and all you do is struggle."


translate English day10_rs_7a490e0f:


    pl "...What are you trying to say?"


translate English day10_rs_20ec60b0:


    ev "That at this rate, you will die."


translate English day10_rs_f18322cf:


    pl "Because you'll gobble me up?"


translate English day10_rs_6393788e:


    ev "No--it will be this space you have created that will do the job."


translate English day10_rs_97f75279:


    nar "Evelynn Violetta gets up from her seat and lifts each of the empty plates."


translate English day10_rs_d7a76d51:


    ev "Now then, remember to love one another as God loves you."


translate English day10_rs_97d2fa1a:


    nar "And after her usual words of greeting and parting, she leaves the room."


translate English day10_rs_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day10_rs_cdb50fc3:


    "\n I don't know how long has passed since then. I open my book up to my bookmark, but I can't remember any of what I was reading."


translate English day10_rs_a49c216e:


    "Is helping someone and being someone they can rely on really the same as becoming that person's god? Every word she uttered to me was enigmatic."


translate English day10_rs_a1d33b66:


    "I don't want to become Rose's god, of course.{w} But if God is the only one who can go against the Pestis and save her life, then I have to acquire that power."


translate English day10_rs_7b758a38:


    et "I vaguely believed I'd be able to do this. That I needed to."


translate English day10_rs_98ba5dff:



    nvl clear
    "\n And then I think of something ominous and look up. Is this really for Rose's sake? I'm not doing this for selfish reasons of my own, am I?"


translate English day10_rs_ea7ac5e3:


    "I quickly shake my head. I'm trying to cure Rose's disease, here. It can't possibly NOT be for her sake."


translate English day10_rs_9d3872c2:


    "Though the answer is clear to me, I feel a strange haste, or maybe a panic, starting to come over me. My pencil grows slippery with my sweat."


translate English day10_rs_ebe8883b:


    "The Cleanup Department has got to be busy while I'm here doing this. I've been skipping work without telling them anything."


translate English day10_rs_faa35bd0:


    et "But as long as I have the key, it doesn't matter what happens. I can always use Bishop Evelynn as an excuse, and as soon as this is over, I can go back just fine."


translate English day10_rs_848c56a5:



    nvl clear
    "\n And even if I were to fail a little, I could just confess it to the angel and have her make it so that it never happened."


translate English day10_rs_b938855f:


    et "The hand turning the pages twitches. I bring my now-useless hands together and offer another prayer to the angel. I've lost count of how many times I've done this."


translate English day10_rs_5ee02e6e:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Rose has a disease.{w} It's my fault--I shouldn't have taught her what it was like outside, or said those things without thinking."


translate English day10_rs_94878e33:


    "Rose still listens to me and likes me, but in all honesty, it doesn't feel good for me."


translate English day10_rs_0b804f3d:


    "I don't have the right. And it's like she sees me as a prince in some fairy tale, but I see her more as an animal or a germ--or a machine..."


translate English day10_rs_82c751df:


    et "And I know I shouldn't, but...\""


translate English day10_rs_94d4771a:



    nvl clear
    "\n I'm talking to myself. Ever since the day she appeared to me, she has never once answered my prayers."


translate English day10_rs_73975f9e:


    et "But if I don't pray, the angel will forget I exist. It will be like I never existed for her, and I'll lose the only one I can rely on."


translate English day10_rs_0d145281:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"...That's why I'm looking for a way to cure her disease now.{w} I could just take her to the hospital, but I'm looking for it myself."


translate English day10_rs_a29e6500:


    "It's because... Well... If this gets out of hand, it will cause trouble for Rose and Lavi."


translate English day10_rs_63708a36:


    "Rose has to stay a secret. If the Health Department found out about her, they'd blame Lavi and make him take responsibility..."


translate English day10_rs_3f9a35aa:


    "And they could punish the priests here for not figuring it out, or even Bishop Evelynn for helping them..."


translate English day10_rs_55694c91:


    et "Yeah... Yeah. I'm not doing this for me. I'm doing this because I have to.{w} I have to. This is the best way...\""


translate English day10_rs_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day10_rs_3a4a669a:


    et "\n The candle's flame goes out."


translate English day10_rs_742d6873:


    rs "[na]."


translate English day10_rs_de9eb7c4:


    rs "Today, Rose wants to tell you something."


translate English day10_rs_7f0d3492:


    rs "It is this fact. Rose is not a complete human. While she is human, her composition cannot be called human."


translate English day10_rs_356498fa:


    rs "Rose is an artificial lifeform created by Academics Department priest Lavien Rose using his genetic information. She is what is sometimes referred to as a homunculus."


translate English day10_rs_16e80a5b:


    rs "Rose's outer skin resembles his, too, because she is his double."


translate English day10_rs_bda525ef:


    rs "Because the act of creating new life in this way is blasphemous due to its nature of playing God, Lavien concealed Rose's existence."


translate English day10_rs_0d36b951:


    rs "This is the same reason we have been lying to you."


translate English day10_rs_a22b90a1:


    rs "Did you know?{w} Rose understands. That is what Rose expected to hear."


translate English day10_rs_26ec7381:


    rs "Now that you understand, allow Rose to propose a solution to this incident. Immediately end all efforts.{w} Reason: Rose is a created being."


translate English day10_rs_c0f97ef0:


    rs "It does not matter if she dies, if she becomes sick, or if she gets better."


translate English day10_rs_2cfdda18:


    rs "Immediately end all of your efforts thus far and do what has always needed to be done."


translate English day10_rs_7074971f:


    rs "Explain this situation to Rose's brother.{w} Leave this place.{w} You are an outsider.{w} You must not continue to be here."


translate English day10_rs_fd427f83:


    rs "Forget about everything regarding Rose, go back to your life, and figure things out yourself."


translate English day10_rs_e7e0a006:


    rs "You're worried about Rose?"


translate English day10_rs_c872995f:


    rs "...You really are like him, [na]."


translate English day10_rs_b4cb7446:


    nar "When I open my eyes, it's still dark. I must have fallen asleep at the desk, since my head hurts and my shoulders are stiff."


translate English day10_rs_45f2bfa6:


    nar "I want to light the candle, but I can't find the tool for doing so."


translate English day10_rs_dd5bda43:


    nar "It would probably be okay to just go back to sleep, but my head hurts because it was lying on the desk."


translate English day10_rs_d114de5b:


    nar "In the end, I wait for my eyes to adjust to the darkness, then take out my key and leave the room."


translate English day10_rs_152e4037:


    nar "I see Lavien there.{w} And next to him is an unfamiliar person."


translate English day10_rs_b53e247c:


    en "What? [na]?"


translate English day10_rs_e08d2cce:


    pl "Hm?{w} Oh, I remember you--the one from the Magic Department. How long's it been?"


translate English day10_rs_72fb7b96:


    en "I mean... I don't think it's been long enough for you to forget my name and call me \"the one from the Magic Department,\" anyway..."


translate English day10_rs_fd0ed4e3:


    en "What are you doing here?"


translate English day10_rs_806d20d9:


    pl "I... I had something to talk to you about, Lavi.{w} Haha. I guess I was here first, huh, Enoch?"


translate English day10_rs_68ffec34:


    en "I'm sorry for assuming--I didn't realize you were here already.{w} I just hope you weren't bored..."


translate English day10_rs_b66d47b6:


    pl "No, I wasn't waiting for very long. I just... wanted to read a little."


translate English day10_rs_7bdc6227:


    en "You said that before, too. I didn't think you'd like the library much, [na]."


translate English day10_rs_6095401a:


    en "You've been, uh, smelling a little different lately too..."


translate English day10_rs_3bb075ee:


    pl "Well, I probably smelled like dead bodies before."


translate English day10_rs_1c350eae:


    en "No, that's not... Hmm. How to put it into words?"


translate English day10_rs_fa16298e:


    rv "People all have a distinctive smell to them--a natural body odor."


translate English day10_rs_397e5d13:


    rv "Normally it's overshadowed by sweat or makeup, but..."


translate English day10_rs_1a338e30:


    rv "To use you as an example, you used to smell warm, like summer."


translate English day10_rs_c18f1794:


    rv "But now it's like the floral scents of the library have seeped into you."


translate English day10_rs_d72a0981:


    pl "Well... It does smell pretty powerful in here, so I'm not exactly surprised. The rest of the Academics Department priests smell the same, right?"


translate English day10_rs_11bfc159:


    rv "Perhaps, though they don't all smell like oil and grease like I do~"


translate English day10_rs_a827197f:


    en "Hey, it's just proof you're working hard, right? Everyone really appreciates what you do, Lavi."


translate English day10_rs_549c9b1f:


    rv "I'm honored to be thought of that way."


translate English day10_rs_5199de30:


    pl "Alright, we've talked enough about our own smells or whatever. But what about you?"


translate English day10_rs_f0c06d52:


    en "Oh, uhh... Well, I take care of myself. You know, with the stuff you spread on your skin..."


translate English day10_rs_70009078:


    pl "Why would anyone bother covering up their smell, anyway?"


translate English day10_rs_2392b3e2:


    en "There's a lot of reasons, but... I guess it's just part of what makes me happy, really."


translate English day10_rs_bc6501bf:


    en "Gotta take care of yourself before you can take care of other people, after all."


translate English day10_rs_97198a86:


    pl "Yeah, you're right about that..."


translate English day10_rs_3976d915:


    rv "Let's not stand here talking. Why don't we go inside? I'll get some tea ready."


translate English day10_rs_d8de6776:


    pl "...Wait, can we use that room?"


translate English day10_rs_8b58060d:


    rv "Yes. Though it only has a chair and a table, as always."


translate English day10_rs_c102eaa3:


    nar "Lavien opens the door; Rose isn't beyond it. I didn't realize this room was okay for people to go in on a whim."


translate English day10_rs_87f0d8e1:


    en "Huh? Lavi, you--what happened to your room?"


translate English day10_rs_96ad862f:


    rv "Actually, my achievements have been recognized... They're letting me move into a slightly larger room."


translate English day10_rs_a7cdaba5:


    en "Wait, then you could have at least gotten some furniture! It's not very convenient otherwise."


translate English day10_rs_f804e24e:


    rv "Hehe. It's not somewhere I'll be staying for very long anyway."


translate English day10_rs_b778e9d1:


    rv "Are you two okay with black tea? If you need anything else, you can tell me."


translate English day10_rs_84949578:


    en "I'll have mine iced."


translate English day10_rs_68c45ac8:


    pl "Hmm... I'll have milk with it."


translate English day10_rs_9eed354d:


    rv "Very well. I'll only be a moment."


translate English day10_rs_ea192b83:


    nar "It feels weird to be in here with someone other than Rose or Lavi."


translate English day10_rs_8c7c256e:


    nar "This used to be Rose's room, but it's turned into almost a playroom. There's only some books and a few cushions in it."


translate English day10_rs_3e59264c:


    pl "You and Lavi came here at the same time, right? How long have you known each other?"


translate English day10_rs_9a0bec46:


    en "Well... How long is it? I came here right after my coming-of-age ceremony, so...{w} About two years, I'd say."


translate English day10_rs_5353bbed:


    pl "Not six?"


translate English day10_rs_9d164173:


    en "...Do I look that old to you?"


translate English day10_rs_b3b862d5:


    pl "No, not that... But are you sure?"


translate English day10_rs_f096273f:


    en "I mean, yeah... We're in different departments, though, so I guess I don't know the exact deatils..."


translate English day10_rs_27cc9202:


    en "But hey, all that matters is that we're pals now!"


translate English day10_rs_b5910455:


    pl "If you don't know everything there is to know about him, how can you call him a friend?"


translate English day10_rs_4fc2cdf2:


    pl "You're just fooling yourself at that point."


translate English day10_rs_424d4d06:


    en "I kinda see where you're coming from, and this is just my opinion, but I think friends still keep secrets from each other."


translate English day10_rs_4e6801ce:


    en "I want to respect that, I guess... And some people need time before revealing things about themselves, too."


translate English day10_rs_8d75708d:


    pl "There must be a good reason for keeping those secrets, though.{w} And nobody will ever know how someone feels unless the person actually says something."


translate English day10_rs_e07a35c6:


    pl "If people are keeping secrets from each other, then it's not friendship--it's just lying to one another."


translate English day10_rs_8945b1b3:


    pl "Actually, you're the type who goes straight to Lavi whenever he needs to talk about something, aren't you?"


translate English day10_rs_a63d935c:


    en "Geh! How did you..."


translate English day10_rs_bb93b2f1:


    pl "It's totally obvious, if you two are friends, considering your personalities.{w} I might have just been bluffing before, but..."


translate English day10_rs_a4787db0:


    pl "Don't blame me if the secrets you tell him in private end up in someone else's ears~"


translate English day10_rs_5a3beff5:


    en "I get what you're trying to say, but I think it's just a matter of trust, in the end..."


translate English day10_rs_ea6f674d:


    en "Good virtue draws other people to you, and that builds trust."


translate English day10_rs_6fa6fe8d:


    pl "Sigh..."


translate English day10_rs_58263e41:


    en "And Lavi's really good at listening, so I tend to talk to him about stuff."


translate English day10_rs_78ed1ce7:


    en "Only people who have felt the same way would understand like that."


translate English day10_rs_1a952526:


    rv "Well, I'm very honored to hear it."


translate English day10_rs_e3ccce6b:


    en "Uwaaah!" with sshake


translate English day10_rs_91170ca4:


    nar "He didn't particularly sneak in or anything, but I'm pretty sure this guy isn't the good-listener type--he's just the type that always goes unnoticed."


translate English day10_rs_fe99ee05:


    rv "But Enoch is the type to keep things bottled up, so once he starts talking, he goes on and on."


translate English day10_rs_0402ac12:


    en "R-Really? Well, the listening is just as important as the talking."


translate English day10_rs_ce82adab:


    pl "Why do you keep trying to flatter him like that?"


translate English day10_rs_3176ded4:


    en "There's just a lot I feel like I can learn from him, you know?"


translate English day10_rs_dd579847:


    rv "It's all thanks to the high esteem you hold me in.{w} Here are your iced tea and your warm milk."


translate English day10_rs_af9397ae:


    pl "...Did you put sugar in here or anything?"


translate English day10_rs_948df03a:


    rv "No, I didn't put anything in. Did you need any?"


translate English day10_rs_acf30c01:


    pl "No... I just figured I'd ask. Thanks for this."


translate English day10_rs_0c1f4038:


    en "Yeah, thanks for the tea, Lavi.{w} And sorry for barging in and then getting you to serve it to me."


translate English day10_rs_b84414ac:


    rv "Not at all. This is nothing compared to the kindness both of you show me."


translate English day10_rs_e0392d0a:


    rv "If there's anything I can ever help with, please let me know."


translate English day10_rs_66d50b97:


    en "Well, if you insist, then...{w} Do something about that super formal attitude! It's making me nervous just hearing it..."


translate English day10_rs_54ef5e07:


    rv "Ack... Is that so? Bad habits die hard, I suppose."


translate English day10_rs_106fc9d1:


    pl "You were calling Lavi your best friend, so I wondered how different he was from when he talks to me. But he's the same as always."


translate English day10_rs_d5d04910:


    pl "How on earth do you have to live to pick up the habit of constantly bowing and apologizing to people?"


translate English day10_rs_92b23a27:


    rv "Hehe. You've got a point."


translate English day10_rs_14c08412:


    en "Yeah, he's teasing you, you know."


translate English day10_rs_43846182:


    pl "No, not at all! That makes me sound like the bad guy, bro."


translate English day10_rs_e312acae:


    en "You know, you call me bro sometimes, but you just call Lavi by his name. That's weird too..."


translate English day10_rs_6b3de20d:


    pl "He doesn't give that same impression. Also, he's short.{w} Anyway, he doesn't think anything of it, so who cares?"


translate English day10_rs_147bb24c:


    rv "Indeed. You may refer to me as you wish."


translate English day10_rs_0ea19a0c:


    en "Mgh..."


translate English day10_rs_cc6ad936:


    pl "Come to think of it, \"bro,\" how is your sister doing?"


translate English day10_rs_3fa7f247:


    en "Regular and healthy like always. She asks about you a lot, actually."


translate English day10_rs_7b83407e:


    en "You should come visit once in a while."


translate English day10_rs_cc709839:


    pl "Okay, okay. Geez, I feel bad for concerning her now."


translate English day10_rs_0fc1dc9a:


    nar "My mind is already a total mess. Why would I ever go somewhere so noisy?{w} Must be nice to not have to worry or think about what you're saying, Enoch."


translate English day10_rs_567a6d8f:


    nar "The only reason he can be so optimistic all the time is because his straight and proper sister is always there to guide him."


translate English day10_rs_1c98dd3b:


    pl "...Does she take care of you a lot?"


translate English day10_rs_a4621121:


    rv "......"


translate English day10_rs_75a507cf:


    en "Huh? ...That's a weird question. But yeah, she always has. Back then, and now."


translate English day10_rs_d59959d9:


    en "I'm her bodyguard mostly to try and repay her for that somehow."


translate English day10_rs_7854f57e:


    pl "Really? What's that like?"


translate English day10_rs_cf2c9f5b:


    en "Basically I'm just sticking with her to protect her. I have to always be training my body and mind for it."


translate English day10_rs_9b33db4e:


    en "Someone who lacks that training could never be allowed to protect her."


translate English day10_rs_8e99d775:


    pl "You really like her, huh?{w} I wonder how she's taking care of you to make you feel that way."


translate English day10_rs_67d1ad23:


    pl "Not that I'm trying to talk shit about it. She's just a little too formal for me... You know, a little unfriendly."


translate English day10_rs_947b5668:


    en "I can't exactly deny that... But for me..."


translate English day10_rs_a37484e8:


    en "Just her being there is a huge help, you know? And she always keeps me in her thoughts..."


translate English day10_rs_6a0b4521:


    en "She trusts me, and she's a model of what I want to be in the future.{w} I could go on and on about the little things."


translate English day10_rs_1461f10c:


    en "It's not just concrete expressions or direct help I owe her for. The simple fact that she's been my sister is really important."


translate English day10_rs_3825d645:


    pl "So you don't need her help?"


translate English day10_rs_d8b70df8:


    en "Not exactly... It's more it doesn't need to be the way, I guess..."


translate English day10_rs_edea4fad:


    en "Obviously, all older siblings should help out their younger siblings!{w} But that said..."


translate English day10_rs_5a8c8922:


    en "Honestly, it's not natural for a lot of older siblings to do that for their little brothers and sisters."


translate English day10_rs_e07d43cc:


    en "Everyone needs to take responsibility for their own lives. Siblings are relationships of striving to help each other out."


translate English day10_rs_1bf53d38:


    en "I don't think you should end up where one side helps the other and not the way around."


translate English day10_rs_a2ac7616:


    pl "So you're saying... that someone who's been helped should show appreciation and gratitude?"


translate English day10_rs_a696367d:


    en "Basically, yeah. And since help is something everyone gets..."


translate English day10_rs_5b48abc2:


    en "Oh, but you're an only child, Lavi. I doubt you understand much of this."


translate English day10_rs_fea67b41:


    en "You know, you could have said something if you were having trouble getting into the conversation~"


translate English day10_rs_35d596e3:


    rv "I didn't want to ruin the fun you seemed to be having...{w} Things that are hard to understand are regrettable."


translate English day10_rs_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day10_rs_baf8fc91:


    rv "By the way, isn't it nearly time for you two to be on your way back?"


translate English day10_rs_81b38c74:


    en "Yeah, I was just thinking of leaving. Seriously, thanks for today.{w} Are you coming with me, [na]?"


translate English day10_rs_6b660f58:


    pl "No, I'll stay for another few minutes. Still had something to do... Be careful, alright?"


translate English day10_rs_287abbab:


    en "Oh, right, you had something to tell him.{w} Okay, then see you both later."


translate English day10_rs_a44a3293:


    nar "The ceiling used by the Academics Department priests is a little low for him, so he has to duck under the doorway to get out."


translate English day10_rs_b6075345:


    nar "Now that the annoying buzzing fly is gone, the room goes back to its usual, quiet state."


translate English day10_rs_021580f3:


    pl "What was THAT about?"


translate English day10_rs_70d853d7:


    nar "Lavien puts down the tray in his hands at my question."


translate English day10_rs_1ca6614b:


    rv "Rose has been asleep in bed all day."


translate English day10_rs_62894ea5:


    rv "She seems a little sick, so I just gave her some food and medicine and told her not to leave."


translate English day10_rs_d8e9d667:


    rv "Rose told me to tell you, if I saw you, that she wanted to see you tomorrow no matter what..."


translate English day10_rs_fba8e074:


    pl "No, I mean that stuff about you being an only child. Is that true?"


translate English day10_rs_d8ed936b:


    rv "What?"


translate English day10_rs_5f4447df:


    pl "You and Enoch came in at the same time, yeah? You must have been friends for a while."


translate English day10_rs_20f85d48:


    pl "How come he doesn't know about Rose?"


translate English day10_rs_211eb580:


    pl "Actually, NONE of this is adding up."


translate English day10_rs_6ab5d079:


    pl "You've been working here for a lot longer than a day or two. Why doesn't anyone find Rose strange or mysterious?"


translate English day10_rs_b52da704:


    rv "It's because of how we display it to others.{w} You believed it at first too, didn't you? ...Ehehe."


translate English day10_rs_921ebcd9:


    pl "What the hell are you laughing about?"


translate English day10_rs_6d46cd09:


    rv "I'm sorry...?"


translate English day10_rs_e13edee7:


    pl "I asked, why the hell do you sound so happy?"


translate English day10_rs_4c7876ac:


    pl "Your sister is sick, on the verge of death--and you're being treated like garbage because of her. How are you smiling like that?"


translate English day10_rs_ab285449:


    pl "What, do you think someone's gonna come up and give you a gold star for effort?"


translate English day10_rs_a8f3b325:


    pl "Every single piece of this situation is literally tearing me the fuck apart and driving me insane. How is it different for you?"


translate English day10_rs_cf67a4dd:


    rv "Little [na], I--"


translate English day10_rs_29945571:


    pl "Rose said I'm like you..."


translate English day10_rs_0bb55cc5:


    pl "Shit. Unlike you, the smartass auxiliary bishop here, I'm a total mess with issues that barely even matter..."


translate English day10_rs_0a07d41c:


    pl "Don't you see it?"


translate English day10_rs_35af5bd4:


    rv "......"


translate English day10_rs_1dad67b7:


    nar "I leave Lavien alone and exit the room."


translate English day10_rs_44bafeb4:


    nar "I go up the stairs and leave the dark basement.{w} The first fresh air in my lungs in a while is stinging and cold, and doesn't smell like anything."


translate English day10_rs_6a50b5ba:


    nar "I've had a lot of dreams about a lot of ideas, but in the end, it was all just me trying to run away from reality. I fucked everything up."


translate English day10_rs_3bef4668:


    nar "No matter what I tried to regain at this point, none of it can be undone."


translate English day10_rs_e2ee7d31:


    nar "I started this as a way to take responsibility by myself, but I never felt any of that responsibility in the first place. Which makes sense. I never WANTED to have that responsibility."


translate English day10_rs_a3dd1076:


    nar "Still, I don't want to push the responsibility on someone else.{w} I'm pretty sure doing that will just lead to a future where I suffer alone."


translate English day10_rs_07023cef:


    nar "I wanted to make it like this never happened.{w} I never wanted compensation--I wanted a miracle to happen to erase everything."


translate English day10_rs_8fed4d4b:


    nar "Poor Rose. I couldn't bring the princess out of her tower. She'll look up at a low ceiling for the rest of her life instead of the sky."


translate English day10_rs_3a4c366b:


    nar "And she'll breathe the artificial floral scents instead of fresh air. For her, that was supposed to be the best way."


translate English day10_rs_e1dcb4cf:


    nar "I should never have taught her about fun if I wasn't willing to take responsibility for it.{w} I should never have delved deeper into her secrets."


translate English day10_rs_2fa1981f:


    nar "I should never have met her.{w} It's all... It's all..."


translate English day10_rs_d6d53cec:



    nvl clear
    et "\n \"My fault...\""


translate English day10_rs_76b2fe88_5:


    nvl clear


translate English day10_rs_cf53f34f:


    "\n The sky is dark and rainy. It looks like it'll rain all night. Under the large shadow cast by the angel's wings, I put my hands together and lower my head."


translate English day10_rs_0b6d58b7:


    "Facing the ground, dirty and with that terrible dusty smell, makes me feel like I've become a sinner."


translate English day10_rs_a9e3bfc5:


    "Blocked by my cries welling up in my throat, I don't reveal the sins I embrace--I just groan and moan. I still can't confess to this sin."


translate English day10_rs_35b65401:


    "That's why I'm praying. For my tranquility, his peace, and Rose's happiness..."


translate English day10_rs_1efed88b:


    et "The angel says nothing, but she listens to my prayers for a long time."


translate English day10_rs_76b2fe88_6:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_rs_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_rs_36ca220a:



    nvl clear
    "\n After sunset--or at least, it would have been, if not for the midnight sun--I go to the library again."


translate English day11_rs_0b007926:


    "I'm worried about what I'll say if I run into Lavi again, but neither he nor any of the other priests are around. Not even the slight, almost overlookable presences are here."


translate English day11_rs_2a3de554:


    et "Finally, I realize how long a time I've spent outside. Having gotten the huge library all to myself, I touch nothing and hole myself up in my cramped little study.{w} This must be what Rose always meant when she talked about a place she was allowed to be in."


translate English day11_rs_7c8b3b37:



    nvl clear
    "\n I don't remember anything after that point, just fragmented scenes floating up into my mind here and there. I don't remember any of the contents of any of the books I so desperately claw through."


translate English day11_rs_86521c0c:


    "The candle is lit, and the room is bright enough, but my vision is dark. Instinctually, I know I've reached my limit."


translate English day11_rs_8b75b23d:


    "The moment my consciousness fully returns, I come face to face with the despair I've been covering up this whole time."


translate English day11_rs_113cbd9e:


    et "The pen I've been holding and the book on the desk fall to the floor. It's over. I can run from this all I want, but there's nowhere left TO run."


translate English day11_rs_5d8a5adc:



    nvl clear
    "\n It's the third day since coming here. I've had two days, and yet I've accomplished nothing.{w} And while I waste time like this, poor Rose's condition is getting worse."


translate English day11_rs_a14bb0c0:


    "I'm sure Lavien already realizes what his sister's disease is. He probably blames himself for it, just like I do, and pretends nothing is wrong while racking his brain over a way to fix it."


translate English day11_rs_daff70a8:


    "Otherwise, why would he hide the truth from me? Should I just go to him right now and talk to him about it?"


translate English day11_rs_33d5f4df:


    "I don't know... I just don't know anything anymore. It feels like my brain lets out a screech every time I try to think of something else."


translate English day11_rs_b253fe46:


    et "Only memories of bygone days float to the surface like regrets, one at a time."


translate English day11_rs_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_rs_6f58bf32:


    "\n \"How much brain power do you think it takes to create a new story?\""


translate English day11_rs_6e97752b:


    "She's essentially an incomplete human. Like a machine missing a part or two, or a pie in an oven that doesn't have all the ingredients in it. When God made her, He forgot something important that all humans need."


translate English day11_rs_fb198fd2:


    et "Being different from the others doesn't make her special. Like an idiot, I mistook her Pestis for something mystical, something fascinating. And that irresponsible curiosity had caused this Pestis."


translate English day11_rs_9d361ed4:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"You are an outsider. You are not permitted to remain here.\""


translate English day11_rs_ef6d6687:


    "Being born with something missing isn't a sin.{w} So nobody could selfishly bring her any harm or criticize her for it. Punishment is reserved for those who have sinned. You can't hold her responsible for a \"sin\" that's been with her since she was born."


translate English day11_rs_956d99ec:


    et "She needs someone to stand by her and take on all of the responsibility--and punishment--in her place."


translate English day11_rs_d6411397:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Nobody ever asks Rose for help. But Rose is always prepared to help others.\""


translate English day11_rs_1ea31afc:


    "Poor Rose. It's all my fault.{w} If only I'd saved you sooner."


translate English day11_rs_d3ee9109:


    et "I was trusted with your safety. I had a responsibility to protect you. But I didn't protect you--in fact, I harmed you. I'm sorry."


translate English day11_rs_790905d0:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Bye-bye.\""


translate English day11_rs_9e30afad:


    "I should have devoted myself more to you. When we were walking around the temple and you were so happy to be wearing girls' clothes, I shouldn't have objected--I should have praised you.{w} I shouldn't have looked over at that flower and pretended to care about it."


translate English day11_rs_ed40acfd:


    "I should have actually listened to when you complained, when you talked about your family situation, when you said unkind things.{w} I should have watched over you at night when you went back to the dorm to make sure you didn't feel bored.{w} And when you messed up your own body and your room out of pure intentions, and broke that machine, I should have smiled and patted you on the head even if your hair was filthy."


translate English day11_rs_a2fffe8e:


    et "Even if someone else tried to blame you, I should have taken on that sin, because you were never to blame for any of it."


translate English day11_rs_7cc55212:



    nvl clear
    "\n When you said you loved me, I should have said I loved you back.{w} I should have kept on saying it forever, always staying by your side."


translate English day11_rs_50183ef2:


    et "Forever, and ever, and ever..."


translate English day11_rs_06c6145d:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"According to you, 'fun' is a positive feeling one has when doing things together, and what makes one feel sad when it's over. Rose felt that way too.\""


translate English day11_rs_c4e2e3df:


    "\"And so she waited. For a long time. So Rose feels like she's having fun right now.\""


translate English day11_rs_b22811fc:


    et "I'm sorry, Rose.{w} I did this to you..."


translate English day11_rs_76b2fe88_2:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_rs_97256658:


    nar "I hear something I've never heard here before. A knock at the door."


translate English day11_rs_5b2d4829:


    nar "At first, I figure I'm just hearing things, but after a few moments, the knocking grows louder."


translate English day11_rs_b5b53851:


    nar "Suddenly I remember a cat we'd raised back home. It would use its claws to scratch at the door until someone opened it."


translate English day11_rs_6970666a:


    nar "There's only one person who could be knocking like this on the door of an ownerless study."


translate English day11_rs_fd8cfce8:


    pl "...Rose."


translate English day11_rs_07b73999:


    rs "[na]!"


translate English day11_rs_98505af7:


    nar "As soon as the door opens, she hugs me, without even looking at my face."


translate English day11_rs_004ca252:


    nar "She tightly embraces my waist and buries her face in my chest. The cold outside air stuck to her clothes blows to me as well."


translate English day11_rs_3dda987b:


    nar "My nose, which has grown even more sensitive overnight, doesn't suffer with the stench coming off her."


translate English day11_rs_e8724aeb:


    nar "That stench of rotting flesh, which I haven't smelled in days."


translate English day11_rs_cc477d05:


    nar "And I can also smell perfume, as though she tried using it to cover up that deathly odor."


translate English day11_rs_a4fb22e7:


    nar "Unfortunately, it's so strong it mixes with her skin's odor and makes it even worse."


translate English day11_rs_9691d440:


    pl "Rose, you...{w} Where's your brother? Why are you alone?"


translate English day11_rs_0ed0ebfd:


    nar "It must hurt at this point, and yet her face is normal--like she doesn't even feel the pain."


translate English day11_rs_38a0822c:


    nar "And it doesn't look like she's trying to endure pain, either.{w} That's great, but seeing her face makes me not want to ask any more questions."


translate English day11_rs_37bc9692:


    nar "Dealing with her now will just tire me out."


translate English day11_rs_2b769455:


    rs "Were you surprised Rose could come by herself?"


translate English day11_rs_fdf35ffc:


    pl "...You were never the one to visit me before."


translate English day11_rs_fab8ac62:


    rs "Rose missed you."


translate English day11_rs_8bff8d4b:


    nar "This beloved girl stuck to my clothes now..."


translate English day11_rs_a6c8b9fe:


    nar "When I remember she's carrying germs that kill people and is actively decaying, I start to feel something odd about each of her actions."


translate English day11_rs_eb1e660c:


    pl "......"


translate English day11_rs_f12401d2:


    nar "As I pat Rose's head, I bring my arm out slowly.{w} Hoping it doesn't get in the way."


translate English day11_rs_b5c390ad:


    nar "But she must have thought it was a strange thing to do, because as I go back to the desk, she clings stubbornly behind me, pushing herself up against me."


translate English day11_rs_3c24aaae:


    rs "Are you reading?"


translate English day11_rs_6f4cc9ae:


    pl "Yeah."


translate English day11_rs_9cd2d742:


    nar "Rose looks at the book, seeming bored. There must have been a few things she was hoping to see before coming here."


translate English day11_rs_17ae64a6:


    nar "And those things are contact with me, and conversation, though I really hope that second one isn't it--but it seems like both are."


translate English day11_rs_b602ab1f:


    nar "Why am I avoiding her?"


translate English day11_rs_0e0da18b:


    nar "She's been the only thing on my mind lately. Wasn't thinking about her the only thing I'd been doing?"


translate English day11_rs_742d6873:


    rs "[na]."


translate English day11_rs_fb8db86b:


    pl "Rose, could we talk later?"


translate English day11_rs_d4cd8d02:


    rs "Pardon?"


translate English day11_rs_27699fda:


    pl "I'll do whatever it is you want.{w} For now I just want to focus. Do you understand what I mean?"


translate English day11_rs_de6d4b8a:


    pl "So you go read a book, or do whatever else you feel like..."


translate English day11_rs_4b6d78e7:


    rs "When is later?{w} When your research is done, [na]?"


translate English day11_rs_32d4a555:


    pl "...Yeah."


translate English day11_rs_aedfc416:


    rs "Why?"


translate English day11_rs_873a5506:


    nar "Why are you doing it?"


translate English day11_rs_3bf0adac:


    nar "You can ask me all you want. I've answered so many times."


translate English day11_rs_8e92b2aa:


    nar "I feel so bad for her.{w} She got this disease because I wasn't careful enough.{w} I have to atone for the sin I committed."


translate English day11_rs_63eec8f1:


    nar "This is all for you.{w} All for... For..."


translate English day11_rs_eb1e660c_1:


    pl "......"


translate English day11_rs_91b6c4ec:


    rs "[na]?"


translate English day11_rs_883e143e:


    pl "It's your fault..."


translate English day11_rs_6c5d1cf2:


    rs "Rose's?"


translate English day11_rs_200b656c:


    pl "It's your fault. Dammit, this is all your fault, isn't it?! Everything! Every last thing!" with sshake


translate English day11_rs_0fbdc218:


    pl "If only you weren't here... You messed everything up!" with sshake


translate English day11_rs_76b2fe88_3:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_rs_9e52e148:


    "\n After my sudden outburst, she just stares at me, not seeming surprised or afraid."


translate English day11_rs_30ca0a1f:


    "She might actually be SO surprised she's just in shock."


translate English day11_rs_8aab647e:


    "But her impassive gaze is enough to make me feel even more miserable."


translate English day11_rs_43a393bf:


    et "She probably never thought every single action, no matter how little, had the power to manipulate someone's emotions to this extent."


translate English day11_rs_6d4e17d2:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Are you tired?\""


translate English day11_rs_1f243401:


    "Her tone is easygoing, like she still doesn't understand the situation, but I fully understand even those few words."


translate English day11_rs_eb9c056c:


    et "Every day I've spent trying to take responsibility for her has been painful and agonizing. Even someone like me, who has never been someone's guardian before, immediately understood how heavy the responsibility for taking care of someone is."


translate English day11_rs_8eae9dcb:



    nvl clear
    "\n That weight is strange and ominous.{w} The more days pass, the more distant I feel myself getting from the place I was before."


translate English day11_rs_e02414ef:


    "I took responsibility, so I had to be serious about treating her as precious. I should have loved her. But I couldn't."


translate English day11_rs_33dad6bc:


    et "Ever since that day she pulled all the books off the shelf and poured the trash over her head--or possibly even since the day we first met--I felt a distance between us that was rooted in a dislike for her."


translate English day11_rs_4fc93eb4:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Are you tired of Rose?\""


translate English day11_rs_80cda58b:


    "Yes--and those dull words are making it worse."


translate English day11_rs_a6a43dd7:


    "After a hundred times of her talking to me, finally I have an insincere response. I can't even try putting a smile on in this uncomfortable situation--those eyes, staring at me, as if observing me--that silence..."


translate English day11_rs_cd8bbd6e:


    "My vision starts to go black, and for just an instant, I feel like I can see inside Rose's mind--something nobody has ever seen."


translate English day11_rs_76dc277b:


    et "Inside her head, it's black and deep. An enormous hole.{w} A never-ending abyss... which I've fallen into like a trap."


translate English day11_rs_86cd9da4:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Yeah, I'm tired. I'm so tired I feel like dying."


translate English day11_rs_11adfe64:


    "But I'm not the only one. Lavien is the one you're making suffer so much by not knowing how to live independently! Lady Evelynn is the one who would suffer if anyone finds out you were snuck in here! The priests in this department are the ones who have to go along with your craziness! Everyone's tired as hell!\""


translate English day11_rs_e80fd518:


    et "After raising my voice again, Rose finally understands what I'm implying. She gives a start, gasping.{w} She really wasn't calm after all--she just didn't understand the severity of the situation. She only has one guardian, and now he's like this, and she's in this situation..."


translate English day11_rs_35e2e576:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Rose is sorry.\""


translate English day11_rs_0253ae1d:


    et "The voice trickling from her tightly closed lips is softer than usual. Despite the brevity of her comment, it comes out mumbled."


translate English day11_rs_c74385bc:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Rose is sorry. She did her best."


translate English day11_rs_002ee576:


    "She tried so hard. She wanted to become the Rose you liked, [na].\""


translate English day11_rs_b010f1b9:


    "......"


translate English day11_rs_f58bceb2:


    "\"Rose really loves you, [na]. So please, don't hate her."


translate English day11_rs_45576927:


    "If you sever your bond with Rose, the Rose you like will disappear.\""


translate English day11_rs_b49f629a:


    "Bond?"


translate English day11_rs_4e53a029:


    "\"Please, don't sever your bond with Rose...\""


translate English day11_rs_0b0ec87a:


    "The \"thing\" fidgeting before me starts playing with her fingers. She looks like she's frightened, but also like she's embarrassed."


translate English day11_rs_6d182b0b:


    et "W h y ?"


translate English day11_rs_a62dbc72:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Why's something that isn't a person talking?\""


translate English day11_rs_71abe65f:


    "\"...Rose is a person...\""


translate English day11_rs_c352f191:


    "No. You are not a person. If you were, you wouldn't need to pretend to be one."


translate English day11_rs_b309f014:


    "People live on communication and understanding. They act based on an understanding of others' emotions, they verbalize what the want to convey to others, and if it's not conveyed, they explain."


translate English day11_rs_26244fee:


    et "But you are different.{w} No matter how many people are around, you surprise others with shameful or indiscreet actions, and you simply obey information you get instead of understanding it.{w} And in the middle of all that attention, you only think about your own position--you can't understand the position of those trying to clean up after you, and instead just cause them more trouble."


translate English day11_rs_5dc08680:



    nvl clear
    "\n I would understand if you were three years old, or at the very least someone who had just become an adolescent, but you're probably older than I am."


translate English day11_rs_153fe462:


    "Being different from others doesn't give you the right to mess up other people's lives or a shield to hide behind while you make trouble for them."


translate English day11_rs_8bcad8c1:


    et "I don't know how it would be with your approving family, but if you can't even put forth the least bit of effort, then outside your family you'll never be perceived as a person."


translate English day11_rs_48e42db0:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Rose became a normal girl. She's different from before.\""


translate English day11_rs_663b8feb:


    "\"Different how?\""


translate English day11_rs_602b2492:


    "\"Was that not enough? Rose will try even harder."


translate English day11_rs_b46f4076:


    et "She's sorry for everything, [na]. And Lavi, Rose is sorry, Rose is... Rose is...\""


translate English day11_rs_4ce0f244:



    nvl clear
    "\n I can think of several reasons, but I understand that none of them mean anything.{w} No matter what I say to her, she won't understand. This is exactly how she tempts other people into giving up on things."


translate English day11_rs_0880e57a:


    "Is it still a sin if you're ignorant of it?{w} Nobody could make her ignorance into a sin because of what she lacks--so she's lived her life permanently unaware of it. And even I thought that was the way it had to be."


translate English day11_rs_ce52aa2b:


    et "But that's not a good enough reason to force myself to endure the rejection I feel towards her.{w} After all, honest girls are SUPPOSED to smell like flowers."


translate English day11_rs_76b2fe88_4:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_rs_d91dc835:


    "\n \"I've got a fact for you.{w} Fresh meat actually has a sweet smell to it.{w} But your blood only smells rotten."


translate English day11_rs_1a8f332b:


    "You're disgusting.{w} I can't stand that awful stench of yours anymore.\""


translate English day11_rs_d356af07:


    "The words from my lips are dry and stiff. Completely monotone, with none of the ups or downs or depth or emotion that voices are supposed to have.{w} And I'm unusually calm through the whole thing."


translate English day11_rs_bc6af3c7:


    et "My vision blurs, doubling, then tripling, warping into a complex pattern.{w} A moment later, I realize something is wrong."


translate English day11_rs_37ec4f9d:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Ahhh, ahhhhhh...\"" with sshake


translate English day11_rs_05dcd5a0:


    "Before my eyes, Rose is twisted into a shape I've never seen before.{w} Her tears, the size of rice grains, fall from her muddled eyes, streaking down her bright red cheeks."


translate English day11_rs_0c3856b4:


    "The clothes she liked so much are a wreck now, probably from gripping them too hard."


translate English day11_rs_6897468c:


    "\"Why...?\""


translate English day11_rs_917e3f0d:


    et "Something stirs in my heart. Everything about her that I've seen until now, all the time I've spent with her, quickly melts into her tears and flows away with them. I suddenly realize I'm shaking my head."


translate English day11_rs_2c5ae14f:



    nvl clear
    "\n This isn't something that's supposed to happen.{w} Her pained crying grows louder, mercilessly disrupting my distorted mind."


translate English day11_rs_cf5ccb4c:


    et "I can't bring myself to believe that there was something even more hopeless here.{w} I have to reject it. Deny it."


translate English day11_rs_35b2e092:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Just be quiet and stay still like the doll you are. Like the unfeeling doll you are..."


translate English day11_rs_97a472b1:


    "Like you've always been. What are you crying NOW for?"


translate English day11_rs_334f3f14:


    "It's too late!{w} For everything!{w} I'm the one who wants to cry!!\"" with sshake


translate English day11_rs_01940181:


    "I kick something down--maybe a bookshelf next to me, or something more decorative. The room's small size means the furniture is all packed together. Books and trophies clatter to the floor."


translate English day11_rs_5678800d:


    "The paper covering the walls and floor leaps into the air, dancing.{w} Looking at all my efforts the past few days makes it seem like nothing at all. Pointless rows of letters. Wastes of time. They're piles of paper, and nothing else."


translate English day11_rs_d5b69333:


    et "I reach for a golden trophy lying amidst them."


translate English day11_rs_e0419b40:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"Did Rose do something bad?{w} Is that why you hate Rose, [na]?"


translate English day11_rs_4e4c6529:


    "Rose is sorry. Rose is sorry for everything.\""


translate English day11_rs_21905093:


    "Don't say \"everything.\" Say what exactly you're sorry for. You've always been like this. Do you think things would have changed if I'd endured it and pretended it never happened?"


translate English day11_rs_5d7238e3:


    "I bite down on my lip so those trembling words don't come out. She's still bawling.{w} It feels like everything's turned upside down. If I have to keep listening to that awful wailing, I'll actually go insane."


translate English day11_rs_76b2fe88_5:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_rs_76b2fe88_6:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_rs_810c6ee2:


    et "\n In the end, I swing the object in my hand. Rose lets out one final cry, then clutches her head and staggers." with sshake


translate English day11_rs_b864dc74:



    nvl clear
    "\n \"It hurts...\""


translate English day11_rs_75655457:


    "She's not crying now, but instead she just repeats those words over and over."


translate English day11_rs_49a9ed56:


    "It hurts? It hurts? Why?{w} That's what I want to know.{w} How did things turn out this way? Who am I supposed to assign blame for this?" with sshake


translate English day11_rs_033e1e15:


    et "If I thought about it a little more, I might figure it out. But I can't think about anything anymore.{w} My sense of reason is completely gone. In my hazy, enraged mind, I only know that there's no going back from here."


translate English day11_rs_5afb2c1e:



    nvl clear
    "\n Her skull, hard and round, seems to somehow dent with every time I bring the trophy down."


translate English day11_rs_cb8c586c:


    "I focus only on the vibrations coming through my hand, and keeping my sweaty, heated grip on the handle.{w} Rose cries all the while."


translate English day11_rs_81937af9:


    "I'm making noise, too, nonverbally. It comes out like a roar, like I'm absolutely terrified."


translate English day11_rs_0c6b8fc6:


    et "And in truth, I am."


translate English day11_rs_76b2fe88_7:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_rs_5bec1c56:


    "\n The heavy thumps travel from my arm to my body. I feel that signature softness of gold. A drop, then two, of blood join the sweat dripping down my face. I smell heated iron." with sshake


translate English day11_rs_bf03c7c7:


    et "But the thing I'm most afraid of is that she still hasn't lost consciousness--and moving her hands towards me."


translate English day11_rs_ed9a05ce:



    nvl clear
    "\n Eventually, she cries out \"Help! Brother!\" and grabs onto my arm."


translate English day11_rs_2a046952:


    et "Stop! Do NOT touch me with that filthy body of yours! I scream instead of replying to her, which probably doesn't get through to her." with sshake


translate English day11_rs_c934edf5:



    nvl clear
    "\n That rotten ball of flesh is nothing but an awful stench given form now.{w} To be honest, she's long seemed like a big, pus-filled thing overlaid on a girl's skin. She can't live on her own, and yet she doesn't help those letting her live--instead she brings disease and calamity like some sort of jinx." with sshake


translate English day11_rs_d4854f04:


    et "Saving her is more than just watching over her--it's giving yourself over to her.{w} And when someone does, she plants her roots in them to keep on surviving, like a parasite. Eventually, the person rots, and they die. But she's never gotten rid of anyone that easily. Because she couldn't."


translate English day11_rs_5f956f69:



    nvl clear
    et "\n That's how I try to prove to myself that I am innocent, free of sin. But in the end, these are nothing but the excuses of a murderer."


translate English day11_rs_76b2fe88_8:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_rs_68d8119f:


    et "\n Rose is no longer moving.{w} I can't see that ever-charming, pretty face of hers behind all her blood-soaked bangs. She's been losing hair the last few days, and I could see the redness of her scalp through it. The papers on the floor become another pool of blood as the red continues running through them."


translate English day11_rs_f5b7c854:



    nvl clear
    "\n This dusty, unused room is now filled with the stenches of her death.{w} I stand still, breathing. My bright-red, faraway vision finally starts to shift back into reality."


translate English day11_rs_30eb9868:


    "The strength quickly leaves my arms, and the now bent trophy falls from my hand.{w} My gaze, too, falls to the floor. Rose's hand is still outstretched towards me."


translate English day11_rs_b6d65c42:


    et "The trophy lies nearby, with \"Lavien Rose\" written in small letters on it."


translate English day11_rs_76b2fe88_9:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_rs_76b2fe88_10:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_rs_626af568:


    "\n \"...Little [na].\""


translate English day11_rs_9808c28c:


    "And then I hear his voice from behind me. I don't know how long he's been there.{w} The door's been open the whole time, though, and it's only natural he couldn't get permission to enter from the room's original owner."


translate English day11_rs_40c43faa:


    "\"...ahaha, hahaha...\""


translate English day11_rs_ede59d12:


    et "So when our eyes meet, I--the outsider who wasn't allowed to intrude--stalk past him out of the room without a word."


translate English day11_rs_76b2fe88_11:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_rs_32b0006c:


    "\n Lavien doesn't try to stop me. I don't hear him following me, either."


translate English day11_rs_2468824e:


    et "He just seems to see the two of us off. Eternally."


translate English day11_rs_76b2fe88_12:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_rs_fe5c11eb:


    "\n At this point, I actually feel pretty refreshed. My walk back to the dorm is quiet. I'm sure this path will be filled with people waiting for my execution tomorrow."


translate English day11_rs_6d7652d5:


    et "The future doesn't even bear thinking about now. I killed someone, and I'll be punished for it.{w} With the highest punishment of all--death."


translate English day11_rs_fd328244:



    nvl clear
    "\n I'll probably be interrogated beforehand. They won't let me decide how I want to die."


translate English day11_rs_eebab863:


    "They cut off someone's head in the last execution I saw here, but I doubt it'll be that easy for me.{w} If I'm to die, I want them to beat me with blunt objects so I can experience the same pain Rose did."


translate English day11_rs_aa694072:


    "If I died like that, the suffering I feel now will end too."


translate English day11_rs_fbdd90fc:


    et "Whether or not they're satisfied with my punishment, I won't be around anymore for them to blame.{w} Punishment is a way of cleansing sin, so I'll be able to die with a pure heart.{w} And I'll finally have that eternal freedom I've dreamed of."


translate English day11_rs_76b2fe88_13:


    nvl clear


translate English day11_rs_ebe847e4:


    et "\n And yet, for some reason, I haven't heard anything."


translate English day11_rs_4379d8ff:


    nar "I go back to my room, change my clothes, and wait for the bell to ring to tell me it's lunchtime."


translate English day11_rs_45bed802:


    nar "I thought for sure some guys in black suits would kick down the door and come storming in."


translate English day11_rs_e9eca204:


    nar "But I only hear the footsteps of passerby and regular, everyday conversations. Nobody so much as knocks."


translate English day11_rs_5b600e3d:


    nar "Something must have gone wrong.{w} The thought makes me panic."


translate English day11_rs_9117003d:


    nar "If nothing continues to happen and I, alone, end up seeing an average tomorrow..."


translate English day11_rs_2ab315ab:



    nvl clear
    "{nw}" with sshake


translate English day11_rs_31f6756d:



    nvl clear
    nar "No. That must not happen. It must never happen."


translate English day11_rs_cca3b493:


    nar "I leave the room and head to the library again."


translate English day11_rs_c23e0f5b:


    nar "I never thought I'd go back there after leaving it. It's like I'm a bug purposely flying into a Venus flytrap."


translate English day11_rs_57cb8da5:


    nar "While there are people in the library, none appear before me.{w} Whenever I coincidentally spot someone, they quickly disappear."


translate English day11_rs_2e7bb007:


    nar "It's only right for the shy priests here to be cautious around a cold-blooded killer.{w} They speak in hushed tones that I can't make out."


translate English day11_rs_d6375698:


    nar "I'm sure they remembered that I, the wild animal who murdered someone, am on the disposal team, and thinking that I came to dispose of the corpse."


translate English day11_rs_c9788f50:


    nar "I lift a hand to open the door, only to find it makes a clacking sound--it won't budge.{w} It's locked."


translate English day11_rs_72b872c0:


    nar "Since I have the key, I bring it out and open the door...{w} But that's where things get stranger."


translate English day11_rs_3373e18d:


    nar "There's no corpse inside.{w} The piles of papers and broken trophy are gone too.{w} And it's clean inside--not a bloodstain in sight."


translate English day11_rs_fdabdfae:


    nar "There's no trace of me ever having been here, either, as though the events of the last few days had never happened."


translate English day11_rs_2d29dc93:


    pl "...Ahh!" with sshake


translate English day11_rs_115b7962:


    nar "The witch appears right then, and I run up to her, falling to my knees and looking up."


translate English day11_rs_7dcd03e1:


    nar "She doesn't close the book she's reading; she just moves her eyes to look at me."


translate English day11_rs_6829688e:


    pl "You're the one who left the door closed, right, Lady Evelynn?{w} And you'd have the key, so..."


translate English day11_rs_e85f01cb:


    pl "What, uh...{w} What happened to what was in here?"


translate English day11_rs_af67f3fc:


    ev "......"


translate English day11_rs_abfca0cc:


    pl "...I'm trying to ask you what happened to Rose's body!"


translate English day11_rs_9e989102:


    pl "If you can't say, then at least tell me where Lavien is right now!"


translate English day11_rs_af67f3fc_1:


    ev "......"


translate English day11_rs_9d3c4bd1:


    pl "I... I killed her.{w} I used a trophy or something--hit her in the head, over and over, until she couldn't move...!"


translate English day11_rs_34615f1a:


    pl "She cried and said it hurt, and I didn't listen at all, and I killed her."


translate English day11_rs_2786ca21:


    pl "Ha ha... I still can't believe she'd ever cry...{w} Come on, isn't this enough? I killed Rose! I KILLED HER!" with sshake


translate English day11_rs_af67f3fc_2:


    ev "..."


translate English day11_rs_61b249bf:


    pl "...Why... Why won't you say anything to me?!{w} I'm a murderer! I killed one of your priests!" with sshake


translate English day11_rs_17c9a4dd:


    pl "Please, take me away! Punish me until this sin is gone!{w} Put me anywhere, even if it's Hell, I don't care!" with sshake


translate English day11_rs_af67f3fc_3:


    ev "......"


translate English day11_rs_15a441f8:


    nar "I put my hand through the gap in the bookshelf and brush all of the neatly-arranged books out.{w} They fall out three or four at a time." with sshake


translate English day11_rs_a06cb1ed:


    nar "If they don't come out, I force them out with both hands.{w} The resulting pile of papers floods across the floor in a chaotic mess."


translate English day11_rs_e9eb8c8d:


    nar "Evelynn doesn't look at it. She just turns the page in her book.{w} Nothing seems to matter. I don't belong here anymore."


translate English day11_rs_f4b7f365:


    nar "I go around the temple, explaining Rose to anyone who will listen, telling them that I killed her."


translate English day11_rs_beaa01ca:


    nar "Lavien Rose actually has a twin sister. Younger than him, but looks just like him."


translate English day11_rs_ab011b39:


    nar "They were hiding it all this time, but she's there. I swear."


translate English day11_rs_eb5ab5e3:


    nar "She's a boring kid who spend whole days reading one children's story over and over."


translate English day11_rs_b0b55702:


    nar "She gets lonely easily, and likes talking to people. She hates tomatoes; she always grumbles about them."


translate English day11_rs_eee9928c:


    nar "She can't speak normally, and she's bad at expressing herself."


translate English day11_rs_7053a460:


    nar "She never wants to leave her room.{w} She thinks that if she leaves, it'll make her brother sad."


translate English day11_rs_c4fb0997:


    nar "So she stayed holed up in her room forever.{w} But then I had to go in and teach her about the outside world. It's my fault she died."


translate English day11_rs_c88ad8de:


    nar "Please, remember her. Don't treat her like she never existed! Come on!" with sshake


translate English day11_rs_236a2b42:


    nar "All of them look at me in confusion, then pass me by.{w} I'm like an animal they're unable to communicate with."


translate English day11_rs_51b386be:


    nar "I'm getting the feeling I know what I needed to apologize for.{w} What exactly I should confess to the angel."


translate English day11_rs_25848afa:


    pl "I'm sorry, Rose.{w} I couldn't bring myself to love you."


translate English day11_rs_f6b45fa4:


    nar "I should have just confessed my sin from the start.{w} Instead, it turned into a poison and ruined my body and mind."


translate English day11_rs_dea5bf79:


    nar "It's such a blessing to have somewhere I can go to confess.{w} And it's an equally fortunate blessing to be able to touch the angel."


translate English day11_rs_afc00276:


    nar "Within the hollow where the milk of life flows, covered with a gentle warmth and a smell of death that makes me realize I'm alive..."


translate English day11_rs_75a222cc:


    nar "...the angel, in a voice only I can hear, bestows me with a brilliant light, her radiant wings opened."


translate English day11_rs_df4e4948:


    nar "I have the ability to dedicate my soul to her..."


translate English day11_rs_00635f2b:


    nar "I..."


translate English day11_rs_6811412f:


    my "What are you saying, [na2]...? Who's Rose?"


translate English day11_rs_928ec3d0:


    nar "In the end, I can't get anyone to forgive my sin."


translate English day11_rs_b270b064:


    nar "The gray, rainy sky has opened up, and in the blankness, impurities have mixed in."


translate English day11_rs_0d452b12:


    nar "The faint scent of irises wafts to me from the place where I've closed my eyes, letting me know that my judgment has finally come."


translate English day11_rs_76b2fe88_14:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_rs_76b2fe88:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_rs_76b2fe88_1:


    nvl clear


translate English day12_rs_d06c1dd2:


    nar "I'm in a cramped, dark space that smells of dust. I squint against the hot, white light coming in through the small window."


translate English day12_rs_a9edb545:


    nar "The floor is cold and my way is blocked by a portcullis. Those at the temple called this dreary place the Sacrament of Penance."


translate English day12_rs_ec986074:


    nar "I hear the creak of the rusted door opening immediately followed by the appearance of a shadowy figure against the bars."


translate English day12_rs_365edb2b:


    nar "The long silhouette, as large as the wall, grows shorter and shorter until the person at last stands in front of me."


translate English day12_rs_611567d7:


    ev "Good day. We've met again, you and I."


translate English day12_rs_eabf2c8b:


    ev "And in the end, you've become a sinner, Brother.{w} Entrapped in an empty prison of your own making, you have crossed a river you will never return back over."


translate English day12_rs_d098b2cb:


    ev "After trying so hard to live, today is the day you will at last lose everything."


translate English day12_rs_8877fbe3:


    ev "All those who give themselves over to curiosity live in fear of this day."


translate English day12_rs_dcbacd70:


    ev "If you still have any regrets as a human, then you may hate me for not making her existence public."


translate English day12_rs_0b5cf768:


    ev "But please, don't mistake me for being any more cruel or heartless than I truly am."


translate English day12_rs_a16f8ac0:


    ev "Even I would have preferred to love them forever, had it been possible."


